\id MAT - Abureni 
\h Amatiu 
\toc1 Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba Ma̠ Agu̠o̠ Amatiu Age̠ Bho̠ 
\toc3 Amat 
\toc2 Amatiu 
\mt2 Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba Ma̠ Agu̠o̠ 
\mt1 Amatiu 
\mt2 Age̠ Bho̠ 
\imt1 Otighom 
\ip A̠d̠ire onon bha̠ Amatiu wa̠ ezin a̠d̠ien bho̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ Enigha̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ age̠. I̠na ogun ma̠ otua̠ ebhugh ola̠ ukpon ugurumeni ola̠ awe̠le̠man ogir d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ a̠ten odi o̠ni̠ ogbo ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s. D̠a̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba ta̠ Amaki̠ na̠ A̠luk, uloghom i̠na d̠a̠ opa̠n a̠d̠ien ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠livai̠. 
\ip D̠a̠ rala ya̠ na̠ eten, A̠zib̠a̠ a̠gua̠n d̠a̠ aru̠nu̠ a̠riwil d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom A̠zu bho̠ ma̠a̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠ruom Akrai̠st, o̠nyi̠ itenemeni wa̠ na̠ odoni bho̠, wa̠ ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠rileghom omom irileghom bho̠. Amatiu age̠ ma̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba bho̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom A̠zu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ aguo̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ eloghom A̠zizo̠s wa̠ Anaze̠re̠t bho̠ bha̠ Akrai̠st, o̠ni̠ itenemeni sa̠ ta̠ agba a̠mutiom ma̠ agu̠o̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny od̠i. I̠na a̠bhin obhel a̠leriom agu̠o̠ Azizo̠s a̠muzughod̠iom ra̠d̠ire d̠a̠ ugba̠iny i̠zo̠ bho̠ ya̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st, wa̠ ta̠ a̠rileghom ma̠ irileghom bho̠. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, Ib̠eb̠i A̠su̠gbagba i̠nye̠n na̠ ebhin ugba̠iny na̠ omom i̠zo̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠biniguma̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ amar agba ma̠ omuzughod̠iom iwowa̠ bho̠. 
\ip Agu̠o̠ anwa na̠ a̠sen Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n bho̠, mare̠ ma̠ anagha ma̠ a̠duom ta̠ Amatiu, ma̠a̠, “A̠zizo̠s bha̠ Akrai̠st, O̠li̠le̠ma ta̠ Aru̠li̠le̠ma na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ta̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠.” D̠a̠ ebula̠ eleleguma̠ i̠nye̠n bha̠ A̠zizo̠s O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, i̠yar eka̠ o̠da i̠na obhin, o̠ko̠l i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ na̠ Witenemeni bho̠. 
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠ 
\io1 O̠pu̠r ob̠eton a̠ghud̠um na̠ ogir agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s \ior (1:1—4:25) \ior* 
\io1 Asu̠gbagba d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu bho̠. \ior (5:1—7:29) \ior* 
\io1 A̠d̠ien kere kere atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, a̠sidogh na̠ i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an \ior (8:1—18:35) \ior* 
\io1 E̠gi̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m na̠ i̠kparakpar a̠kikiom ekunuguma̠ \ior (19:1—23:39) \ior* 
\io1 Iwowa̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ emite \ior (24:1—25:46) \ior* 
\io1 Omugh na̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s \ior (26:1—28:20) \ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Od̠ud̠ul O̠la ta̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st 
\r (A̠luk 3:23-38) 
\p  
\v 1 Od̠ud̠ul wa̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ ma̠ eghun wa̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st, o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ebraham a̠mite bho̠:  
\v 2 Ebraham amar Azi̠ki̠; sa̠ Azi̠ki̠ amar A̠zeko̠pu̠; sa̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠ amar A̠zuda̠ na̠ a̠rumor d̠o̠yo̠;  
\v 3 sa̠ A̠zuda̠ amar Ape̠re̠z na̠ Aze̠ra, wa̠ onweni d̠awa aro̠ ma̠ Atama bho̠; sa̠ Ape̠re̠z amar E̠zro̠n; sa̠ E̠zro̠n amar Aram;  
\v 4 sa̠ Aram amar Ami̠nadab; sa̠ Ami̠nadab amar Anaso̠n; sa̠ Anaso̠n amar Asalmo̠n;  
\v 5 sa̠ Asalmo̠n amar A̠boa̠z wa̠ onweni bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ A̠rehab bho̠; sa̠ A̠boa̠z amar Obe̠di̠, wa̠ onweni bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ A̠rufu bho̠; sa̠ Obe̠di̠ amar Aze̠si̠;  
\v 6 sa̠ Aze̠si̠ amar O̠li̠le̠ma A̠devidi; sa̠ A̠devidi amar Aso̠lo̠mo̠n, wa̠ onweni bho̠ aro̠ ma̠ ani̠ ta̠ A̠yuraya bho̠;  
\v 7 sa̠ Aso̠lo̠mo̠n amar A̠rihoboa̠m; sa̠ A̠rihoboa̠m amar Abi̠za; sa̠ Abi̠za amar Asaf\f + \fr 1:7 \fq Asaf \ft idi a̠risisi na̠ obheligi ma̠ Asa. Kpone d̠a̠ 1 O̠wal 3:10\f*;  
\v 8 sa̠ Asaf amar A̠zehosafat; sa̠ A̠zehosafat amar A̠zoram\f + \fr 1:8 \fq A̠zoram \ft Idi o̠nu̠ a̠b̠ekei bho̠ na̠ obhelegi ma̠ A̠zehoram. Kpone d̠a̠ 1 Aru̠l 22:50\f*; sa̠ A̠zoram amar Uzaya;  
\v 9 sa̠ Uzaya amar A̠zotam; sa̠ A̠zotam amar Ahaz; sa̠ Ahaz amar E̠zi̠kaya;  
\v 10 sa̠ E̠zi̠kaya amar Amanase̠; sa̠ Amanase̠ amar Amo̠n; sa̠ Amo̠n amar A̠zosaya;  
\v 11 sa̠ A̠zosaya amar A̠zekonaya\f + \fr 1:11 \fq A̠zekonaya \ft A̠zekonaya na̠ A̠zohakim onin o̠ni̠ bho̠. Kpone d̠a̠ 2 Aru̠l 24:6\f* na̠ a̠rumor d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ igiel wa̠ ub̠ol awa ka̠ id̠ighom d̠a̠ Ababi̠lo̠n bho̠.  
\v 12 Igiel wa̠ na̠ ed̠ighom awa d̠a̠ Ababi̠lo̠n bho̠, sa̠ A̠zekonaya amar A̠seti̠e̠l; sa̠ A̠seti̠e̠l amar A̠zerubabe̠l;  
\v 13 sa̠ A̠zerubabe̠l amar Abihud; sa̠ Abihud amar E̠li̠aki̠m; sa̠ E̠li̠aki̠m amar Azo̠;  
\v 14 sa̠ Azo̠ amar Azado̠k; sa̠ Azado̠k amar Aki̠m; sa̠ Aki̠m amar E̠li̠ud;  
\v 15 sa̠ E̠li̠ud amar E̠li̠aza; sa̠ E̠li̠aza amar Amatan; sa̠ Amatan amar A̠zeko̠pu̠;  
\v 16 sa̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠ amar A̠zose̠fu̠ owolom ta̠ A̠meri, wa̠ amar A̠zizo̠s wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠. 
\p  
\v 17 O̠ku̠a bha̠ eb̠la̠ ramu̠m bho̠, obeton d̠a̠ Ebraham ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ A̠devidi, bha̠ d̠iobh na̠ inya̠ amu̠m; ya̠a̠ obeton d̠a̠ A̠devidi ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ igiel e̠d̠u̠a Ababi̠lo̠n bho̠, bha̠ d̠iobh na̠ inya̠ amu̠m; ya̠a̠ ob̠eton igiel e̠d̠u̠a Ababi̠lo̠n bho̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ igiel ta̠ Akrai̠st\f + \fr 1:17 \fq Akrai̠st \ft a̠d̠igh Akrai̠st bha̠ o̠nu̠ A̠grik, ya̠a̠ Witenemeni bha̠ o̠nu̠ Ibru na̠ Aramai̠k, a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, “uwa̠ udoni bho̠.”\f*, bha̠ d̠iobh na̠ inya̠ amu̠m. 
\s1 I̠mara ta̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 2:1-7) 
\p  
\v 18 Onon agu̠o̠ ubhin u̠mar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st bho̠. A̠zose̠fu̠ a̠sibh A̠meri, onweni D̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ obhin ani̠, ya̠a̠ kisa̠ awa ta̠ eten otu bha̠ A̠meri na̠ a̠mumor o̠nyi̠ ola̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠ru.  
\v 19 Agu̠o̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ owolom d̠o̠yo̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i o̠ni̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom o̠ko̠ro̠ A̠meri bho̠, sa̠ aru̠ru̠an ogbogina̠ o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ e̠nwo̠ngi̠na.  
\v 20 Agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠bhin a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ i̠ru̠an bho̠, sa̠ otileduom ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ a̠mutuma̠ i̠na d̠a̠ amala, a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “A̠zose̠fu̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, ka̠ oghil obhin A̠meri ma̠ o̠ro̠ ani̠ d̠oyom, ezin bho̠ eghun wa̠ i̠na a̠mumor bho̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠ru.  
\v 21 I̠na ta̠ amar olobhiri o̠nyi̠, sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠ghol a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s, ezin bho̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠awa.” 
\p  
\v 22 Eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n imite ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ omuzoghod̠iom i̠di̠ar ya̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ owil bho̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠: 
\q1  
\v 23 “I̠bi̠ghe̠! E̠kar o̠nyani̠ ta̠ a̠mumor amar olobhiri o̠nyi̠, sa̠ ta̠ oghol I̠na ma̠ I̠manu̠e̠l”\f + \fr 1:23 \ft \xt Azaya 7:14\f* (a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, “A̠zib̠a̠ od̠i na̠ i̠yar”). 
\p  
\v 24 Igiel wa̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ asu̠ma bho̠, sa̠ a̠gir agu̠o̠ otileduom ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ a̠ruom i̠na bho̠ sa̠ a̠bhin ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠yel.  
\v 25 Ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ okod̠uom d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠meri tu̠tu̠n amar o̠nyi̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠ghol a̠d̠ien D̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s. 
\c 2  
\s1 A̠ma̠zua̠n ta̠ Iloghodi̠ar bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel wa̠ u̠mar A̠zizo̠s, d̠a̠ Abe̠ti̠li̠he̠m wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠zudia̠ bho̠, bha̠ a̠sora̠n igiel wa̠ E̠ro̠d aro̠ ma̠ o̠li̠le̠ma bho̠, sa̠ iloghodi̠ar i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ agba opuomite ogogo bho̠ iru d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m,  
\v 2 sa̠ ipura̠n ma̠a̠: “Od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ken O̠li̠le̠ma A̠zu wa̠ u̠mar bho̠? I̠yar u̠bi̠gh e̠ni̠nai̠ny D̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ igiel wa̠ a̠b̠etina̠ bho̠ sa̠ i̠yar uru ra̠ okpud̠ia̠n onigha̠ o̠yo̠.” 
\p  
\v 3 Igiel bho̠ E̠ro̠d amu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ abar bho̠ a̠nyegi i̠na na̠ eb̠la̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m.  
\v 4 Sa̠ a̠kokod̠i ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ sa̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Ta̠ o̠mar Akrai̠st bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠ken?”  
\v 5 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠: “D̠a̠ Abe̠ti̠li̠he̠m wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠zudia̠ bho̠, ezin bho̠ owil bho̠ age̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠no̠n a̠guri: 
\q1  
\v 6 “ ‘Anwa Abe̠ti̠li̠he̠m wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ebhugh A̠zuda̠ bho̠, anwa i̠ki̠r a̠pu d̠a̠ ogbo irileghom ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠zuda̠ bho̠, ku̠ku̠m eka̠, o̠ni̠ irileghom ta̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ oyom a̠mite, ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠rileghom a̠nwunom D̠ami̠, Izre̠l.’\f + \fr 2:6 \ft \xt Amai̠ 5:2,4\f* ” 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ E̠ro̠d a̠bhelegi ma̠ iloghodi̠ar bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na a̠pura̠n a̠loghom a̠ga̠i obhel wa̠ e̠ni̠nai̠ny bho̠ a̠mite bho̠.  
\v 8 Sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠a̠: “I̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ Abe̠ti̠li̠he̠m ka̠ e̠mar epura̠n egboloma̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ bho̠. Ka̠ inyin u̠bi̠gh, bha̠ id̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠loghom epa̠, b̠o̠ka̠ ami̠ agi̠ ani̠ ka̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n I̠na.”  
\v 9 Awa i̠mu̠gho̠n a̠fugh ta̠ O̠li̠le̠ma bho̠ i̠we̠le̠, sa̠ agu̠o̠ awa na̠ e̠d̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ e̠ni̠nai̠ny wa̠ awa i̠bi̠gh d̠a̠ opuomite ogogo bho̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ d̠a̠ awa sa̠ awa i̠tu̠o̠no̠m tu̠tu̠n ka̠ amara d̠a̠ anyu̠ esi wa̠ O̠nyi̠ bho̠ od̠i bho̠.  
\v 10 Sa̠ obhel bho̠ awa i̠bi̠gh e̠ni̠nai̠ny bho̠ sa̠ awa ibhon ologi ma̠ ibom.  
\v 11 Sa̠ awa id̠igh d̠a̠ otu bho̠ ka̠ i̠bi̠gh O̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ A̠meri onweni bho̠, sa̠ ikpud̠ia̠n I̠na, sa̠ ikpegion a̠rigba̠ i̠di̠ar edim d̠awa inigha̠ I̠na ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠: a̠gol na̠ afraki̠nse̠ns na̠ amaya.  
\v 12 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠l opa̠n eten imula̠ iyel d̠a̠ ebhugh d̠awa, ezin bho̠ ukikiom awa d̠a̠ amala ma̠a̠ awa omula̠ d̠o̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ E̠ro̠d. 
\s1 Eghil wa̠ o̠d̠u̠a o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Izipt 
\p  
\v 13 Agu̠o̠ awa i̠d̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ otileduom ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ d̠a̠ amala a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “B̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠bhin O̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ onweni D̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ anu̠r agi̠ d̠a̠ Izipt ka̠ aro̠, tu̠tu̠n anwa ta̠ a̠mula̠ amu̠gho̠n d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ d̠ami̠, ezin bho̠ E̠ro̠d ta̠ abho̠ro̠gh O̠nyi̠ bho̠ ma̠ ogigh.”  
\v 14 Sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ epa̠, a̠bhin O̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ onweni D̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ugula̠n obha̠ ad̠u̠a agi̠ d̠a̠ Izipt.  
\v 15 Sa̠ awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ tu̠tu̠n E̠ro̠d a̠mugh, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ omuzoghod̠iom a̠fugh ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ wa̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ owil a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “Ami̠ ibhelegi ma̠ O̠nyi̠ D̠ami̠ d̠a̠ Izipt a̠mutiom.”\f + \fr 2:15 \ft \xt Osia̠ 11:1\f* 
\s1 O̠ze̠gi̠ I̠gbara Anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ 
\p  
\v 16 Igiel bho̠ E̠ro̠d abi̠gh ma̠ iloghodi̠ar bho̠ na̠ egelemeni i̠na bho̠, sa̠ ologi do̠yo̠ a̠gurom, sa̠ ato̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠ze̠gi̠ eb̠la̠ i̠gbara ilobhiri anwi̠i̠ny d̠a̠ Abe̠ti̠li̠he̠m na̠ eb̠la̠ eghighira̠ bho̠, ya̠ na̠ ed̠um i̠wal ala ma̠ obhin osor, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠sora̠n a̠ga̠i obhel wa̠ iloghodi̠ar bho̠ i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na bho̠.  
\v 17 Onon agu̠o̠ ubhin umuzoghod̠iom iwowa̠ ya̠ owil A̠zerimaya a̠wa̠ bho̠, ma̠a̠: 
\q1  
\v 18 “U̠mu̠gho̠n o̠gba igbir d̠a̠ Arama, ed̠i na̠ i̠kparakpar ifinigha̠, 
\q1 A̠rese̠l na̠ a̠leghe ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ ola̠ na̠ o̠le̠gh i̠na tu̠tu̠n ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ onima̠ d̠o̠, ezin bho̠ awa na̠ emugughu.” 
\s1 O̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ Izipt O̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Anazare̠t 
\p  
\v 19 Igiel bho̠ E̠ro̠d a̠mugh bho̠, sa̠ otileduom ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ d̠a̠ amala d̠a̠ Izipt  
\v 20 a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “B̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠bhin O̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ onweni D̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l, ezin bho̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eku ma̠ a̠ghud̠um O̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ emugh.”  
\v 21 O̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ a̠bhin O̠nyi̠ bho̠ na̠ onweni bho̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l.  
\v 22 Ya̠a̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na amu̠gho̠n ma̠a̠ Ake̠lo̠s o̠nyi̠ ta̠ E̠ro̠d na̠ a̠rileghom A̠zudia̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ghil o̠gi̠ i̠se̠, sa̠ ukikiom i̠na d̠a̠ amala ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ agba Agalili.  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ e̠ma ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Anazare̠t, ma̠ omuzoghod̠iom i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠wo̠l d̠a̠ owil bho̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠: “Ta̠ obhelegi I̠na ma̠a̠ ola̠ Anazare̠t.” 
\c 3  
\s1 Asu̠gbagba ta̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 1:1-8; A̠luk 3:1-18; Azo̠n 1:19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ igiel bho̠ Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠ a̠ru bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ghana A̠zudia̠ ka̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠  
\v 2 ma̠a̠: “Itiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠inyin, ezin bho̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠tua̠n.” 
\p  
\v 3 Onon bha̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ owil Azaya agba a̠gboloma̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “Okoroko na̠ a̠si na̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ e̠ghana bho̠, na̠ agba ma̠a̠, 
\q1 ‘I̠tu̠ghu̠mane̠ ma̠ eten ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, ma̠ eselegi ma̠ reten d̠o̠yo̠.’ ” 
\p  
\v 4 A̠rukpe ibura̠ ta̠ Azo̠n, bha̠ ubhin ipur e̠nam a̠dol\f + \fr 3:4 \fq E̠nam a̠dol \ft e̠nam e̠kpu̠aman\f* o̠le̠m, sa̠ i̠na akpo̠aghan o̠kara ozu e̠nam a̠kitineni ma̠ ekika̠gh d̠o̠yo̠. Ed̠ia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ bha̠ i̠ganw na̠ ame̠ ya̠ od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ aparapa.  
\v 5 Igiel obha̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m na̠ A̠zudia̠ na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh d̠a̠ eghighira̠ Azo̠dan id̠u i̠gi̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 6 Sa̠ i̠na a̠wur awa ma̠ amu̠m d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y Azo̠dan, agu̠o̠ awa iloghoma̠n i̠karabh d̠awa sa̠ i̠gba imutiom bho̠. 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na abi̠gh o̠lo̠gh Rafarisi na̠ Rasadusi na̠ eru ra̠ owura̠ amu̠m bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: “Inyin anwi̠i̠ny i̠bho̠ru̠bho̠ru̠ i̠karabh i̠di̠ar, a̠nyen a̠kikiom inyin oghil o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ibom i̠gam\f + \fr 3:7 \fq I̠gam \ft ibom i̠gam osobh ase̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠\f* ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠?  
\v 8 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, imume ma̠ itu ya̠ ta̠ eleriom ma̠a̠ inyin na̠ otiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠inyin.  
\v 9 Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ko o̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠ e̠re̠ma d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin ma̠a̠, ‘I̠yar onwuna̠ ma̠ obom o̠we̠de̠ Ebraham.’ Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠bhin ikputu\f + \fr 3:9 \fq Ikputu: \ft I̠gbaki̠ghe̠; ikpokpogh i̠gbaki̠ghe̠ \f* i̠nye̠n a̠tenemeni ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Ebraham.  
\v 10 I̠se̠n, na̠ ologhom oguri ma̠ u̠do̠ d̠a̠ igbolo iriren bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ kerekere oriren ola̠ omum d̠o̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i imuma̠, ta̠ ogu okoton, orobh o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ anya.” 
\p  
\v 11 “Ya̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ a̠wur inyin amu̠m ma̠ oleriom ma̠a̠ inyin na̠ otiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠inyin, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠pu ami̠ na̠ a̠ru ma̠ ola̠ ami̠ olei d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠gi̠o̠n id̠id̠igh agbaka d̠o̠yo̠. I̠na ta̠ a̠bhin E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ na̠ anya a̠wur inyin.  
\v 12 I̠na na̠ a̠sibh okporoma̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠, ma̠ obhin o̠b̠i̠r o̠si̠ d̠o̠yo̠ okokod̠i ikpo ed̠ia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ od̠ighom d̠a̠ esi eko bho̠, ya̠a̠ ta̠ anu̠o̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ibhobho bho̠ d̠a̠ anya ola̠ ka̠ od̠im d̠o̠.” 
\s1 Owur Amu̠m ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 1:9-11; A̠luk 3:21-22) 
\p  
\v 13 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠ sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ Agalili agi̠ d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y Azo̠dan ka̠ ate̠i̠ Azo̠n owur o̠yo̠ amu̠m.  
\v 14 Ya̠a̠ Azo̠n na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ ogir o̠ku̠a, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Akpe̠ ku ma̠ anwa ma̠ owur ami̠, bha̠ anwa na̠ a̠ru ku d̠ami̠ ma̠ owur oyom.”  
\v 15 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠: \wj “Ma̠ra̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a ma̠ i̠se̠n ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom agu̠o̠ a̠sora̠n o̠ro̠ bho̠.”\wj* Sa̠ Azo̠n a̠ma̠ra̠ a̠gir o̠ku̠a.  
\v 16 Azo̠n owur A̠zizo̠s amu̠m o̠we̠le̠ ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠bhun bho̠ sa̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ a̠gurona̠ sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh ka̠ E̠mu̠gh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠sor akpasan i̠na ka̠ ukpugh osege.  
\v 17 Sa̠ okoroko a̠si a̠mite d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny ma̠a̠: “Onon o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, wa̠ ami̠ itula̠n ibom bho̠, wa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠bhon ologi na̠ a̠gboloma̠ bho̠.” 
\c 4  
\s1 Eru bho̠ Ad̠agi̠an A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 1:12,13; A̠luk 4:1-13) 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ E̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠rileghom A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ghana ma̠ eru bho̠ ma̠ o̠d̠agi̠an O̠yo̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ne ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ tu̠tu̠n eruba̠l a̠d̠uga̠la̠n na̠ etita̠n, sa̠ o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi i̠na.  
\v 3 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ad̠agi̠an bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Agu̠o̠ anwa i̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, bha̠ ruome ma̠ ikpo i̠gbaki̠ghe̠ i̠nye̠n etenegia̠n ed̠ia̠n.” 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠: \wj “Na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri ma̠a̠: ‘O̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ko obhin d̠o̠ d̠a̠ od̠e ed̠ia̠n ku̠ku̠m a̠d̠um, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ikpo a̠fugh ya̠ na̠ emite d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.’\wj*\f + \fr 4:4 \ft \xt Oloko 8:3\f*\wj ”\wj* 
\p  
\v 5 O̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠, sa̠ eru bho̠ a̠bhin i̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ka̠ amarame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ asi̠kaka otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠,  
\v 6 sa̠ eru bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ I̠na ma̠a̠: “Agu̠o̠ anwa i̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, bha̠ pele ma̠ a̠sor. Ezin bho̠, na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “ ‘I̠na ta̠ a̠ruom itileduom bho̠ ma̠ okponom Oyom, 
\q1 sa̠ ta̠ e̠su̠ar anwa d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa, 
\q1 b̠o̠ka̠ anwa na̠ od̠ighia̠nma̠ ma̠ a̠wel d̠a̠ o̠gbaki̠ghe̠.’\f + \fr 4:6 \ft \xt Raso̠r 91:11,12\f*” 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠: \wj “Na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri nyen ma̠a̠: ‘Ko o̠d̠agi̠an Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom!’\wj*\f + \fr 4:7 \ft \xt Oloko 6:16\f*\wj ”\wj* 
\p  
\v 8 D̠a̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠se̠, sa̠ eru bho̠ a̠bhin I̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu ola̠ amar agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ sa̠ atu̠o̠gho̠m a̠leriom I̠na ma̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠dila̠de irileghom e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ isosorogia̠n d̠awa,  
\v 9 sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ I̠na ma̠a̠: “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ Nyam eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n, ka̠ Anwa ikpud̠ia̠n i̠ko̠l ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠: \wj “Eru, tene ma̠ ad̠u̠a! Na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri ma̠a̠: ‘Ko̠le̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom ma̠ a̠gir a̠nigha̠ I̠na ku̠ku̠m.’\wj*\f + \fr 4:10 \ft \xt Oloko 6:13\f*\wj ” \wj* 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ eru bho̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a. I̠se̠ d̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠, sa̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ iru ra̠ i̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ inigha̠ i̠na. 
\s1 O̠ke̠ Ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 1:14,15; A̠luk 4:14,15) 
\p  
\v 12 Igiel bho̠ u̠gba unigha̠ I̠na ma̠ na̠ o̠d̠u̠o̠m Azo̠n d̠a̠ ikoli bho̠, sa̠ I̠na ad̠u̠a agi̠ d̠a̠ Agalili.  
\v 13 Sa̠ i̠na awe̠le̠ ma̠ Anazare̠t agi̠ ka̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ Akapanu̠m d̠a̠ aka abadi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Aze̠bu̠lo̠n na̠ Anaftalai̠,  
\v 14 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ omuzoghod̠iom iwowa̠ ta̠ owil Azaya ma̠a̠: 
\q1  
\v 15 “Ebhugh Aze̠bu̠lo̠n na̠ ebhugh Anaftalai̠, 
\q1 d̠a̠ akagara esoroma̠ abadi̠ wa̠ d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ Azo̠dan bho̠, 
\q1 Agalili esi wa̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny a̠rughun A̠zu na̠ erugh bho̠. 
\q1  
\v 16 A̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ erugh d̠a̠ azi̠m bho̠, 
\q1 na̠ e̠bi̠gh e̠b̠alab̠al ola̠ na̠ awar ibom. 
\q1 Ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh d̠a̠ eghighira̠ okokogh omugh bho̠ eka̠, 
\q1 e̠b̠alab̠al na̠ amu̠o̠m awa.” \f + \fr 4:16 \fl O̠lo̠gho̠m d̠a̠ atu̠ghan 
\fp \ft Ubhin d̠a̠ Azaya 9:1.\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Ob̠eton obhel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ake̠ ma̠ o̠gba orile ma̠a̠: \wj “Itiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh, ezin bho̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠tua̠n!”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠bhelegi Ma̠ I̠pu̠r Ogbo I̠tu̠o̠no̠m D̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 1:16-20; A̠luk 5:1-11) 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rile agbal Abadi̠ Agalili, sa̠ abi̠gh i̠wal a̠rumor, Asai̠mo̠n wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠pita̠ bho̠ na̠ Anduru umor d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ na̠ erobh o̠gbo̠ d̠a̠ abadi̠ bho̠. Awa i̠ku̠ ma̠ i̠ku̠.  
\v 19 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠tu̠o̠no̠me̠ Ami̠, sa̠ Ami̠ ta̠ a̠tenemeni inyin i̠ku̠ ma̠ i̠ku̠ a̠nwunom.”\wj* 
\v 20 I̠se̠ onin obhel bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠we̠le̠ ma̠ i̠gbo̠ d̠awa iten ogbo i̠tu̠o̠no̠m D̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 21 O̠d̠u̠a i̠se̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, sa̠ abi̠gh ipa̠n i̠wal a̠rumor, A̠zemsi o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Aze̠bidi na̠ Azo̠n umor d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ ologi oghugh na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠awa Aze̠bidi, na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠man i̠gbo̠ d̠awa, sa̠ a̠bhelegi awa.  
\v 22 Sa̠ awa i̠we̠le̠ epa̠ ma̠ oghugh bho̠ na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠awa iten ogbo i̠tu̠o̠no̠m D̠o̠yo̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ sa̠ A̠koko ma̠ O̠lo̠gh A̠nwunom 
\r (A̠luk 6:17-19) 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rile d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ Agalili atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠a̠ ru̠gala d̠awa, sa̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba irileghom bho̠, sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere asu̠nwe̠r na̠ eb̠la̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere ali̠gam a̠ruzu ya̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 24 Sa̠ o̠du̠ D̠o̠yo̠ asasaragi̠an d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ A̠siria̠, sa̠ awa ibhin eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r a̠d̠ien kere kere rasu̠nwe̠r na̠ i̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh ali̠gam a̠ruzu, na̠ ogbo ya̠ a̠ruru na̠ e̠b̠am, na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ena̠ bho̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ a̠risi ozu na̠ eb̠ogina̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠koko awa.  
\v 25 Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom d̠a̠ Agalili, na̠ Ebhugh A̠d̠iobh Re̠ma, na̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, na̠ A̠zudia̠, na̠ re̠ma ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠b̠e̠ye̠ma Azo̠dan bho̠, i̠tu̠o̠no̠m I̠na. 
\c 5  
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠a̠ Anyu̠ Igu bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ asi̠n d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ I̠na.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na akpato̠n o̠nu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa. 
\s1 Odu Ib̠eb̠i O̠gho̠r 
\q1 Sa̠ agba ma̠a̠:  
\v 3 \wj “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ iloghoma̠n ekulom d̠awa d̠a̠ e̠mu̠gh bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ezin bho̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny ola̠ awa.\wj* 
\q1  
\v 4 \wj Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ezin bho̠ ta̠ o̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠awa!\wj* 
\q1  
\v 5 \wj Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh ado̠l o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ezin bho̠ a̠de bho̠ ta̠ aro̠ a̠nigha̠ awa!\wj* 
\q1  
\v 6 \wj Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠, o̠ko̠i̠ na̠ ebhiroma̠ orugh ya̠ igielake̠ na̠ ed̠ighi bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ezin bho̠ ta̠ elegha̠n awa!\wj* 
\q1  
\v 7 \wj Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekpon igbirigbir bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ezin bho̠ awa ta̠ e̠te̠i̠ okpon igbirigbir!\wj* 
\q1  
\v 8 \wj Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ologi i̠b̠ab̠ala bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ezin bho̠ awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh A̠zib̠a̠!\wj* 
\q1  
\v 9 \wj Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ emutiom ekima̠ bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ezin bho̠ ta̠ obhelegi awa ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠!\wj* 
\q1  
\v 10 \wj Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ odin a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠ d̠awa na̠ ogbikimeni bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ezin bho̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny ta̠ aro̠ a̠nigha̠ awa.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 11 \wj “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin igiel a̠nwunom na̠ erogi inyin, sa̠ na̠ egbikimeni inyin, sa̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere i̠karabh na̠ igunugha̠ na̠ eb̠ologiom inyin ma̠ ebula̠ ami̠.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ibhone ma̠ ologi ma̠ ebo, ezin bho̠ alu̠kpe̠ d̠inyin ibom d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny. Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ awa igbikimeni ma̠ a̠riwil ya̠ id̠ia̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ inyin bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Ub̠on na̠ E̠b̠alab̠al 
\p  
\v 13 \wj “Inyin ub̠on e̠mara̠nwunom onon, ya̠a̠ ka̠ ub̠on bho̠ osibh mu̠, ka̠ ta̠ od̠ighi eka̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠lisibh bho̠ ta̠ a̠nwe a̠mite? Abar ola̠ ta̠ obhin ogir bo̠mu̠, a̠ten ozu orobh ma̠ a̠nwunom o̠ze̠re̠gi̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 14 \wj “Inyin e̠b̠alab̠al e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠. E̠ma ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu ola̠ na̠ anwo̠gi̠na bo̠.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Obha̠ agu̠o̠ o̠su̠o̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ ato̠di̠ obhin abafu̠ onin o̠to̠ma okpegiom. Ya̠a̠ na̠ o̠gbam ghan d̠a̠ anyu̠ abar ola̠ u̠marame̠ni̠ ma̠ onigha̠ e̠b̠alab̠al eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ otu bho̠.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj D̠a̠ onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, e̠b̠alab̠al d̠inyin amu̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠nwunom, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh ib̠eb̠i ogir d̠inyin, sa̠ ta̠ e̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ Oloko bho̠ 
\p  
\v 17 \wj “O̠ni̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an d̠o̠ ma̠a̠, Ami̠ iru ma̠ ogbogion Oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi, bo̠d̠o̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ A̠riwil bho̠. Ami̠ iru d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbogion, ya̠a̠ ami̠ iru ma̠ omuzoghod̠iom.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, tu̠tu̠n ote̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠de onon ta̠ eten e̠d̠u̠a, bebina̠ e̠pe̠re̠pe̠r bo̠d̠o̠ ekpo abar ola̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ oloko bho̠ ola̠ ta̠ ad̠u̠a bo̠ tu̠tu̠n ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠guri d̠a̠ aka ma̠ ekpo abar ola̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ oloko bho̠, sa̠ awe̠le̠man o̠b̠ar na̠ obha̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ta̠ obhelegi i̠na ma̠ wa̠ aki̠r a̠pu d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠gir i̠di̠ar ya̠ oloko bho̠ ato̠ bho̠ sa̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a nyen, ta̠ obhelegi i̠na ma̠a̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Sa̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, usigimeni ka̠ igielake̠ d̠inyin ipel ita̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠, inyin ko od̠igh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny.”\wj* 
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ I̠gam 
\p  
\v 21 \wj “Inyin o̠mu̠gho̠n ya̠ u̠gba inigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom igied̠i bho̠ ma̠a̠: ‘Ka̠ ogigh o̠ni̠.\wj*’\f + \fr 5:21 \ft \xt E̠d̠u̠a 20:13\f*\wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠gigh o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh ase̠.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ agam i̠gam a̠nigha̠ ma̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠ bo̠d̠o̠ u̠marani̠ d̠o̠yo̠, ta̠ a̠d̠igh ase̠. O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠ bo̠d̠o̠ u̠marani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ ‘Ema̠!’ ta̠ a̠d̠igh ase̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ikei A̠zu bho̠. O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Ob̠ogoro ema̠,’ bha̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ e̠banya bho̠ a̠sugho.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 23 \wj “Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ anwa a̠bhin abar alu̠kpe̠ d̠oyom agi̠ d̠a̠ enwen alu̠kpe̠ bho̠, sa̠ anwa i̠ru̠ru̠an e̠kal abar ola̠ anwa i̠pi̠o̠m umor d̠oyom,\wj* 
\v 24 \wj We̠le̠ ma̠ abar alu̠kpe̠ d̠oyom i̠se̠ d̠a̠ ukpo bho̠, ma̠ a̠d̠ia̠ ka̠ a̠tulugia̠n umor d̠oyom ma̠ a̠mutiom ekima̠. I̠se̠ ku ma̠ agi̠ ka̠ akpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ d̠oyom.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 25 \wj “Wia̠ne ma̠ a̠tulugia̠n na̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ anwa na̠ o̠ku̠anan bho̠ d̠a̠ obhel inyin od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ eten\wj*\f + \fr 5:25 \fq D̠a̠ eten \ft ob̠eton obhel bho̠ aku̠anan bho̠ a̠sor bho̠. \f*, \wj ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ko obhin d̠o̠ nyam o̠gi̠o̠m ma̠ osobhmase̠ bho̠, sa̠ osobhmase̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠bhin anwa agi̠o̠m o̠du̠o̠ma bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ o̠du̠o̠m anwa d̠a̠ ikoli.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, anwa ko omite d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ tu̠tu̠n ka̠ anwa na̠ akpe̠ kabar kabar d̠a̠ amu̠kpe̠ ebhumase̠ bho̠ amadon.”\wj* 
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ Od̠e E̠ma 
\p  
\v 27 \wj “Inyin na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n ka̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠: ‘Ko od̠e ma̠ e̠ma.’\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Ya̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠kpon ani̠ebhom sa̠ ibhir okod̠uom, bha̠ na̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ e̠ma d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ od̠iom ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam ogir o̠karabh, poko ma̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠robh. Anwa ma̠ orobh onin esi ozu d̠oyom a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ orobh eb̠la̠ ozu d̠oyom d̠a̠ e̠ba anya bho̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam ogir i̠karabh, sobhe ma̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠robh. Anwa ma̠ orobh onin esi ozu d̠oyom a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ obhin eb̠la̠ ozu d̠oyom ka̠ od̠ighom d̠a̠ e̠ba anya bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ Ogbogina̠ Ilom 
\r (Amatiu 19:9; Amaki̠ 10:11; A̠luk 16:18) 
\p  
\v 31 \wj “Na̠ o̠gba oguri ma̠a̠: ‘O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠gbogina̠ ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠, bha̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ a̠d̠ire ogbogina̠ ilom.’\wj*\f + \fr 5:31 \ft \xt Oloko 24:1\f* 
\v 32 \wj Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, a̠ten ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ ani̠ o̠ni̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ e̠ma, ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠gbogina̠ ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ od̠e ma̠ e̠ma. Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhin ani̠ ola̠ oku̠a, a̠sor oloko od̠e e̠ma.”\wj* 
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ Od̠e I̠zo̠ 
\p  
\v 33 \wj “Inyin o̠mu̠gho̠n nyen, ya̠ u̠gba unigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom igied̠i ma̠a̠: ‘Ko o̠we̠le̠ ma̠ osibh ogua̠n d̠oyom wa̠ anwa igua̠n bho̠, ya̠a̠ sibhe ma̠ ogua̠n wa̠ anwa igua̠n Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.’\wj* 
\v 34 \wj Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ aghaghana inyin ma̠a̠, ko od̠e na̠ od̠e ma̠ i̠zo̠, a̠d̠igh obhin ote̠nai̠ny, ezin bho̠, obha̠ a̠dila̠de irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠;\wj* 
\v 35 \wj Bo̠d̠o̠ a̠de bho̠, ezin bho̠, obha̠ okpokpolom o̠gbam a̠wel d̠o̠yo̠; bo̠d̠o̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, ezin bho̠, obha̠ e̠ma ta̠ obom O̠li̠le̠ma bho̠.\wj* 
\v 36 \wj Bo̠d̠o̠, ko obhin e̠mu̠ d̠oyom aghad̠i̠an, ezin bho̠ anwa ko orue d̠o̠ a̠d̠ighi bebina̠ ekpo asi̠ghal ma̠ oten aso̠n, bo̠d̠o̠ oten o̠zu̠zu̠a.\wj* 
\v 37 \wj Ya̠a̠, o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠oyom aro̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Yii, Yii,’ bo̠d̠o̠ ‘E̠e̠nyi̠, E̠e̠nyi̠.’ Ya̠a̠, ka̠ a̠pel o̠ku̠a, bha̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠karabh o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠ru.”\wj* 
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ Od̠e Olo 
\r (A̠luk 6:29-30) 
\p  
\v 38 \wj “Inyin o̠mu̠gho̠n ya̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠: ‘Na̠ obhin ekpo a̠d̠ien na̠ o̠kpe̠ ma̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien, sa̠ na̠ obhin ob̠ub̠ura̠ na̠ o̠kpe̠ ma̠ ob̠ub̠ura̠.’\wj* 
\v 39 \wj Ya̠a̠, Ami̠ na̠ aghaghana inyin ma̠a̠, ko owia̠n o̠karabh o̠ni̠ bho̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, ka̠ o̠ni̠ ab̠abh anwa d̠a̠ od̠iom ab̠akagba d̠oyom, tiba̠ra̠ ma̠ agba uwed̠i ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na nyen.\wj* 
\v 40 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan oler onyom iku obhin akapa a̠de d̠oyom, ma̠ra̠ i̠na a̠bhin akapa anyu̠ bho̠ nyen.\wj* 
\v 41 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠ponoma̠ nyam ma̠ orol a̠dol d̠o̠yo̠ orile amai̠l,\wj*\f + \fr 5:41 \fq Amai̠l \ft owewegh esi ola̠ a̠lei i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ i̠wal e̠wala (880) a̠kub̠u.\f*\wj bha̠ d̠ighe na̠ i̠na ma̠ a̠rile ma̠ i̠wal amai̠l.\wj* 
\v 42 \wj Nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠puru nyam abar, sa̠ ka̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan o̠wo̠lo̠ni̠ abar d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠oyom, ko ogineni.”\wj* 
\s1 Otula̠n Ogbo O̠lo̠gi̠an A̠d̠ien 
\r (A̠luk 6:27-28,32-36) 
\p  
\v 43 \wj “Inyin o̠mu̠gho̠n ya̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠: ‘Tula̠ne ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ aka d̠oyom bho̠,\wj*\f + \fr 5:43 \ft \xt I̠to̠t 19:18\f*\wj ma̠ a̠ghel o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ alo̠gh a̠d̠ien anwa bho̠.’ \wj* 
\v 44 \wj Ya̠a̠, Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, itula̠ne ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠lo̠gh a̠d̠ien inyin bho̠, ma̠ siseiny enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eku inyin na̠ egbikimeni bho̠,\wj* 
\v 45 \wj O̠ku̠a sa̠ inyin ta̠ oten anwi̠i̠ny O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠. Ezin bho̠, i̠na na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ ogogo bho̠ na̠ amu̠o̠m id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠, na̠ ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠bha ma̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠b̠ab̠ala bho̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erugh a̠ma̠rugh i̠te̠i̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 46 \wj Ka̠ inyin utula̠n ogbo ya̠ na̠ etula̠n inyin bho̠ ku̠ku̠m, asu̠o̠ bho̠ ka̠ ere? Igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh bho̠ eka̠ na̠ erugh o̠ku̠a.\wj* 
\v 47 \wj Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ inyin na̠ obheleghom ogbo ya̠ inyin uloghom bho̠ ku̠ku̠m, ka̠ inyin ugir ere opeleni? Ibhebhia̠n\wj*\f + \fr 5:47 \fq Ibhebhia̠n \ft Ogbo ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny eghun A̠zu, ma̠ d̠a̠ obhel bho̠. D̠a̠ a̠d̠uma̠ a̠didon bha̠ ogbo ya̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠. \f*\wj bho̠ eka̠ na̠ erugh o̠ku̠a.\wj* 
\v 48 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, irughe ma̠ a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal, ma̠ agu̠o̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ igielake̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal bho̠.”\wj* 
\c 6  
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ Onwo Inwo 
\p  
\v 1 \wj “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ b̠o̠ka̠ ogir ib̠eb̠i d̠inyin i̠ro̠ ma̠ iya̠ inyin na̠ ogir na̠ oleriom a̠nwunom o̠bi̠gh inyin. Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ inyin ugir o̠ku̠a, bha̠ inyin ko o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ amu̠kpe̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 2 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, igiel anwa na̠ a̠nwo ma̠ inwo, ko od̠ia̠ ma̠ a̠pughe ma̠ od̠od̠ue ma̠ agu̠o̠ ibhelebhel bho̠ na̠ egir d̠a̠ u̠gala A̠zu bho̠, na̠ d̠a̠ reten bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠se̠bh awa. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠ awa na̠ e̠te̠i̠ amu̠kpe̠ d̠awa.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Ya̠a̠ anwa, nwo ma̠ inwo ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ekiel agu̠o̠ d̠oyom ko ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠gir,\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ogir inwo d̠oyom aro̠ d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na, sa̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom wa̠ na̠ abi̠gh d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na bho̠ ta̠ akpe̠ nyam.\wj* 
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠siseiny 
\p  
\v 5 \wj “Igiel inyin na̠ osiseiny, o̠ni̠ ko o̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo ibhelebhel\wj*\f + \fr 6:5 \fq Ibhelebhel \ft na̠ e̠gba ma̠ ipa̠n na̠ egir ipa̠n. \f*\wj bho̠. Ezin bho̠ awa na̠ eba̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ e̠mara d̠a̠ ru̠gala na̠ d̠a̠ aka reten bho̠ osiseiny, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠bi̠gh awa. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, awa na̠ e̠te̠i̠ epa̠ ma̠ amu̠kpe̠ d̠awa eleghemeni.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ya̠a̠ igiel anwa na̠ a̠siseiny, d̠ighe d̠a̠ e̠bhai̠ ma̠ a̠gugi ma̠ egugh bho̠, ma̠ a̠siseiny a̠nigha̠ ma̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na bho̠, sa̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom wa̠ na̠ abi̠gh d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na bho̠ ta̠ akpe̠ nyam.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj O̠ni̠ ko ota̠ba̠ ma̠ a̠fugh d̠a̠ a̠siseiny d̠inyin ma̠ agu̠o̠ ibhebhia̠n\wj*\f + \fr 6:7 \fq Ibhebhia̠n \ft ogbo ya̠ ologhom d̠a̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠\f*\wj bho̠, ya̠ na̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠ ota̠ba̠ a̠fugh d̠a̠ a̠siseiny ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠nagha awa.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ko orugh agu̠o̠ awa, ezin bho̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin a̠loghom abar wa̠ na̠ akparama inyin bho̠, kisa̠ inyin ta̠ opuru i̠na.\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, onon agu̠o̠ inyin ta̠ osiseiny:\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘O̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny,\wj* 
\q1 \wj A̠d̠ien d̠oyom aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ e̠tu̠tu̠,\wj* 
\q1  
\v 10 \wj Irileghom d̠oyom a̠ru, \wj* 
\q1 \wj I̠to̠ d̠oyom e̠ro̠ ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠de onon, \wj* 
\q2 \wj Ma̠ agu̠o̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.\wj* 
\q1  
\v 11 \wj Ed̠ia̠n ya̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Nigha̠ i̠yar ya̠ a̠didon. \wj* 
\q1  
\v 12 \wj We̠le̠mane̠ ma̠ i̠karabh d̠i̠yar,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh ya̠ ipa̠n ogbo na̠ ed̠ighi i̠yar bho̠. \wj* 
\q1  
\v 13 \wj Ko oma̠ra̠ i̠yar omel d̠a̠ ad̠agi̠an,\wj* 
\q2 \wj Ya̠a̠, tenemeni i̠yar d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠karabh o̠ni̠ bho̠.’\wj* 
\m  
\v 14 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠, inyin na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh ya̠ a̠nwunom na̠ ed̠ighi inyin, O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ ta̠ awe̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠inyin nyen.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Ya̠a̠, ka̠ inyin o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh ya̠ a̠nwunom na̠ ed̠ighi inyin bho̠, O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ ka̠ o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh d̠inyin nyen.\wj* 
\s1 Atu̠ghan ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ One O̠ko̠i̠ 
\p  
\v 16 \wj “Igiel inyin na̠ one ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠, o̠ni̠ ko o̠ku̠ru̠ru̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ibhelebhel a̠nwunom, ya̠ na̠ egurumeni ma̠ ra̠misigh d̠awa ma̠ oleriom a̠nwunom ma̠ awa na̠ ene ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, awa na̠ e̠te̠i̠ epa̠ ma̠ amu̠kpe̠ d̠awa.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Ya̠a̠, igiel anwa na̠ a̠ne ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠, titila̠ ma̠ a̠misigh d̠oyom ma̠ a̠sigha̠ ma̠ elo d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ d̠oyom,\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwa ko oleriom d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ma̠a̠ anwa na̠ a̠ne ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠, ya̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom ku̠ku̠m wa̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ bho̠. Sa̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom wa̠ na̠ abi̠gh d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na bho̠ ta̠ akpe̠ nyam.\wj* 
\s1 Koko ma̠ I̠di̠ar Edim d̠a̠ Ote̠nai̠ny 
\r (A̠luk 12:33,34) 
\p  
\v 19 \wj “O̠ni̠ ko okoko ma̠ i̠di̠ar edim d̠inyin d̠a̠ a̠de onon, esi wa̠ ad̠u̠i̠ny na̠ o̠sari̠ ta̠ e̠pi̠e̠gi̠, sa̠ aru̠gba ta̠ eb̠ogion ed̠igh ka̠ eb̠ighogh bho̠.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ya̠a̠, ikoko ma̠ i̠di̠ar edim d̠inyin d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny, esi wa̠ ad̠u̠i̠ny bo̠d̠o̠ o̠sari̠ ko o̠pi̠e̠gi̠ d̠o̠, sa̠ aru̠gba ko ob̠ogion d̠o̠ ed̠igh ka̠ eb̠ighogh bho̠.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Esi wa̠ i̠di̠ar edim d̠oyom od̠i bho̠, i̠se̠ esi ologi d̠oyom ta̠ aro̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 \wj “Ekpo a̠d̠ien bha̠ ato̠di̠ ozu o̠ni̠. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom aghu̠a, eb̠la̠ ozu d̠oyom ta̠ amar awar.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ekpo ad̠ien d̠oyom na̠ a̠b̠oma̠n, eb̠la̠ ozu d̠oyom ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ azi̠m. Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ku̠gba ma̠ e̠b̠alab̠al wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ozu d̠oyom bho̠ na̠ a̠ten azi̠m, o̠ku̠a ka̠ azi̠m bho̠ ta̠ aro̠ eka̠?\wj* 
\s1 A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ Okpoki 
\r (A̠luk 16:13) 
\p  
\v 24 \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue aro̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom aru̠mu̠ bo̠. Ezin bho̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠ghel odi sa̠ ta̠ a̠tula̠n uwed̠i, bo̠d̠o̠ ta̠ a̠zuruna̠ ma̠ eghoiy a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi, sa̠ ta̠ ab̠agh e̠mu̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ uwed̠i. O̠ni̠ ka̠ orue d̠o̠ ako̠l A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ okpoki.\wj* 
\s1 I̠ku̠nu̠ na̠ I̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh 
\r (A̠luk 12:22-31) 
\p  
\v 25 \wj “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, o̠ni̠ ko o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan a̠ghud̠um d̠inyin ma̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ od̠e, bo̠d̠o̠ abar ola̠ o̠d̠a, bo̠d̠o̠ ipulupul ozu bho̠, na̠ abar ola̠ o̠lagha. A̠ghud̠um na̠ olei d̠o̠ ma̠ abar a̠pu ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, sa̠ ozu olei d̠o̠ ma̠ abar a̠pu ma̠ ibura̠, ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Ikpone ma̠ ed̠ighom a̠ghud̠um i̠nu̠r ya̠ na̠ e̠bhe̠bh d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠. Awa igbebh d̠o̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ib̠u d̠o̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ikpol d̠o̠ nyen ed̠ia̠n eguri d̠a̠ esi eko, ya̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ na̠ a̠koko awa. Inyin ulei d̠a̠ ma̠ abar opu awa ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 27 \wj A̠nyen inyin ola̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠bhin d̠a̠ i̠nyo̠gho̠ghan alo̠gho̠m bebina̠ ekud̠i obhel d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠?\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “Ya̠a̠, inyin na̠ o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan ere na̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ ibura̠? I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpon ra̠lele ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠sala bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa na̠ ebhin e̠su̠. Awa igir d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠kparakpar ogir, ikpogh d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar nyen.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Ya̠a̠, Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠ Aso̠lo̠mo̠n eka̠, d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ obura̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ibura̠ ya̠ ibhon ile̠i ita̠ odi i̠se̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠buri ma̠ i̠gho̠gho̠ ya̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠didon d̠a̠ e̠sala bho̠, sa̠ o̠nyi̠ obhel sa̠ na̠ orobh na̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠ba anya bho̠, I̠na ka̠ oburi d̠a̠ inyin a̠pu ma̠ o̠ku̠a ke̠re̠? Inyin ogbo ya̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠ghu̠a d̠o̠ bho̠!\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ka̠ o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan efugh ma̠a̠, ‘I̠yar ta̠ od̠e ma̠ ere?’ Bo̠d̠o̠, ‘Ta̠ o̠d̠a ma̠ ere?’ Bo̠d̠o̠ ‘Ta̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an ere?’\wj* 
\v 32 \wj Ezin bho̠ eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n, bha̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ibhebhia̠n bho̠ na̠ ewia̠n o̠te̠i̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠loghom ma̠ a̠bhon inyin o̠te̠i̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠ye̠.\wj* 
\v 33 \wj Ya̠a̠, abar wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu bho̠, bha̠ iwia̠ne ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ a̠ghud̠um igielake̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ta̠ o̠lo̠gho̠m eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n onigha̠ inyin.\wj* 
\v 34 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ko o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan egboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ elegien ta̠ aro̠. Ezin bho̠, elegien na̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ anyo̠gho̠ghan a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na ta̠ aro̠. Ezin bho̠ e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠se̠ a̠wuna̠ ma̠ i̠nyo̠ngho̠yo̠ngh iya̠ o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\c 7  
\s1 O̠bi̠gh Ipa̠n A̠nwunom O̠pi̠e̠ 
\p  
\v 1 \wj “Ka̠ o̠bi̠gh a̠nwunom api̠e̠, b̠o̠ka̠ u̠bi̠gh inyin o̠pi̠e̠.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj A̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ inyin ubhin u̠bi̠gh a̠nwunom u̠pi̠e̠ bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ o̠bi̠gh ani̠ inyin o̠pi̠e̠. Sa̠ a̠d̠ien o̠to̠ma wa̠ inyin ubhin u̠to̠ unigha̠ awa bho̠, bha̠ wa̠ ta̠ obhin o̠to̠ onigha̠ inyin bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 3 \wj “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ anwa na̠ abi̠gh o̠taghatagh d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien umor d̠oyom, sa̠ anwa na̠ ologhoma̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ ali̠kara wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom bho̠?\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Anwa ta̠ atu̠n ere a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ umor d̠oyom ma̠a̠, ‘umor, d̠ighi ami̠ i̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠taghatagh d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom,’ ya̠a̠ ali̠kara od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom?\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Anwa obhelebhel o̠ni̠! D̠ia̠ ma̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ ali̠kara wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom bho̠; i̠se̠ kisa̠ anwa ta̠ amar abi̠gh abar asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠taghatagh wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien umor d̠oyom bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 6 \wj “O̠ni̠ ka̠ onigha̠ ma̠ abar e̠tu̠tu̠ ma̠ a̠sib̠ogho, bo̠d̠o̠ ko orobhod̠i ma̠ ri̠b̠o̠lo̠ ibom a̠b̠ua̠ d̠inyin ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ roporopo, b̠o̠ka̠ ibhin a̠sike d̠awa e̠ze̠re̠gi̠ ed̠iomeni, sa̠ ta̠ etiba̠ra̠ e̠ku̠su̠gi̠ inyin.\wj* 
\s1 Puru, Bho̠ro̠ghe̠, Kpukpu 
\p  
\v 7 \wj “Ipuru, sa̠ ta̠ onigha̠ inyin. I̠bho̠ro̠ghane̠, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh. Ikpukpu, sa̠ ta̠ oguron onigha̠ inyin.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ezin bho̠, ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠puru, ta̠ onigha̠, ola̠ abho̠ro̠ghan ta̠ abi̠gh, ola̠ a̠kpukpu, ta̠ oguron onigha̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 \wj “A̠nyen inyin ola̠ ka̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠puru ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, sa̠ ta̠ a̠b̠eton o̠gbaki̠ghe̠ a̠nigha̠.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ a̠puru ma̠ ena̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠b̠eton o̠karabh abar a̠nigha̠.\wj* 
\v 11 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ku̠gba ma̠ inyin ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠karabh a̠nwunom bho̠ eloghom agu̠o̠ onigha̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠inyin ib̠ebi̠ i̠di̠ar, a̠dina̠mu ma̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠. I̠na ta̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ ipuru I̠na bho̠. \wj* 
\v 12 \wj Kere kere abar ola̠ anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan ma̠ a̠nwunom egir enigha̠ nyam, gire ani̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a ma̠ a̠nigha̠ awa. Ezin bho̠ onon agu̠o̠ Oloko ta̠ A̠mozizi na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ A̠riwil bho̠ ima̠ra̠.\wj* 
\s1 O̠nu̠ Ogigo wa̠ A̠kporia̠n bho̠ 
\p  
\v 13 \wj “I̠wo̠le̠ d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ogigo wa̠ a̠kporia̠n bho̠ ma̠ ed̠igh. Ezin bho̠, o̠nu̠ ogigo wa̠ are̠gh bho̠, na̠ eten wa̠ a̠bhela̠ bho̠, na̠ a̠bhin o̠ni̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighom d̠a̠ omugh, sa̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom na̠ e̠wo̠l i̠se̠ na̠ ed̠igh.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Ya̠a̠, o̠nu̠ ogigo wa̠ na̠ o̠wo̠l na̠ o̠te̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠ a̠kporia̠n, sa̠ eten wa̠ na̠ o̠wo̠l na̠ o̠gi̠ bho̠ eka̠ a̠kporia̠n. Igini a̠nwunom ku̠ku̠m na̠ e̠te̠i̠ na̠ ed̠igh.\wj* 
\s1 Na̠ obhin Itu Oriren na̠ Ologhom Oriren bho̠ 
\p  
\v 15 \wj “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ a̠riwil igunugha̠ ya̠ na̠ eru d̠inyin na̠ ibura̠ ka̠ ro̠nana, ne̠ge̠ i̠gagaman i̠nam.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj Na̠ obhin imuma̠ d̠awa na̠ olelegi awa. A̠nwunom ikpokpo d̠o̠ ma̠ itu a̠grep d̠a̠ ed̠um ib̠ub̠ulom, bo̠d̠o̠ itu a̠fig d̠a̠ e̠ko̠ko̠.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Obha̠ agu̠o̠ ob̠eb̠i oriren na̠ a̠mum ib̠eb̠i itu, ya̠a̠ o̠karabh oriren na̠ a̠mum i̠karabh itu.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ob̠eb̠i oriren na̠ orue d̠o̠ a̠mum i̠karabh itu, obha̠ agu̠o̠ o̠karabh oriren eka̠ ka̠ orue d̠o̠ a̠mum ib̠eb̠i itu.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Kere kere oriren ola̠ omum d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i otu ta̠ ogu o̠gu̠ro̠m, sa̠ ta̠ orobh o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠ba anya bho̠.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ta̠ obhin imuma̠ d̠awa olelegi awa.\wj* 
\s1 Ami̠ Iloghom d̠o̠ Nyam 
\p  
\v 21 \wj “Ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhelegi Ami̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, Wa̠nwuna̠,’ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny, ya̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ igir i̠to̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj D̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠, a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠go̠ya ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠yar ubhin d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien d̠oyom o̠gba ma̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠, obhin a̠d̠ien d̠oyom oze ma̠ a̠ruru, obhin a̠d̠ien d̠oyom ogir a̠d̠izo ilologia̠n, ke̠re̠?’\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Yaa̠, ami̠ ta̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, ‘Obhel ola̠ ami̠ iloghom inyin bo̠, itene ma̠ e̠d̠u̠a, inyin ogbo ya̠ irugh i̠te̠i̠.’\wj* 
\s1 I̠wal Ilo ma̠ A̠rutu bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 6:47-49) 
\p  
\v 24 \wj “Kere kere o̠ni̠ ola̠ amu̠gho̠n atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠ami̠ i̠nye̠n, sa̠ a̠rugh o̠ku̠a, bha̠ ta̠ obhin o̠tu̠o̠m ologhobar o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠lo ma̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ o̠gbe̠o̠ma bho̠.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj Sa̠ igiel a̠d̠io bho̠ alo̠bh bho̠, sa̠ ra̠d̠igho bho̠ iru bho̠, sa̠ rogim bho̠ igim i̠dama ma̠ otu bho̠, otu bho̠ na̠ omel d̠o̠. Ezin bho̠, o̠di̠o̠ma bho̠ bo̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ o̠gbe̠o̠ma.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Ya̠a̠, ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ ola̠ amu̠gho̠n atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠ami̠ i̠nye̠n, sa̠ ogir d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a, bha̠ ta̠ obhin o̠tu̠o̠m ema̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠lo ma̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ i̠si̠sar bho̠.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Sa̠ igiel a̠d̠io bho̠ alo̠bh bho̠, sa̠ ra̠d̠igho bho̠ iru bho̠, sa̠ rogim bho̠ igim, i̠dama ma̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ otu bho̠ a̠mel a̠tutughud̠ia̠n. Abu̠gh emel!”\wj* 
\s1 A̠limon I̠to̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\p  
\v 28 Sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠, igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠kunugiom atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ ro̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 29 Ezin bho̠ i̠na atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠, sa̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ inwegia̠n ita̠ ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠. 
\c 8  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ O̠ni̠ Asu̠nwe̠r Ekid̠igh O̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 1:40-45; A̠luk 5:12-16) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu a̠sor bho̠, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na.  
\v 2 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh a̠ru ra̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “Wa̠nwuna̠! Ku̠gba ma̠ Anwa ta̠ a̠ma̠ra̠, bha̠ koko ami̠ ma̠ ab̠ab̠alame̠ni̠.” 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠selegheni epa̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠kula̠n i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠: \wj “Ami̠ a̠ma̠ra̠, b̠ab̠ala”\wj* Ogbo na̠ onin sa̠ a̠d̠um d̠a̠ asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh bho̠  
\v 4 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠: \wj “Bi̠ghe̠! Ko o̠gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ gi̠e̠ ka̠ a̠leriom ozu d̠oyom okur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ma̠ akpe̠ ma̠ alu̠kpe̠ wa̠ A̠mozizi a̠ruom bho̠, ma̠ oleriom ma̠ anwa na̠ a̠d̠um.”\wj* 
\s1 Ologi Ima̠ra̠ ta̠ We̠mu̠ Ebu E̠gham bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 7:1-10) 
\p  
\v 5 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ Akapanu̠m bho̠, sa̠ odi we̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham\f + \fr 8:5 \fq We̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham \ft ola̠ na̠ a̠rileghom o̠lo̠gh i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100) ogbo e̠gham \f* A̠rom a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ i̠na, sa̠ ale̠gh i̠na  
\v 6 a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “Wa̠nwuna̠, ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠ami̠ na̠ anwe̠r a̠b̠ogina̠ d̠a̠ otu sa̠ na̠ abi̠gh ibom ali̠gam a̠ruzu.”  
\v 7 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran a̠fugh ma̠a̠: \wj “Ami̠ ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠koko i̠na.”\wj* 
\v 8 Sa̠ we̠mu̠ e̠gham bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠: “Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ ilei d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ od̠ighom oyom d̠a̠ ekpukpu i̠galaga otu d̠ami̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, fughe ma̠ i̠na a̠d̠um, sa̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠um.  
\v 9 Ami̠ eka̠ bha̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠, sa̠ ami̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon igboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo e̠gham ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpukpu d̠ami̠ bho̠. Ka̠ ami̠ iruom o̠ni̠ onon ma̠a̠, ‘Gi̠e̠,’ sa̠ ta̠ agi̠; ka̠ ami̠ iruom opa̠n o̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Tue,’ sa̠ ta̠ a̠ru. Ka̠ ami̠ iruom ogoni d̠ami̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Gire ma̠ abar onon,’ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠gir.”  
\v 10 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s amu̠gho̠n i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ a̠b̠a̠gha̠gha̠, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m I̠na bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ami̠ ta̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠ abu̠gh o̠ko̠no̠n d̠a̠ Izre̠l.\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Sa̠ Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ agba opuomite na̠ osor ogogo bho̠, ra̠ ed̠igh na̠ Ebraham, na̠ Azi̠ki̠, na̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ akpata od̠e d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ya̠a̠ ta̠ oze ma̠ idi anwi̠i̠ny Izre̠l ya̠a̠, nab̠o̠, awa anwi̠i̠ny irileghom bho̠, ka̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ obom azi̠m, esi ed̠i na̠ o̠ghi̠r ib̠ub̠ura̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠ o̠lo̠gh e̠gham bho̠ ma̠a̠: \wj “Gi̠e̠! A̠mite a̠nigha̠ nyam agu̠o̠ anwa ima̠ra̠ bho̠.”\wj* Sa̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ a̠d̠um onin obhel obha̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠koko ma̠ A̠d̠izo A̠nwunom 
\r (Amaki̠ 1:29-34; A̠luk 4:38-41) 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠pita̠, sa̠ abi̠gh o̠yo̠go̠-onweni ta̠ A̠pita̠ d̠a̠ e̠mana asu̠nwe̠r ola̠ amu̠m o̠bhi̠i̠y na̠ a̠sibh sa̠ na̠ a̠bhin igiri.  
\v 15 Sa̠ i̠na a̠kula̠n agu̠o̠ ani̠ bho̠, sa̠ amu̠m-o̠bhi̠i̠y bho̠ ad̠u̠a, sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠b̠etina̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ed̠ia̠n aki̠o̠m i̠na i̠na. 
\p  
\v 16 Ate̠i̠ a̠dule, sa̠ ibhinogh a̠d̠izo ogbo ya̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ enyegi iru d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠mulughuom a̠ze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ asi̠ghe̠gi̠ na̠ ekpo a̠fugh, sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠re̠ghu̠ bho̠ a̠d̠umeni,  
\v 17 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ omuzoghod̠iom iwowa̠ ya̠ owil Azaya a̠wa̠ bho̠, ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “I̠na asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ rasu̠nwe̠r d̠a̠ a̠ruzu d̠i̠yar, 
\q2 sa̠ a̠rol a̠dol rasu̠nwe̠r d̠i̠yar.”\x - \xo 8:17 \xt Azaya 53:4\x* 
\s1 Ado̠l O̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zizo̠s 
\p  
\v 18 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh agu̠o̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom na̠ eko i̠na ekiton bho̠, sa̠ a̠ruom ma̠ o̠b̠e̠i̠y d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠.  
\v 19 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ami̠ ta̠ atu̠o̠no̠m anwa agi̠ kesi kesi ola̠ anwa na̠ agi̠.” 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Rududu enwuna̠ ma̠ iyol ya̠ awa na̠ erugh, sa̠ i̠nu̠r anyu̠ eka̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ a̠rutu; ya̠a̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ od̠igh ola̠ ob̠enegiom e̠mu̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, d̠ighi ami̠ id̠ia̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ id̠i ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠.”  
\v 22 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Tu̠o̠no̠me̠ ku ami̠, ma̠ awe̠le̠man imumugh a̠nwunom bho̠, ed̠i ma̠ imumugh d̠awa.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠b̠okumeni ma̠ Ogim 
\r (Amaki̠ 4:35-41; A̠luk 8:22-25) 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ I̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ologi oghugh sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan D̠o̠yo̠ id̠igh ani̠.  
\v 24 Sa̠ o̠gagaman ogim a̠gim awai̠ d̠a̠ abadi̠ bho̠ ma̠ ola̠ ipoka̠na̠n amu̠m id̠u id̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠, ma̠ owie, ya̠a̠ I̠na na̠ okod̠u.  
\v 25 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠su̠me̠ni̠ I̠na ifugh ma̠a̠: “Wa̠nwuna̠, tenemeni i̠yar! A̠d̠ugh na̠ a̠bhin i̠yar!” 
\p  
\v 26 Sa̠ awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠: \wj “Inyin u̠tu̠n ere na̠ oghil a̠rugugu? Inyin a̠nwunom ya̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠ghu̠a d̠o̠!”\wj* Sa̠ I̠na a̠b̠etina̠ a̠mulughuom ogim bho̠ na̠ abadi̠ bho̠, sa̠ ilia̠ i̠ro̠ to̠i̠ny. 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠, ifugh ma̠a̠, “Onon ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien o̠ni̠, ma̠ ola̠ ogim na̠ abadi̠ eka̠ na̠ e̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ D̠o̠yo̠ bho̠?” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠ze ma̠ I̠karabh Aru̠mu̠gh  //  Asi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ I̠wal Ilobhiri A̠nwunom 
\r (Amaki̠ 5:1-20; A̠luk 8:26-39) 
\p  
\v 28 Igiel bho̠ awa i̠be̠i̠ d̠a̠ agba ebhugh Agadara bho̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠pel a̠bhun. Sa̠ i̠wal ilobhiri a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ enyegi i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠karabh esi bho̠ iru ra̠ i̠damaghan i̠na. Awa i̠bho̠ru̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠, a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ a̠mon ate̠i̠, orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠wo̠l esi bho̠ oten.  
\v 29 Awa i̠bi̠gh i̠na sa̠ imulughu ifugh ma̠a̠, “Anwa O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠gh ere d̠a̠ a̠ruzu d̠i̠yar? Anwa iru ma̠ i̠se̠n ma̠ o̠nyo̠gho̠gh i̠yar kisa̠ ta̠ ate̠i̠ ekunuguma̠ obhel bho̠ ke̠re̠?”  
\v 30 Igiel obha̠, obom o̠lo̠gh roporopo na̠ ed̠e ma̠ esi ola̠ osigima̠ d̠o̠ awa.  
\v 31 Sa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ i̠le̠gh i̠na ifugh ma̠a̠: “Agu̠o̠ anwa na̠ a̠ze i̠yar na̠ asi̠ghe̠ bho̠, bha̠ ruome i̠yar o̠gi̠ ka̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ a̠ruzu roporopo bho̠.”  
\v 32 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: \wj “Imite ma̠ e̠d̠u̠a!”\wj* Sa̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh bho̠ imite i̠gi̠ ka̠ id̠igh d̠a̠ roporopo bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh roporopo bho̠ igbudon ighil isor d̠a̠ a̠gbo bho̠, ka̠ i̠bhu̠ghu̠d̠i̠an imugughu d̠a̠ abadi̠ bho̠.  
\v 33 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekponom roporopo bho̠ ikpo ma̠ eghil i̠d̠u̠a, i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ ka̠ i̠gba ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imutuma̠ ma̠ i̠wal ilobhiri a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh na̠ enyegi bho̠.  
\v 34 Obha̠ abar! Sa̠ eb̠la̠ e̠ma bho̠ id̠ua̠n i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ ima̠ra̠nua̠n i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠ oten o̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ebhugh d̠awa. 
\c 9  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠koko ma̠ Odi Ukula̠ O̠ni̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 2:1-12; A̠luk 5:17-26) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh ab̠e̠i̠ d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ bho̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 2 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠misi bho̠, sa̠ idi a̠nwunom irol o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠b̠ogina̠ d̠a̠ ozu d̠a̠ a̠kporokporo ibhin ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ A̠zizo̠s. Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s abi̠gh e̠mi̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, kpo̠ ma̠ a̠luzu, na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠oyom onigha̠ nyam.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ idi ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ id̠igh i̠ru̠ru̠an na̠ epura̠n d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa ma̠a̠, “Onon a̠fugh i̠basi̠ ola̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” 
\p  
\v 4 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠loghom i̠ru̠ru̠an d̠awa, sa̠ a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ inyin na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an i̠karabh d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin?\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Oken wa̠ a̠b̠ur a̠pu ma̠ ofugh bho̠, ‘Na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh d̠oyom onigha̠ nyam,’ bo̠d̠o̠, ‘B̠etina̠ ma̠ a̠rile’?\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ya̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan ma̠a̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh a̠nwunom d̠a̠ a̠de onon.”\wj* Sa̠ i̠na akparame̠ni̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ukula̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “B̠etina̠, ma̠ a̠b̠eton a̠kporokporo d̠oyom ma̠ a̠ten a̠yel d̠a̠ otu d̠oyom.”\wj* 
\v 7 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠b̠ogina̠ bho̠ a̠b̠etina̠ a̠yel d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 8 Igiel bho̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠bi̠gh abar wa̠ a̠mite bho̠, sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh awa, sa̠ i̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠limon ya̠ o̠ku̠a bho̠. 
\s1 Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin A̠bhelegi ma̠ Amatiu bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 2:13-17; A̠luk 5:27-32) 
\p  
\v 9 Agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ a̠d̠igh erile bho̠, sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh o̠ni̠ ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Amatiu, ka̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ e̠fe̠m ogun otua̠-ebhugh bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhelegi a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Tu̠o̠no̠me̠ ami̠.”\wj* Sa̠ Amatiu a̠b̠etina̠ epa̠ atu̠o̠no̠m i̠na. 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na od̠i d̠a̠ akpata od̠e d̠a̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ a̠d̠izo igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh iru ra̠ id̠igh na̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ id̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n.  
\v 11 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠bi̠gh bho̠, sa̠ ipura̠n ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere, ka̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠inyin na̠ a̠d̠ed̠ia̠n igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠ka̠rabh?” 
\p  
\v 12 O̠mu̠gho̠n a̠pura̠n onon, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Ogbo ya̠ a̠ruzu i̠ghu̠a bho̠ i̠bho̠ro̠ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ owil, ya̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r bho̠.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj I̠se̠n, i̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ e̠tu̠ghan ezin abar wa̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠: ‘Ami̠ iba̠ra̠ ku ma̠ okpon igbirigbir, ya̠a̠ o̠kpe̠ alu̠kpe̠ d̠o̠.’ Ezin bho̠ ami̠ iru d̠o̠ ma̠ ra̠ olebh ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom, ya̠a̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.”\wj* 
\s1 Ipura̠n ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ One O̠ko̠i̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 2:18-22; A̠luk 5:33-39) 
\p  
\v 14 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠ sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Azo̠n iru ra̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere wa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠mar na̠ one ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠, ya̠a̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom ine ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 15 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ogbo erogh bho̠ ta̠ e̠tu̠n ere e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ i̠ku̠nu̠ ma̠ obhel wa̠ o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ od̠i na̠ awa bho̠? Ya̠a̠, igiel na̠ a̠ru ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa, sa̠ awa ta̠ ene ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠ye̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠bhin o̠go̠go̠ra̠ omom ukpe na̠ ab̠ad̠i̠ ma̠ opupu akapa bo̠. Ezin bho̠, esi wa̠ u̠b̠ad̠i bho̠ ta̠ a̠puruna̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ akapa bho̠ ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ agu̠an a̠peleni ma̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Obha̠ agu̠o̠ ko o̠lo̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ imom a̠min d̠a̠ opupu akana ozu e̠nam, bo̠d̠o̠ bha̠ akana ozu e̠nam bho̠ ta̠ a̠pol, sa̠ a̠min bho̠ ta̠ ezugia̠n ebhe, sa̠ akana bho̠ ta̠ api̠an. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, na̠ o̠lo̠gh imom a̠min d̠a̠ imom rakana ozu e̠nam, sa̠ i̠wal a̠yi ta̠ ed̠um ebia̠.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠b̠eton O̠gbara O̠nyani̠ d̠a̠ Omugh //  Sa̠ A̠koko ma̠ Ani̠ ola̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r anwani̠ ebia̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 5:21-43; A̠luk 8:41-56) 
\p  
\v 18 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ agba ma̠ i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ irileghom u̠gala A̠zu bho̠ a̠ru, sa̠ a̠mel a̠kpud̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠: “I̠se̠n i̠se̠n kisa̠ ekpo epobh o̠nyani̠ d̠ami̠ a̠sobha̠n. O̠ku̠a eka̠, tue ra̠ agbam agu̠o̠ d̠oyom d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um.”  
\v 19 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠etina̠, sa̠ I̠na na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m o̠ni̠ bho̠. 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ odi ani̠ ola̠, na̠ a̠lei d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal (12) ala ya̠ asi̠ na̠ e̠gbo̠ d̠a̠ ozu, awo̠l d̠a̠ aman ka̠ a̠kula̠n esi wa̠ u̠labh akapa d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠,  
\v 21 ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠fugh d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠: “Ka̠ ami̠ irue ikula̠n akapa d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠um.” 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠tiba̠ra̠ abi̠gh i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠nyani̠ d̠ami̠, ologi d̠oyom akpo̠, ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠umeni nyam.”\wj* Sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠d̠um onin igiel obha̠. 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ otu o̠ni̠ irileghom bho̠ sa̠ abi̠gh ogbo ya̠ na̠ epughe ma̠ o̠za na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ko̠ro̠ na̠ eleghe.  
\v 24 Sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Itene ma̠ e̠d̠u̠a. O̠gbara o̠nyani̠ bho̠ na̠ omugh d̠o̠, i̠na na̠ a̠kod̠u a̠kod̠ua̠.” Sa̠ awa i̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na.  
\v 25 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠ze ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ a̠mutiom bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh agi̠ ka̠ a̠sibh agu̠o̠ o̠gbara o̠nyani̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠.  
\v 26 Sa̠ o̠du̠ abar onon asasaragi̠an d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ I̠wal A̠nwunom Ikpom A̠rid̠ien 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ a̠d̠igh erile bho̠, sa̠ i̠wal a̠nwunom ikpom a̠rid̠ien i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na, imulughu i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, kpone i̠yar igbirigbir!” 
\p  
\v 28 Igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ologi otu bho̠, sa̠ a̠nwunom ikpom a̠rid̠ien bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin oma̠ra̠ ma̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠gir abar onon ke̠re̠?”\wj* Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Yii, Wa̠nwuna̠.” 
\p  
\v 29 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na a̠kula̠n a̠rid̠ien d̠awa a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Aro̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin agu̠o̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin od̠i bho̠.”\wj* 
\v 30 Sa̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠awa i̠kpagi̠na. Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s anyagh ra̠to d̠awa ma̠a̠: \wj “O̠ni̠ ko od̠ighi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠loghom.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 31 Igiel bho̠ awa i̠d̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ awa ibhin o̠du̠ ogir ilologia̠n ta̠ A̠zizo̠s i̠gba i̠sasaragi̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ebhugh obha̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠koko ma̠ Emua̠ O̠ni̠ 
\p  
\v 32 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠d̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠, sa̠ ubhin o̠ni̠ ola̠ eru na̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ emua̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na.  
\v 33 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ze ma̠ eru bho̠ asi̠ghe̠, sa̠ emua̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ake̠ ma̠ ofugh abar, sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ ifugh ma̠a̠: “Abar ola̠ o̠ko̠no̠n ta̠ od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ Izre̠l.” 
\p  
\v 34 Ya̠a̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠: “I̠na na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon ta̠ eru na̠ a̠ze ma̠ a̠ruru.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠kpon A̠nwunom Igbirigbir 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ ibom re̠ma a̠ten i̠gbara re̠ma, atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠a̠ ru̠gala d̠awa, sa̠ a̠b̠om okpokpo ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba irileghom bho̠, sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere rasu̠nwe̠r na̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere ali̠gam a̠ruzu.  
\v 36 Obhel bho̠ i̠na abi̠gh o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ igbirigbir awa id̠ighi i̠na. Ezin bho̠, ali̠gam a̠ruzu d̠awa na̠ ebuiy ka̠ e̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠ na̠ e̠tabh awa, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ro̠nana ya̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ okponom.  
\v 37 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠: “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ed̠ia̠n ya̠ ob̠u bho̠ eb̠uiy, ya̠a̠, ogbo ogir bho̠ ib̠uiy d̠o̠.  
\v 38 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, isiseinye ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ib̠ua̠ bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ afi̠ri̠ma ma̠ ogbo ogir alo̠gho̠m d̠a̠ ogir ob̠u ed̠ia̠n d̠o̠yo̠.” 
\c 10  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s Aso̠n a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal Ogbo-ogir D̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 3:13-19; A̠luk 6:12-16) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kokod̠i d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ a̠limon ola̠ ebhin oze i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh o̠si̠ghe̠gi̠ na̠ okoko a̠d̠ien kerekere rasu̠nwe̠r na̠ kerekere a̠d̠ien ali̠gam a̠ruzu. 
\p  
\v 2 I̠nye̠n bha̠ a̠rid̠ien a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo ogir bho̠. O̠pu̠r bho̠ bha̠ Asai̠mo̠n, wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠pita̠ bho̠, na̠ Anduru umor d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ A̠zemsi o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Aze̠bidi na̠ Azo̠n umor d̠o̠yo̠,  
\v 3 A̠filip na̠ Abatolomio, Ato̠mo̠si̠ na̠ Amatiu ogun ma̠ otua̠ ebhugh bho̠, A̠zemsi o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Ali̠fi̠o̠s na̠ Atadi̠o̠s,  
\v 4 Asai̠mo̠n wa̠ A̠kenan bho̠, na̠ A̠zuda̠s o̠nyi̠ ta̠ I̠skari̠o̠t, wa̠ ra̠ a̠wol I̠na bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠limon a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠ ma̠ o̠ke̠ ogir 
\r (Amaki̠ 6:7-13; A̠luk 9:1-6) 
\p  
\v 5 D̠iobh na̠ i̠wal i̠nye̠n bha̠ ya̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠limon sa̠ a̠du a̠mutiom bho̠. Kisa̠ i̠na a̠du awa a̠mutiom, i̠na a̠kikiom awa a̠fugh ma̠a̠: \wj “O̠ni̠ ka̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Ibhebhia̠n bho̠, ka̠ od̠igh nyen d̠a̠ e̠ma Asameria̠.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ya̠a̠ i̠gi̠e̠ ku̠ d̠a̠ ro̠nana ebhugh Izre̠l ya̠ na̠ ebhe bho̠.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj I̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ ob̠om okpokpo ma̠a̠: ‘Irileghom ote̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠tua̠n.’\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ikoko ma̠ ogbo asu̠nwe̠r, ib̠egione ma̠ imumugh a̠nwunom, i̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh, ize ma̠ a̠ruru ma̠ e̠si̠ghe̠gi̠. Inyin u̠te̠i̠ i̠kpo̠, inigha̠ nyen i̠kpo̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 \wj “O̠ni̠ ka̠ o̠b̠ar na̠ okpoki, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ka̠ o̠kpo̠a ma̠ o̠kara ikpoki d̠inyin,\wj* 
\v 10 \wj a̠d̠igh e̠kpa e̠gi̠, bo̠d̠o̠ akapa onwegina̠, bo̠d̠o̠ agbaka bo̠d̠o̠ okpeti i̠ki̠ani̠. O̠ni̠ ogir bho̠ akpe̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n ogir d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Ke̠ma ke̠ma ola̠ inyin ud̠igh, ipura̠ne ma̠ wa̠ a̠sora̠n d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ ma̠ esul e̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ tu̠tu̠n inyin ta̠ o̠d̠u̠a.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Id̠ighe ma̠ ebheleguma̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ otu bho̠.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ otu bho̠ a̠d̠ighom inyin, bha̠ ekima̠ d̠inyin a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu bho̠. Ya̠a̠ ku̠gba ma̠ awa id̠ighom d̠o̠ inyin, bha̠ ekima̠ d̠inyin a̠mula̠ aro̠ na̠ inyin.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ o̠da d̠o̠ inyin a̠bhin, bo̠d̠o̠ na̠ o̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠inyin, bha̠ ikpukpu ma̠ ibhugh d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠a a̠sike d̠inyin ma̠ esorogi d̠a̠ otu bho̠ bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ ma̠ eten e̠d̠u̠a.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠, ta̠ okpon igbirigbir Aso̠do̠m na̠ A̠gomora opu ma̠ e̠ma obha̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 \wj “Iloghome! Ami̠ na̠ a̠du inyin na̠ a̠mutiom na̠ a̠limon, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ro̠nana d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io i̠gagaman i̠nam. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, inwuna̠ ma̠ eloghom abar ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠karabh i̠di̠ar, ya̠a̠ ikima̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ rukur osege.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Iloghoma̠ne ma̠a̠; a̠nwunom ta̠ eb̠ologh inyin e̠gi̠o̠m d̠a̠ ri̠gada ase̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ e̠gu̠ro̠gh inyin d̠a̠ ru̠gala d̠awa.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Sa̠ ta̠ edin ami̠ ebhin inyin e̠gi̠o̠m Aru̠li̠le̠ma, na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rebhugh bho̠, sa̠ obha̠ ta̠ a̠mutiom e̠ti̠ti̠gha ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ onigha̠ awa, na̠ ogbo ya̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ya̠a̠ igiel ib̠eton inyin unigha̠ awa, o̠ni̠ ko o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan egboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠gba o̠nu̠, bo̠d̠o̠ iya̠ o̠gba, ezin bho̠ ta̠ onigha̠ inyin onin obhel obha̠ ma̠ iya̠ o̠gba.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ezin bho̠, inyin na̠ agu̠o̠ ko ofugh d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin ta̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ aru̠nu̠ d̠inyin agba.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Sa̠ umor ta̠ a̠wol umor ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ ogigh, sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ ta̠ a̠wol o̠nyi̠, sa̠ anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ ewia̠n ro̠we̠de̠ ma̠ o̠ze̠gi̠ awa.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Sa̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠din a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ alo̠gh inyin a̠d̠ien, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ne ka̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠ten.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Sa̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ ogbikimeni inyin d̠a̠ odi e̠ma, bha̠ ighile ma̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ opa̠n e̠ma. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, inyin ka̠ orue d̠o̠ orile d̠a̠ re̠ma Izre̠l e̠b̠e̠i̠, kisa̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠ru.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj O̠ni̠ atu̠ghan na̠ opu d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ e̠bana opu d̠o̠ ma̠ wa̠nwuna̠ i̠na bho̠.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj A̠sora̠n o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan bho̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ ka̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠, na̠ e̠bana bho̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ ka̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠o̠yo̠. Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ na̠ obhelegi ma̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠ ma̠ Abe̠lzibul, ere wa̠ ka̠ obhelegi d̠o̠ ma̠ eghun otu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ola̠ a̠gurom a̠pu ma̠ o̠ku̠a bho̠?\wj* 
\s1 O̠ni̠ wa̠ akpe̠ ma̠ oghil bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 12:2-7) 
\p  
\v 26 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ko oghil awa, ezin bho̠ abar ola̠ ukpegi ola̠ ko omite d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠ma bo̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ola̠ odi d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na ola̠ ko ologhom d̠o̠ bo̠.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Abar ola̠ ami̠ i̠gba inigha̠ inyin d̠a̠ azi̠m, bha̠ i̠gba ma̠ emutiom d̠a̠ e̠b̠alab̠al, sa̠ abar ola̠ ami̠ ibhobhola̠ inigha̠ inyin d̠a̠ a̠to, ib̠ome ma̠ okpokpo ma̠ e̠gba ma̠ e̠sasaragi̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ a̠rutu.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Ko oghil ogbo ya̠ na̠ egigh ipulupul ozu bho̠, ya̠a̠ ko orue d̠o̠ egigh eloghoma̠n ozu bho̠. Ya̠a̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, ighile ku ma̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠rue api̠e̠gi̠ ma̠ eloghoma̠n ozu bho̠, na̠ ipulupul ozu bho̠, d̠a̠ e̠banya bho̠.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Uwol d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠wal ro̠gi̠e̠ ta̠ egule ma̠ ape̠ni̠ ke̠re̠? Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, odi i̠se̠ na̠ omel d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠de ma̠ ola̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin ko ologhom d̠o̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Ya̠a̠, ikpo asi̠ghal e̠mu̠ d̠inyin bho̠ eka̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠loghom o̠nu̠ o̠wal bho̠.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu; inyin ulei abar opu, ma̠ o̠lo̠gh ro̠gi̠e̠ ta̠ egule.\wj* 
\s1 O̠gba Akrai̠st Onigha̠ A̠nwunom 
\r (A̠luk 12:8-9) 
\p  
\v 32 \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ agba ami̠ a̠mutiom d̠a̠ a̠misigh a̠nwunom, obha̠ agu̠o̠ ami̠ ta̠ agba ani̠ i̠na a̠mutiom d̠a̠ a̠misigh O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.\wj* 
\v 33 \wj Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ aku̠a ami̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh a̠nwunom, obha̠ agu̠o̠ ami̠ ta̠ aku̠a ani̠ i̠na d̠a̠ a̠misigh O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Ekima̠ d̠o̠ ya̠a̠ alapogidi 
\p  
\v 34 \wj “O̠ni̠ ko o̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠, ami̠ iru ra̠ omutiom ekima̠ onigha̠ e̠mara̠nwunom onon, ya̠a̠ ami̠ ibhin alapogidi\wj*\f + \fr 10:34 \fq Alapogidi \ft ogidi e̠gham, ubhin urogh a̠sidogh\f*\wj a̠ru. \wj* 
\v 35 \wj Ezin bho̠, ami̠ iru ma̠ o̠bagi̠o̠n,\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘O̠nyi̠ ta̠ a̠wia̠n o̠we̠de̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ o̠nyani̠ ta̠ a̠wia̠n onweni,\wj* 
\q1 \wj sa̠ o̠yo̠go̠-o̠nyani̠ ta̠ a̠wia̠n o̠yo̠go̠-onweni, \wj* 
\q1  
\v 36 \wj sa̠ ogbo a̠ghisia̠n o̠ni̠ ta̠ e̠lo̠gh a̠d̠ien o̠ni̠ bho̠.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 37 \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠tula̠n onweni bo̠d̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠ a̠pu ami̠, na̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠ami̠. Sa̠ ola̠ a̠tula̠n o̠nyani̠ o̠nyi̠ bo̠d̠o̠ olobhiri o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠pu ami̠ eka̠, na̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠ami̠.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ orol d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren d̠o̠yo̠ atu̠o̠no̠m ami̠, o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠ami̠.\wj* 
\v 39 \wj O̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠kighom a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ta̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠. Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ atu̠n ami̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um.”\wj* 
\s1 Amu̠kpe̠ O̠da Akrai̠st Obhin 
\p  
\v 40 \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ ada inyin a̠bhin, bha̠ ada ami̠ a̠bhin. Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ada ami̠ a̠bhin, ada ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ruom ami̠ bho̠ a̠bhin nyen.\wj* 
\v 41 \wj O̠ni̠ ola̠ ada ma̠ owil a̠bhin d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ owil bho̠, ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠d̠ien amu̠kpe̠ ya̠ owil na̠ ate̠i̠ bho̠. Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ada ma̠ ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠ bho̠, ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠d̠ien amu̠kpe̠ ya̠ ob̠eb̠i o̠ni̠ na̠ ate̠i̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 42 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan d̠ami̠ wa̠ aki̠r a̠pu bho̠ eka̠ ma̠ okpa̠ko eb̠ob̠okum amu̠m, ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ amu̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠.” \wj* 
\c 11  
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠kikiom d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ awe̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠, ka̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ agba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma ya̠ itua̠n bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 7:18-35) 
\p  
\v 2 Igiel bho̠ Azo̠n aro̠ d̠a̠ ikoli amu̠gho̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ Akrai̠st na̠ a̠gir bho̠, sa̠ a̠ruom ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠,  
\v 3 ka̠ opura̠n o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Anwa o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠ ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ i̠yar ogon opa̠n o̠ni̠?” 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ Azo̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh bho̠, sekina̠ ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Ogbo ya̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien bho̠, na̠ e̠bi̠gh esi, a̠rukula̠ bho̠ na̠ erile, ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh bho̠ na̠ okoko o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠, remua̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n abar, imumugh a̠nwunom na̠ ob̠egion, sa̠ na̠ o̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba bho̠ na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ o̠tu̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ rogir ya̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠gir bho̠ a̠ghel ami̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 7 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠d̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ake̠ ma̠ o̠gba i̠di̠ar ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ Azo̠n owurma̠mu̠m bho̠ onigha̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠a̠: \wj “Inyin u̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠sala bho̠, ka̠ inyin u̠ru̠ru̠an o̠bi̠gh ere? Ikpoko ya̠ na̠ eduka̠ d̠a̠ o̠fe̠gu̠ ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ku̠gba ma o̠ku̠a d̠o̠, ka̠ inyin u̠ru̠ru̠an ka̠ o̠bi̠gh o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠bura̠ ma̠ ibura̠ e̠no̠gho̠man ke̠re̠? Iloghome ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ebura̠ ma̠ ibura̠ e̠no̠gho̠man, na̠ erugh d̠a̠ rogigo Aru̠li̠le̠ma!\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Ya̠a̠, inyin u̠tu̠n ka̠ o̠bi̠gh ere o̠gi̠? Owil ke̠re̠? Yii, owil ga̠i, ya̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠pu ma̠ owil.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Onon o̠ni̠ wa̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: \wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠ruom o̠ni̠ a̠duom d̠ami̠ ma̠ od̠ia̠ o̠gi̠ kisa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠ru,\wj* 
\q2 \wj ma̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man eten d̠oyom ob̠a̠ra̠.’\wj* 
\m  
\v 11 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ anwani̠ i̠maragi̠ bho̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ma̠ Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠ ta̠ omite d̠o̠; ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ aki̠r a̠pu d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny bho̠, abu̠gh a̠pu i̠na.”\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ob̠eton d̠a̠ amu̠m ta̠ Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠ ra̠ o̠te̠i̠ i̠se̠n, irileghom ote̠nai̠ny na̠ asu̠ ma̠ onyen o̠kparakpar agu̠o̠, sa̠ i̠kparakpar a̠nwunom ku̠ku̠m na̠ ewia̠n na̠ e̠te̠i̠.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Kisa̠ Azo̠n ta̠ a̠ru, eb̠la̠ a̠riwil bho̠ ewa̠ sa̠ oloko bho̠ eka̠ agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ irileghom bho̠.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Sa̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ inyin ta̠ o̠da ma̠ asu̠gbagba d̠ami̠ obhin, bha̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, i̠na I̠lai̠za wa̠ a̠riwil bho̠ iwa̠ ma̠a̠ ta̠ a̠ru bho̠.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj “Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠to, anagha o!”\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 \wj “I̠se̠n, ka̠ ta̠ obhin amu̠m onon atu̠o̠m ere? Awa od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny, ya̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ egbolom a̠b̠ua̠, sa̠ odi na̠ a̠kele ma̠ odi ma̠a̠: \wj* 
\q1  
\v 17 \wj “‘I̠yar upughe ma̠ od̠od̠ue onigha̠ inyin,\wj* 
\q2 \wj ya̠a̠ inyin u̠ghe̠r d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠gba,\wj* 
\q1 \wj I̠yar u̠mo̠r aso̠r ekulom, \wj* 
\q2 \wj ya̠a̠ inyin u̠ku̠nu̠ d̠o̠.’ \wj* 
\m  
\v 18 \wj Azo̠n a̠ru bho̠, na̠ od̠e d̠o̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, na̠ o̠d̠a d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠min nyen, sa̠ inyin u̠gba ma̠a̠: ‘Eru na̠ ab̠am.’\wj* 
\v 19 \wj O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ a̠ru bho̠, na̠ a̠d̠e na̠ ad̠a, sa̠ inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘I̠bi̠ghe̠ ma̠ o̠d̠o̠gho̠d̠o̠gh na̠ o̠d̠a ma̠ a̠min onon, wa̠ na̠ a̠rologha̠n igun ma̠ otua̠-ebhugh na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠.’ Yaa̠, od̠ighi i̠di̠ar o̠ni̠ na̠ eleriom eloghom abar o̠ni̠ bho̠.” \wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠sugi ma̠ Re̠ma ya̠ Otiba̠ra̠ d̠o̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 20 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ake̠ ma̠ osugi re̠ma ya̠ i̠na a̠gir ibom ilologia̠n bho̠, ezin bho̠ awa ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ otiba̠ra̠.  
\v 21 \wj “Ekulom inyin a̠nwunom A̠kora̠zin! Ekulom inyin a̠nwunom Abe̠tsai̠da! Ezin bho̠, ilologia̠n ya̠ ugir unigha̠ inyin bho̠ ma̠ ugir onigha̠ ma̠ Ataya na̠ Asi̠do̠n nab̠o̠, awa ka̠ i̠lo̠gi̠an akapa i̠ku̠nu̠, sa̠ ka̠ ibhugha̠ ma̠ i̠ru̠ru̠ etiba̠ra̠ ka̠ ob̠om igiel.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj O̠ku̠a eka̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ta̠ okpon igbirigbir Ataya na̠ Asi̠do̠n opu inyin d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Ya̠a̠, inyin a̠nwunom Akapanu̠m, ta̠ o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny ke̠re̠? E̠nyi̠, ta̠ orobh inyin osoroni d̠a̠ ekud̠um a̠de imumugh bho̠. Ezin bho̠, ilologia̠n ya̠ ugir unigha̠ inyin bho̠, ma̠a̠ ugir d̠a̠ e̠ma Aso̠do̠m nab̠o̠, e̠ma bho̠ ka̠ i̠ro̠ ate̠i̠ a̠didon.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj O̠ku̠a eka̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ta̠ okpon igbirigbir a̠nwunom Aso̠do̠m opu inyin d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Tue D̠ami̠ ra̠ A̠sira̠ ma̠ Epobh 
\r (A̠luk 10:21-22) 
\p  
\v 25 D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ na̠ ase̠bh anwa O̠we̠de̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ote̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠de. Ezin bho̠ anwa i̠wo̠gi̠o̠m i̠nye̠n iloghodi̠ar bho̠ sekina̠ iloghod̠ire bho̠, sa̠ anwa ileriom kuma̠ ogbo ya̠ olei d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠d̠iar bho̠.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Ya̠ga̠i, a̠sora̠n O̠we̠de̠. Ezin bho̠, a̠d̠igh anwa ma̠ ologi ma̠ o̠to̠ oguri o̠ku̠a.\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 \wj “O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar. O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom O̠nyi̠ bho̠ bo̠, a̠ten O̠we̠de̠ bho̠. Obha̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, a̠ten O̠nyi̠ bho̠, na̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ O̠nyi̠ bho̠ ato̠ ma̠ obhin O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ oleriom.\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “Itue d̠ami̠, eb̠la̠ inyin ya̠ a̠ruzu na̠ edughogh, sa̠ a̠dol na̠ e̠ne̠mu̠o̠m bho̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin osira̠ epobh.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Ib̠etone ma̠ a̠dol d̠a̠ ami̠ ma̠ erol, ma̠ e̠tu̠ghan d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠, ezin bho̠ ami̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ekima̠ na̠ ozuruna̠ eghoi, sa̠ reloghoma̠n a̠ruzu d̠inyin ta̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ ekima̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Ezin bho̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m ami̠ ob̠ub̠ura̠n abar, sa̠ a̠dol d̠ami̠ a̠bhobhogh.”\wj* 
\c 12  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 2:23-28; A̠luk 6:1-5) 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠, A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ ari̠si̠ i̠bu̠kpa ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠, ya̠a̠ o̠ko̠i̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠ke̠ ma̠ ob̠oghi itu i̠bu̠kpa bho̠ o̠kpi̠r od̠e.  
\v 2 Igiel bho̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠bi̠gh bho̠, sa̠ ifugh inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Bi̠ghe̠, ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom na̠ egir abar ola̠ oloko bho̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ogir d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osira̠-epobh bho̠”  
\v 3 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ A̠devidi a̠gir igiel bho̠ o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi i̠na sekina̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu akpu̠ru̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ka̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ abe̠re̠di̠ ya̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ i̠na, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ od̠e, ya̠ i̠ro̠ inigha̠ ma̠ rokur ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ku̠ku̠m bho̠.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Bo̠d̠o̠, inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ d̠a̠ oloko bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ rokur i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ i̠pi̠o̠gho̠m A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠, ya̠a̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ awa esor oloko bho̠ ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ya̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, abar ola̠ a̠pu ma̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj I̠se̠ ma̠ inyin uloghom ezin abar wa̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠: ‘Ami̠ iba̠ra̠ kuma̠ okpon igbirigbir, ya̠ i̠ko̠l d̠o̠,’ nab̠o̠, inyin ka̠ usobh d̠o̠ ma̠ ase̠ obhumeni ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ o̠pi̠o̠gho̠m d̠o̠ bho̠.\wj*\x - \xo 12:7 \xt Osia̠ 6:6\x* 
\v 8 \wj Ezin bho̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠koko ma̠ O̠ni̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 3:1-6; A̠luk 6:6-11) 
\p  
\v 9 A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ sa̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ u̠gala A̠zu bho̠,  
\v 10 sa̠ abi̠gh o̠ni̠ ola̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ na̠ akpari̠an. Sa̠ awa ipura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “A̠sora̠n okoko o̠ni̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠ ke̠re̠?” Awa ipura̠n o̠ku̠a bo̠ka̠ awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh e̠kal ola̠ obhin oler o̠yo̠.  
\v 11 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠nyen o̠ni̠ inyin ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ o̠nana, sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠ a̠mel a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ogugua̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ka̠ o̠gi̠o̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ka̠ a̠sibh a̠mutiom?\wj* 
\v 12 \wj O̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ na̠ olei d̠o̠ ma̠ abar a̠pu ma̠ o̠nana ke̠re̠? O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, a̠sora̠n ogir ib̠eb̠i ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osirepobh.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Selegheni ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠oyom.”\wj* Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠selegheni, sa̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ a̠bhon aro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ uwed̠i.  
\v 14 Sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a ka̠ i̠mimia̠n igboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogigh o̠yo̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s Ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aso̠n bho̠ 
\p  
\v 15 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠loghoma̠n sa̠ ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠tu̠o̠no̠m I̠na, sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ eb̠la̠ awa.  
\v 16 Sa̠ a̠kikiom awa ma̠a̠ od̠ighi̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ eloghom ya̠ igboloma̠ I̠na.  
\v 17 Ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ omuzoghod̠iom iwowa̠ ta̠ owil Azaya bho̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q1  
\v 18 “Obha̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠ami̠ wa̠ ami̠ i̠so̠n bho̠, 
\q2 o̠ni̠ wa̠ ami̠ itula̠n bho̠, wa̠ na̠ a̠bhonomeni ma̠ ologi d̠ami̠ bho̠; 
\q1 Ami̠ ta̠ alo̠gh E̠mu̠gh d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠, 
\q2 sa̠ ta̠ a̠sobh a̠ga̠i ase̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ rebhugh bho̠. 
\q1  
\v 19 I̠na ko o̠b̠u̠man d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠b̠e̠m, bo̠d̠o̠ omulughu izul, 
\q2 o̠ni̠ ko o̠mu̠gho̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ okoroko d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ reten bho̠. 
\q1  
\v 20 I̠na ko onwinigi d̠o̠ ma̠ ikpoko ya̠ na̠ e̠nyu̠bhi̠an, 
\q2 sa̠ i̠na ko od̠imigi d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠tani̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ od̠im nyen, 
\q1 tu̠tu̠n i̠na ta̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ igielake̠ a̠sobh ase̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom. 
\q1  
\v 21 Sa̠ rebhugh bho̠ ta̠ eb̠em ologi d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠.”\f + \fr 12:21 \ft \xt Azaya 42:1-4\f* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s na̠ A̠belzibul 
\r (Amaki̠ 3:20-30; A̠luk 11:14-23; 12:10) 
\p  
\v 22 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠ sa̠ idi a̠nwunom ibhin o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh na̠ anyo̠gho̠gh, ola̠ aro̠ ma̠ emua̠ ola̠ a̠rid̠ien na̠ eb̠omia̠n nyen, iruom i̠na. Sa̠ i̠na a̠koko ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ake̠ ma̠ ofugh abar, o̠bi̠gh esi.  
\v 23 Sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ na̠ epupura̠n ma̠a̠, “Onon ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 24 Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon ta̠ Abe̠lzibul, we̠mu̠ a̠ruru bho̠ na̠ a̠ze ma̠ i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh.” 
\p  
\v 25 Ya̠a̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠loghom i̠ru̠ru̠an d̠awa bho̠, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Irileghom ola̠ aru̠gi̠an na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ ago̠gu̠an a̠mel, sa̠ e̠ma bo̠d̠o̠ eghun otu ola̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ko o̠mara d̠o̠ gigiribh.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠ Eru bho̠ na̠ a̠ze ma̠ Eru bho̠ na̠ asi̠ghe̠, sa̠ i̠na na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n ozu d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ aru̠gi̠an! O̠ku̠a ka̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ amara gigiribh?\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠ Ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠limon ta̠ Abe̠lzibul na̠ a̠ze ma̠ a̠ruru na̠ asi̠ghe̠gi̠, ka̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠inyin na̠ e̠bhin ere na̠ eze na̠ e̠si̠ghe̠gi̠? D̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, awa ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ isobhmase̠ d̠inyin.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Ya̠a̠, agu̠o̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin E̠mu̠gh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ze ma̠ a̠ruru na̠ asi̠ghe̠gi̠ bho̠, bha̠ iloghome ma̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ inyin.\wj* 
\p  
\v 29 \wj “Bo̠d̠o̠, ka̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu omomona̠n ka̠ a̠ghumi ma̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠, a̠sigimeni ka̠ na̠ a̠d̠ia̠ abhad̠i̠ ma̠ omomona̠n bho̠, i̠se̠ kisa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue amar afo̠i̠ny otu omomona̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 30 \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ri̠la d̠o̠ na̠ ami̠, na̠ a̠wia̠n ami̠; sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ na̠ ami̠ okokod̠ia̠n bho̠, na̠ asasaragi̠.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, eb̠la̠ i̠karabh ya̠ o̠ni̠ a̠gir na̠ a̠fugh i̠basi̠ ya̠ o̠ni̠ a̠fugh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠, ta̠ o̠we̠le̠man; ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠fugh i̠basi̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, ko o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠fugh i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠, ta̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠na, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠fugh i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, ka̠ o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠ i̠na, a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ amu̠m onon, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ amu̠m wa̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠.\wj* 
\s1 Oriren na̠ Itu d̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (A̠luk 6:43-45) 
\p  
\v 33 \wj “Ku̠gba ma̠ anwa amar a̠koko ma̠ oriren ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠bhon, bha̠ itu oriren bho̠ obhon, ya̠a̠ ku̠gba ma̠ anwa na̠ amar d̠o̠ a̠koko ma̠ oriren bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠bhon, bha̠ itu oriren bho̠ ko obhon d̠o̠ nyen. Ezin bho̠ na̠ obhin otu bho̠ na̠ ologhom oriren bho̠.\wj* 
\v 34 \wj Anwi̠i̠ny i̠bho̠ru̠bho̠ru̠ i̠karabh i̠di̠ar. Inyin ogbo ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠ ta̠ ed̠ighi eka̠ efugh ib̠eb̠i a̠fugh. Ezin bho̠, a̠d̠ien i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠ni̠ a̠kokod̠i a̠muzoghod̠i d̠a̠ ologi bho̠, i̠ye̠ bha̠ iya̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠fugh bho̠.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj O̠ni̠ wa̠ ob̠eb̠i ologi bho̠, na̠ a̠mutioghom ib̠eb̠i i̠di̠ar d̠a̠ ib̠eb̠i ya̠ a̠kpol d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠; sa̠ o̠karabh o̠ni̠ bho̠, na̠ a̠mutioghom i̠karabh i̠di̠ar d̠a̠ i̠karabh ya̠ a̠kpol d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 36 \wj I̠se̠n, bha̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, kere kere a̠fugh i̠te̠i̠, ya̠ a̠nwunom ifugh bha̠ ta̠ obhin osobh ase̠ onigha̠ awa d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 37 \wj Ezin bho̠ ta̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien a̠fugh d̠oyom sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠bhin eyel ase̠, sa̠ ta̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠fugh d̠oyom sa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠bhin ebhum ase̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Ipuru ma̠ Elegh 
\r (Amaki̠ 8:11,12; A̠luk 11:29-32) 
\p  
\v 38 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ idi i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠ ifugh inigha̠ I̠na ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni, i̠yar na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan o̠bi̠gh elegh d̠a̠ ozu D̠oyom.”  
\v 39 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠: \wj “Amu̠m i̠basi̠ ola̠ oghila̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ a̠puru ma̠ elegh; ya̠a̠ elegh ola̠ ta̠ oleriom i̠na bo̠, a̠ten elegh ta̠ owil A̠zona̠.\wj* 
\v 40 \wj Onin agu̠o̠ wa̠ A̠zona̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ okurogh obom ena̠ ma̠ i̠sar etita̠n na̠ i̠sar a̠d̠ugula̠n bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ologi a̠de bho̠ ma̠ i̠sar etita̠n na̠ i̠sar a̠d̠ugula̠n.\wj* 
\v 41 \wj D̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠, a̠nwunom A̠ninive ta̠ e̠mara e̠gba ma̠ onyob̠a̠ ebhumeni ma̠ amu̠m onon; ezin bho̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n okpokpo ta̠ A̠zona̠, sa̠ itiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠awa. Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ma̠ A̠zona̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n!\wj* 
\v 42 \wj D̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠, O̠li̠la ani̠ebhom ebhugh Ase̠ba ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ agba ma̠ onyob̠a̠ ebhumeni ma̠ amu̠m onon; ezin bho̠, i̠na ad̠u̠a ma̠ esi egbeiny a̠ru ra̠ anagha ma̠ eloghom abar ta̠ Aso̠lo̠mo̠n. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ma̠ Aso̠lo̠mo̠n od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n!\wj* 
\s1 Omula̠ oru ta̠ O̠karabh E̠mu̠gh bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 11:24-26) 
\p  
\v 43 \wj “Igiel o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠, sa̠ na̠ ada na̠ agi̠ na̠ ada na̠ a̠ru ma̠ a̠risisi ya̠ aghi̠ghi̠ra ma̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh esi ola̠ a̠sora̠n od̠igh o̠ro̠. Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠a̠ na̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠,\wj* 
\v 44 \wj sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ otu wa̠ ami̠ i̠d̠u̠a bho̠.’ Igiel i̠na a̠misi sa̠ abi̠gh ma̠a̠, otu bho̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bo̠, na̠ o̠mar ogber oselegi ma̠ i̠di̠ar,\wj* 
\v 45 \wj i̠se̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠bhin ipa̠n od̠ua̠l i̠karabh aru̠mu̠gh ya̠ i̠bho̠ru̠ ipu i̠na ma̠ o̠b̠aragu̠ma o̠yo̠, sa̠ awa ta̠ ka̠ ed̠igh erugh d̠a̠ ozu o̠ni̠ bho̠. Sa̠ e̠do̠lo̠ghu̠ma o̠ni̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠gurom a̠pu ma̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠pu̠r igiel bho̠. Obha̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ aro̠ nyen d̠a̠ o̠karabh amu̠m onon.”\wj* 
\s1 Oweni na̠ A̠rumor ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 3:31-35; A̠luk 8:19-21) 
\p  
\v 46 Agu̠o̠ i̠na od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ a̠fugh na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ onweni na̠ a̠rumor d̠o̠yo̠ iru ra̠ i̠mara d̠a̠ etire na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠ghan o̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an o̠yo̠.  
\v 47 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Bi̠ghe̠, onweni d̠oyom na̠ a̠rumor d̠oyom na̠ e̠mara d̠a̠ etire na̠ e̠bho̠ro̠ghan ofugha̠n onyom.”  
\v 48 Sa̠ awo̠ran o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠: \wj “A̠nyen oweni d̠ami̠, ya̠a̠ wa̠ a̠nyen a̠rumor d̠ami̠?”\wj* 
\v 49 Sa̠ i̠na a̠selegheni ma̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ atu̠o̠m ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠: \wj “Onweni d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠rumor d̠ami̠ bha̠ ogbo iya̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\v 50 \wj Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠gir i̠to̠ ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠, bha̠ umor d̠ami̠, na̠ u̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, na̠ onweni d̠ami̠.”\wj* 
\c 13  
\s1 A̠sidogh Ogbebh ma̠ Ed̠ia̠n bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 4:1-9; A̠luk 8:4-8) 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ onin a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mite d̠a̠ otu bho̠ agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ aka abadi̠ bho̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom iko i̠na ikiton ma̠ ola̠ i̠na agi̠ ka̠ a̠pel a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de, sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠mara d̠a̠ egbolom.  
\v 3 Sa̠ agba ma̠ a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar a̠nigha̠ awa d̠a̠ ra̠sidogh ma̠a̠: \wj “I̠nagha o! Ogbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n agi̠ d̠a̠ o̠si̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ ogbebh ed̠ia̠n.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Sa̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na a̠kpo ikpo ed̠ia̠n bho̠ asar bho̠, sa̠ idi imel d̠a̠ eten, sa̠ i̠nu̠r bho̠ iru ra̠ ikpokpoiny id̠e i̠mado̠n.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Ya̠a̠ idi sa̠ imel d̠a̠ a̠de o̠gbe̠o̠ma, esi ola̠ o̠do̠gho̠l bho̠ okud̠um d̠o̠. Sa̠ i̠rabh epa̠ ma̠ o̠su̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠do̠gho̠l bho̠ okud̠um d̠o̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ ogogo a̠mite bho̠, sa̠ i̠nyu̠n i̠ghaghara d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ i̠ki̠ka o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Sa̠ idi imel d̠a̠ e̠ku̠ko̠ ib̠ub̠ulom, sa̠ e̠ku̠ko̠ ib̠ub̠ulom bho̠ i̠su̠ ikpegiom ed̠ia̠n bho̠ i̠bhu̠ghu̠d̠i̠ i̠ze̠gi̠.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Sa̠ idi imel d̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i a̠de, sa̠ imum imuma̠ ya̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100) a̠bin, idi e̠rabharabh (60) a̠bin, sa̠ idi imum a̠d̠usubh na̠ d̠iobh (30) a̠bin i̠se̠.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠to, anagha o!”\wj* 
\s1 Ezin A̠sidogh bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 4:10-12; A̠luk 8:9-10) 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ iru ra̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ anwa na̠ a̠rogha̠n a̠sidogh na̠ a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “D̠a̠ inyin bha̠ na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ologhom i̠di̠ar e̠wo̠gi̠na irileghom ote̠nai̠ny; ya̠a̠ unigha̠ ani̠ d̠o̠ awa.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj I̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ o̠lo̠gho̠m o̠gbam, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠b̠utu, ya̠a̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ bho̠, ta̠ o̠wo̠r nyen ya̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Ami̠ idin o̠ku̠a na̠ a̠bhin a̠sidogh na̠ a̠fugha̠n awa:\wj* 
\q1 \wj “Ezin bho̠ ta̠ ekpon, ya̠a̠ ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠.\wj* 
\q2 \wj Awa ta̠ e̠nagha, ya̠a̠ awa ko o̠mu̠gho̠n d̠o̠ e̠mu̠gho̠nyan nyen.”\wj* 
\m  
\v 14 \wj Sa̠ ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom onigha̠ awa ma̠ iwowa̠ ta̠ Azaya ma̠a̠:\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘D̠a̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n bha̠ ta̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n sa̠ ko o̠mu̠gho̠nya̠n d̠o̠;\wj* 
\q2 \wj d̠a̠ o̠bi̠gh bha̠ ta̠ e̠bi̠gh, ya̠a̠ ko olelegi d̠o̠.\wj* 
\q1  
\v 15 \wj Na̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n;\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ na̠ ob̠ulugi ma̠ ra̠to d̠awa,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ na̠ okpegi ma̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠awa,\wj* 
\q1 \wj ma̠ ola̠ awa ibhin d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠awa e̠bi̠gh abar,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n d̠o̠ na̠ ra̠to d̠awa, \wj* 
\q2 \wj ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ka̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ eloghoma̠n eten.’\wj* 
\m  
\v 16 \wj Ya̠a̠, na̠ otutumeni inyin ogbo ya̠ a̠rid̠ien bho̠ na̠ e̠bi̠gh esi bho̠, sa̠ ra̠to bho̠ na̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ akparame̠ni̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, a̠d̠izo a̠riwil na̠ ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom e̠mar e̠bho̠ro̠ghan o̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠, na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n d̠o̠.\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s agba ma̠ ezin A̠sidogh  //  Ogbebh ma̠ Ed̠ia̠n bho̠ O̠si̠si̠ghe̠ni̠ 
\p  
\v 18 \wj “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠nagha ma̠ ezin a̠sidogh ogbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ amu̠gho̠n a̠duom irileghom bho̠, sa̠ i̠na o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠, bha̠ o̠karabh o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ ugbebh d̠a̠ ologi o̠ni̠ bho̠. I̠nye̠n bha̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ imel d̠a̠ eten bho̠.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ya̠a̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ imel d̠a̠ a̠de o̠gbe̠o̠ma bho̠, bha̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n asu̠gbagba bho̠, sa̠ i̠da epa̠ ibhin d̠a̠ a̠libhon ologi.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Ya̠a̠ isi d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠ki̠ka iya̠ awa, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ ekud̠i obhel, sa̠ imel i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ igiel ali̠gam a̠ruzu bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ uponoma̠ awa d̠a̠ ebula̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Sa̠ iya̠ imel d̠a̠ ed̠um ib̠ub̠ulom bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n asu̠gbagba bho̠, sa̠ i̠nyo̠gho̠nyo̠gh e̠mara̠nwunom na̠ e̠ralma ogbo e̠li̠la i̠vi̠mo̠m asu̠gbagba bho̠, sa̠ awa orue d̠o̠ ma̠ omum itu.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Ya̠a̠, ikpo ed̠ia̠n ya̠ imel d̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i a̠de bho̠, bha̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n asu̠gbagba bho̠ sa̠ i̠mu̠gho̠nyan bho̠, sa̠ imum itu ga̠i, idi i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100), sa̠ idi e̠rabharabh (60), sa̠ idi a̠d̠usubh na̠ d̠iobh (30) a̠bin i̠se̠, d̠a̠ ikpo ya̠ ubhin ugbebh bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh Ib̠utula d̠a̠ O̠si̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh opa̠n a̠sidogh a̠fugh ma̠a̠: \wj “Irileghom ote̠nai̠ny agu̠b̠an o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠gbebh ib̠eb̠i ikpo ed̠ia̠n d̠a̠ o̠si̠ d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ ekod̠u bho̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠o̠yo̠ agi̠ ka̠ alo̠gi̠o̠gho̠m ib̠utula d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io i̠bu̠kpa bho̠ sa̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Sa̠ igiel i̠mu̠nu̠mu̠n i̠bu̠kpa bho̠ i̠rabh imite bho̠, sa̠ ib̠utula bho̠ eka̠ i̠rabh imite.\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 \wj “Sa̠ aru̠bana bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ o̠si̠ bho̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, ‘We̠mu̠, wokuma̠ ugbebh ib̠eb̠i ikpo i̠bu̠kpa d̠a̠ o̠si̠ d̠oyom? O̠ku̠a ka̠ ib̠utula i̠wo̠l d̠a̠ a̠ken emite?’\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, ‘O̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien a̠gir o̠ku̠a.’ \wj* 
\p \wj “Sa̠ aru̠bana bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘I̠yar o̠gi̠ ka̠ ob̠ugion o̠si̠ghe̠gi̠ ke̠re̠?’\wj* 
\p  
\v 29 \wj “Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘E̠e̠nyi̠, bo̠ka̠ inyin u̠b̠aram na̠ i̠bu̠kpa bho̠ ob̠ugion na̠ ib̠utula bho̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Ima̠ra̠ i̠wal a̠yi e̠su̠ emum itu. Sa̠ d̠a̠ igiel ob̠u ed̠ia̠n bho̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠ruom ogbo ob̠u ed̠ia̠n bho̠, ma̠ ed̠ia̠ eb̠ugion ib̠utula bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ to okokod̠i o̠gho̠ro̠gi̠ o̠bhu̠gi̠ orobh. Ya̠a̠ ta̠ okokod̠i ma̠ i̠bu̠kpa bho̠ okpol d̠a̠ esi eko d̠ami̠.’ ”\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh Ekpo Amu̠stad bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 4:30-32; A̠luk 13:18-19) 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh opa̠n a̠sidogh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Irileghom ote̠nai̠ny agu̠b̠an ekpo amu̠stad ola̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin a̠gbebh d̠a̠ o̠si̠ d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj Eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na aki̠r a̠pu d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ikpo ya̠ na̠ ogbebh bho̠ eka̠, igiel na̠ asu̠ abu̠gh, bha̠ abu̠gh a̠pu ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠gho̠gho̠ a̠mobobh na̠ e̠su̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ bho̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠ten oriren, ma̠ ola̠ i̠nu̠r anyu̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ elo ma̠ a̠rutu d̠a̠ i̠gha bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh A̠yist bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 13:20-21) 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ i̠na a̠rogh opa̠n a̠sidogh ma̠a̠, \wj “Irileghom ote̠nai̠ny agu̠b̠an o̠nyi̠ki̠kara a̠yist ya̠ ani̠ebhom a̠bhin alo̠gh d̠a̠ o̠to̠ma̠ i̠sar-abafu̠ ed̠ia̠n ibhugh, sa̠ iwubhmeni ma̠ eb̠la̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Ezin wa̠ A̠zizo̠s A̠rughom Ra̠sid̠ogh bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 4:33-34) 
\p  
\v 34 A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠sidogh a̠fugh eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠. Sa̠ bebina̠ abar ola̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ola̠ i̠na obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠sidogh a̠fugh na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.  
\v 35 O̠ku̠a bho̠ i̠nye̠n imuzoghod̠iom abar wa̠ owil bho̠ a̠wa̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: 
\q1 “Ami̠ ta̠ akpato̠n o̠nu̠ d̠ami̠ a̠rogh ra̠sidogh, 
\q2 sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ agba ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na a̠mutiom, ka̠ d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠.”\f + \fr 13:35 \ft \xt Raso̠r 78:2\f* 
\s1 Ezin A̠sidogh Ib̠utula bho̠ 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠gbogion a̠kokod̠ia̠n bho̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na ifugh ma̠a̠, “Gba ma̠ ezin a̠sidogh ib̠utula ya̠ d̠a̠ o̠si̠ bho̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar.” 
\p  
\v 37 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠gbebh ib̠eb̠i ikpo ed̠ia̠n bho̠ bha̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj O̠si̠ bho̠ bha̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, ib̠eb̠i ikpo bho̠ bha̠ anwi̠i̠ny irileghom bho̠, ya̠a̠ ib̠utula bho̠ bha̠ anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ o̠karabh o̠ni̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 39 \wj Sa̠ o̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien wa̠ a̠gbebh ib̠utula̠ bho̠ bha̠ eru bho̠. Ib̠ua̠ bho̠ bha̠ ekunuguma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ ogbo ob̠u bho̠ bha̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 40 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, agu̠o̠ ta̠ ob̠ugion ib̠utula bho̠ okokod̠i o̠bhu̠gi̠ bho̠, obha̠ bha̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom.\wj* 
\v 41 \wj O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠ruom itileduom d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ta̠ e̠si̠ghe̠gi̠ d̠a̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠kpo̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠le̠ge̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ ogir i̠karabh bho̠, na̠ eb̠la̠ idighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠.\wj* 
\v 42 \wj Sa̠ ta̠ erobhod̠i awa e̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠ba anya bho̠, d̠a̠ esi wa̠ ed̠i na̠ o̠ghi̠r ib̠ub̠ura̠ od̠i bho̠.\wj* 
\v 43 \wj Igiel obha̠, ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom bho̠ ta̠ e̠war agu̠o̠ ogogo bho̠ d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠awa. Wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ra̠to, amar anagha o!\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh E̠wo̠gi̠na I̠di̠ar Edim 
\p  
\v 44 \wj “Irileghom ote̠nai̠ny agu̠b̠an i̠di̠ar edim ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na d̠a̠ o̠si̠ ma̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ agi̠ ka̠ abi̠gh, sa̠ a̠puta̠ awo̠gi̠. Sa̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ ibo bho̠, sa̠ ad̠u̠a ka̠ a̠wol eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin a̠gho ma̠ egbolom o̠si̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 45 \wj “O̠lo̠gho̠m i̠se̠, irileghom ote̠nai̠ny agu̠b̠an o̠ni̠ a̠b̠ua̠ ola̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a ma̠ esi na̠ a̠ten esi na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan ib̠eb̠i i̠b̠o̠lo̠.\wj* 
\v 46 \wj Sa̠ ka̠ abi̠gh odi o̠b̠o̠lo̠ obom a̠b̠ua̠, sa̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠wol eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠bhin a̠gho ma̠ o̠b̠o̠lo̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh O̠gbo̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 47 \wj “O̠lo̠gho̠m i̠se̠, irileghom ote̠nai̠ny agu̠b̠an o̠gbo̠ ola̠ usoroni d̠a̠ abadi̠ sa̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere ina̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ isin.\wj* 
\v 48 \wj Igiel bho̠ ina̠ bho̠ isin o̠gbo̠ bho̠ imuzo bho̠, sa̠ i̠ku̠mi̠ku̠ bho̠ ikpor o̠gbo̠ bho̠ ibhuneni d̠a̠ egbolom, sa̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de i̠so̠n ib̠eb̠i i̠na bho̠ i̠lo̠gi̠ d̠a̠ egunu, ya̠a̠ i̠karabh bho̠, sa̠ awa irobhod̠i.\wj* 
\v 49 \wj Obha̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠. Itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ e̠so̠n id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ib̠eb̠i bho̠,\wj* 
\v 50 \wj sa̠ ta̠ erobhodi awa e̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠ba anya bho̠, d̠a̠ esi wa̠ ed̠i na̠ o̠ghi̠r ib̠ub̠ura̠ od̠i bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 51 \wj “Inyin o̠mu̠gho̠nyan eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ke̠re̠?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Yii.” 
\p  
\v 52 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠ ola̠ ada ma̠ atu̠ghan irileghom ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ a̠bhin, bha̠ agu̠b̠an o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠, sa̠ a̠mutioghom imom na̠ igba̠iny i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na alo̠gi̠ a̠guri d̠a̠ igba̠ i̠d̠i̠ar edim d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Owil Ogboe̠ma na̠ Olei d̠o̠ ma̠ Abar 
\r (Amaki̠ 6:1-6; A̠luk 4:16-30) 
\p  
\v 53 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ ma̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rogh a̠sidogh i̠nye̠n awe̠le̠ bho̠.  
\v 54 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa d̠a̠ u̠gala d̠awa, ma̠ ola̠ awa ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠. Sa̠ awa na̠ epupura̠n ma̠a̠, “Eloghom abar onon na̠ a̠d̠ien ilologia̠n i̠nye̠n ka̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠ken eru?”  
\v 55 “Onon O̠nyi̠ ta̠ o̠du̠gi̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠? Oweni d̠o̠yo̠ ubhelegi d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠meri ke̠re̠? Sa̠ a̠rumor d̠o̠yo̠ bha̠ A̠zemsi na̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ na̠ Asai̠mo̠n na̠ A̠zud d̠o̠ ke̠re̠?  
\v 56 Eb̠la̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bo̠ na̠ i̠yar i̠se̠n ke̠re̠? O̠ku̠a ka̠ eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠ken eru?”  
\v 57 Sa̠ rologi d̠awa igurom d̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠yo̠. 
\p Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ubhin d̠o̠ ma̠ owil o̠tu̠o̠m abar d̠a̠ e̠ma d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ eghun otu wa̠ i̠na a̠mite bho̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 58 Ebula̠ agu̠o̠ awa od̠umom d̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ogir d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠izo ilologia̠n i̠se̠. 
\c 14  
\s1 Omugh ta̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 6:14-29; A̠luk 9:7-9) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ E̠ro̠d we̠mu̠ irileghom odi agba ebhugh\f + \fr 14:1 \ft E̠ro̠d aro̠ ma̠ we̠mu̠ irileghom odi agba d̠a̠ inya̠ a̠bin d̠a̠ ebhugh Izre̠l.\f* bho̠, amu̠gho̠n o̠du̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠,  
\v 2 sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Onon ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠; i̠na na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh! Obha̠ ezin bho̠ ra̠limon i̠nye̠n na̠ i̠kpasan i̠na bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 3 Ezin bho̠ E̠ro̠d a̠b̠ol Azo̠n, sa̠ adu̠o̠m d̠a̠ ikoli ma̠ ebula̠ E̠ro̠di̠as ani̠ ta̠ A̠filip umor d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 4 Ezin bho̠ Azo̠n a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠: “Na̠ osora̠n d̠o̠ nyam ma̠ obhin E̠ro̠di̠as ani̠.”  
\v 5 Sa̠ E̠ro̠d abho̠ro̠gh ogigh Azo̠n, ya̠a̠ i̠na a̠ghil a̠nwunom bho̠, ezin bho̠ awa eloghom ma̠ Azo̠n owil. 
\p  
\v 6 D̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ e̠yal i̠mara ta̠ E̠ro̠d, sa̠ o̠nyani̠ ta̠ E̠ro̠di̠as aghe̠r d̠a̠ a̠misigh ogbo o̠d̠e̠ bho̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠d̠igh ologi ma̠ E̠ro̠d.  
\v 7 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ E̠ro̠d a̠sibhigha̠ a̠gua̠n onigha̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ kere kere abar ola̠ ta̠ a̠puru i̠na.  
\v 8 Sa̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠pura̠n onweni d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠puru bho̠, sa̠ oweni d̠o̠yo̠ a̠ruom i̠na ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠gba onigha̠ E̠ro̠d ma̠a̠, “Nigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n i̠se̠n e̠mu̠ ta̠ Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠kpa imobh.”  
\v 9 Sa̠ o̠li̠le̠ma bho̠ a̠b̠ogina̠, ya̠a̠ ebula̠ i̠zo̠ bho̠ na̠ ogbo o̠d̠e̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom awa ma̠ onigha̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ i̠na a̠puru bho̠.  
\v 10 Sa̠ i̠na ato̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ osobh e̠mu̠ ta̠ Azo̠n d̠a̠ ologi ikoli bho̠.  
\v 11 Sa̠ awa irol e̠mu̠ bho̠ d̠a̠ e̠kpa imobh ra̠ inigha̠ ma̠ o̠gbara o̠nyani̠ bho̠, sa̠ o̠nyani̠ bho̠ a̠bhin ka̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 12 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ Azo̠n i̠gi̠ ka̠ irol ekuna̠ bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a ka̠ id̠i, sa̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠gba inigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠nigha̠ ma̠ Ed̠ia̠n ma̠  //  D̠iobh na̠ I̠wal O̠ni̠r na̠ Ogho E̠wala (5,000) O̠ni̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 6:30-44; A̠luk 9:10-17; Azo̠n 6:1-14) 
\p  
\v 13 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s amu̠gho̠n abar wa̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ Azo̠n bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ku̠ku̠m a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh sa̠ ad̠u̠a agi̠ ma̠ esi ola̠ aro̠ kukunum. Sa̠ agu̠o̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ re̠ma d̠awa i̠wo̠l ya̠ a̠wel i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na.  
\v 14 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠bhun d̠a̠ egbolom bho̠, sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom sa̠ igbirigbir awa id̠ighi i̠na, sa̠ a̠koko ma̠ ogbo asu̠nwe̠r ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh bho̠. 
\p  
\v 15 Igiel bho̠ a̠d̠io na̠ ate̠i̠ a̠dule bho̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ iru ra̠ ifugh inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Onon esi ola̠ od̠i kukunum, ya̠a̠ obhel na̠ a̠ten. Ruome ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ e̠d̠u̠a e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma bho̠ ka̠ eghoyogh ed̠ia̠n ya̠ awa ta̠ ed̠e.” 
\p  
\v 16 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Na̠ osora̠n d̠o̠ awa ma̠ o̠d̠u̠a. Inigha̠ awa ma̠ abar od̠e.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠yar unwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar esi onon, a̠ten ogho ikpokpogh abre̠di̠ na̠ i̠wal ikpo ina̠.” 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Ibhine ma̠ eru ma̠ i̠se̠n.”\wj* 
\v 19 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ i̠gho̠gho̠ bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin ogho ikpokpogh abre̠di̠ bho̠ na̠ i̠wal ikpo ina̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠b̠eka̠ a̠kpon d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠tutumeni ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠. Sa̠ i̠na a̠pupugion a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠ru̠gi̠ iinigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 20 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa id̠e, sa̠ ilegha̠n ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠, sa̠ ikokod̠i ma̠ i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r ya̠ isughia̠n bho̠ imuzoghod̠i d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal (12) a̠rukpuom.  
\v 21 Aro̠ ka̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala (5,000) ilobhiri a̠nwunom id̠e. U̠wal ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ anwani̠ na̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny ya̠ id̠e ani̠ bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠rile d̠a̠ Anyu̠ Amu̠m 
\r (Amaki̠ 6:45-52; Azo̠n 6:15-21) 
\p  
\v 22 D̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠nugi ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh ed̠ia̠ eb̠etina̠ na̠ i̠na i̠b̠e̠i̠y d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na ta̠ aro̠ a̠b̠a̠ra̠ tu̠tu̠n ka̠ i̠na na̠ a̠ruom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ oyeleghu o̠mado̠n.  
\v 23 Igiel bho̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ eyeleghu bho̠, sa̠ i̠na asi̠n d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu ka̠ a̠siseiny tu̠tu̠n a̠d̠io a̠kpegi, sa̠ i̠na ku̠ku̠m aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.  
\v 24 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, oghugh bho̠ na̠ agi̠ ma̠ egbeiny d̠a̠ obodo bho̠, sa̠ opoka̠n amu̠m bho̠ na̠ a̠b̠oroghom awa, ezin bho̠ ogim bho̠ na̠ a̠gim na̠ adama awa. 
\p  
\v 25 Igiel bho̠ ate̠i̠ obhel ogir wa̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠\f + \fr 14:25 \fq Obhel ogir wa̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠ \ft Ob̠eton d̠a̠ i̠sar ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ odin aki̠lo̠ki̠ ma̠ ame̠ghe̠le̠. Idi ogbo na̠ eb̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ asi̠ro̠, idi etita̠n, idi a̠d̠uga̠la̠n. \f* bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠rile d̠a̠ anyu̠ amu̠m agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ awa.  
\v 26 Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠bi̠gh agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠rile d̠a̠ anyu̠ amu̠m bho̠, sa̠ rologi d̠awa ikpoyogh, sa̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, “Obha̠ e̠mu̠gh o,” sa̠ ikpo ma̠ izul d̠a̠ ebula̠ a̠rugugu. 
\p  
\v 27 Ogbo na̠ onin, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠kpo̠ ma̠ ologi. O̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu. Ami̠!”\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, ku̠gba ma̠ anwa na̠ agu̠o̠ ga̠i, bha̠ ruome ami̠ ma̠ orile d̠a̠ anyu̠ amu̠m bho̠ oru d̠oyom.”  
\v 29 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Tue.”\wj* Sa̠ A̠pita̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠ a̠sor a̠rile d̠a̠ anyu̠ amu̠m bho̠ na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 30 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na abi̠gh e̠mi̠ ogim bho̠, sa̠ a̠rugugu isibh i̠na, sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ od̠in, sa̠ i̠na a̠mulughu a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, tenemeni ami̠.”  
\v 31 Ogbo na̠ onin, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠o̠m agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠sibh i̠na sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠ghu̠a d̠o̠, ologi d̠oyom na̠ a̠kpo ma̠ ere?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 32 Sa̠ i̠wal awa ipel id̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠, sa̠ ogim bho̠ a̠lia̠. 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ oghugh bho̠ ikpud̠ia̠n inigha̠ i̠na d̠a̠ ozuruna̠ eghoi, sa̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, anwa O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.”  
\v 34 Sa̠ awa i̠b̠e̠i̠ ka̠ isul d̠a̠ Age̠ne̠sare̠t.  
\v 35 Sa̠ a̠nwunom e̠ma bho̠ ilelegi i̠na, sa̠ iruom ka̠ obhinogh eb̠la̠ ogbo asu̠nwe̠r d̠a̠ eghighira̠ bho̠ oru d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 36 Sa̠ awa i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠a̠ i̠na a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ ogbo asu̠nwe̠r bho̠ ma̠ okula̠n bebina̠ esi bho̠ u̠labh akapa d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ ikula̠n bho̠ id̠um i̠man. 
\c 15  
\s1 I̠to̠to̠gi̠ Od̠ud̠ul 
\r (Amaki̠ 7:1-13) 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠, sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m i̠gi̠ ka̠ ipura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠,  
\v 2 “Ezin ka̠ ere ka̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ od̠ud̠ul ibom ro̠we̠de̠ bho̠? Awa ititila̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa kisa̠ na̠ ed̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n!” 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠a̠, inyin eka̠ ka̠ inyin na̠ odin ere na̠ obhin d̠a̠ od̠ud̠ul d̠inyin na̠ okpon oloko ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠?\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Ezin bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘Zuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi a̠nigha̠ ma̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom’\wj*\f + \fr 15:4 \ft \xt E̠d̠u̠a 20:12\ft ; \xt Oloko 5:16\f*\wj sa̠ ‘O̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠fugh i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠ bo̠d̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠, ta̠ ogigh.’\wj*\f + \fr 15:4 \ft \xt E̠d̠u̠a 21:17\ft ; \xt I̠to̠t 20:9\f* 
\v 5 \wj Ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, o̠kpe̠ bo̠ ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ onweni d̠o̠yo̠, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na ka̠ ibhin alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠ ma̠ iya̠ A̠zib̠a̠. \wj* 
\v 6 \wj Sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ozuruna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ eghoi a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠o̠yo̠. O̠ku̠a bha̠ inyin na̠ ogbogion oloko ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m ratu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠inyin.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Inyin ibhelebhel! A̠sora̠n ga̠i ya̠ Azaya a̠wa̠ a̠gboloma̠ inyin bho̠ ma̠a̠,\wj* 
\q1  
\v 8 \wj “ ‘A̠nwunom i̠nye̠n na̠ ebhin aru̠nu̠ d̠awa na̠ ebuom ami̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj ya̠a̠ rologi d̠awa isigima̠ ami̠.\wj* 
\q1  
\v 9 \wj Awa na̠ e̠ko̠l ami̠ ma̠ obhubho i̠kpo̠, \wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ agu̠o̠ roloko ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.’ ”\wj*\f + \fr 15:9 \ft \xt Azaya 29:13\f* 
\s1 I̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ na̠ E̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ O̠ni̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 7:14-23) 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ i̠na a̠kokod̠i ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠nagha, ma̠ e̠mu̠gho̠nyan o!\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Abar wa̠ na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ d̠o̠, ma̠ wa̠ na̠ api̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ abar wa̠ na̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ bho̠ na̠ api̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 12 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ iru ra̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa a̠loghom ma̠a̠ rologi Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ egurom ma̠ igiel bho̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠nye̠n bho̠ ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Kere kere oriren ola̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny ogbebh d̠o̠, ta̠ ob̠uron.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj I̠we̠le̠mane̠ awa, ogbo ya̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi na̠ erileghom ogbo ya̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi. Sa̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi a̠rileghom o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ esi, i̠wal awa ta̠ emel ed̠igh d̠a̠ ogugua̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 15 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Gba ma̠ ezin a̠sidogh onon asi̠se̠ghe̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar.” 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠se̠n eka̠ bha̠ inyin ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ nyen ke̠re̠?”\wj* 
\v 17 \wj “Inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠a̠, kere kere abar ola̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ na̠ awo̠l d̠a̠ okurogh, sa̠ na̠ a̠tenegia̠n ati̠n ma̠ ola̠ na̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ orobh ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ya̠a̠, i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ na̠ emite bho̠, i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ekpo ologi bho̠ emite eru, i̠ye̠ bha̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ezin bho̠, d̠a̠ ekpo ologi bho̠, bha̠ esi i̠karabh i̠ru̠ru̠an ya̠ ogigh o̠ni̠, na̠ orile isorogi,\wj*\f + \fr 15:19 \fq Orile isorogi \ft A̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ilom ya̠ na̠ e̠gi̠ ma̠ ari̠gi̠. \f*\wj od̠e e̠ma, ob̠igh a̠b̠igh, o̠gba onyob̠a̠ igunugha̠, o̠gba o̠ni̠ o̠pi̠e̠ na̠ emite na̠ eru bho̠.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj I̠nye̠n bha̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠pi̠e̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠we̠le̠man otitila̠ agu̠o̠ kisa̠ od̠e ed̠ia̠n na̠ o̠pi̠e̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Ologi Ima̠ra̠ Ani̠ A̠kenan bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 7:24-30) 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ agba Ataya na̠ Asi̠do̠n.  
\v 22 I̠se̠ sa̠ ani̠ ola̠ ebhugh A̠kenan a̠mite a̠ru ra̠ a̠leghe ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, kpone ami̠ ma̠ igbirigbir! Eru na̠ ab̠am o̠nyani̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠ o̠kparakpar agu̠o̠.” 
\p  
\v 23 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s na̠ o̠wo̠ran d̠o̠ i̠na bebina̠ abar. Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ iru ra̠ i̠le̠gh i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ze i̠na ma̠ asi̠ghe̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ a̠leghe na̠ atu̠o̠no̠m i̠yar.” 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ani̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Uruom d̠o̠ ami̠ ma̠ o̠tu̠n ipa̠n ogbo oru, ya̠a̠ uruom ami̠ ma̠ oru d̠a̠ ro̠nana ya̠ na̠ ebhe bho̠, d̠a̠ a̠nwunom Izre̠l.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 25 Sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n a̠nigha̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, lo̠ghe̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ami̠.” 
\p  
\v 26 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Na̠ osora̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ orobh ed̠ia̠n i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ onigha̠ a̠sib̠ogho.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ga̠i, Wa̠nwuna̠. Ya̠a̠, anwi̠i̠ny a̠sib̠ogho bho̠ eka̠ na̠ ed̠e ma̠ i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r ya̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ akpata od̠e ta̠ wa̠nwuna̠ awa na̠ emeleghu bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 28 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Ani̠ bho̠, alu̠bu̠gh ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom! A̠mite ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠gh bho̠.”\wj* Sa̠ o̠nyani̠ ani̠ bho̠ a̠d̠um epa̠ d̠a̠ ogbo obhel obha̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠koko ma̠ A̠d̠izo A̠nwunom 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ aka abadi̠ Agalili sa̠ asi̠n d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de.  
\v 30 Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom iru d̠o̠yo̠. Awa i̠b̠ar na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠ikighu ma̠ re̠gha, ogbo ikpom a̠rid̠ien, a̠rukula̠, remua̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nwe̠re̠ghu̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere a̠d̠izo rasu̠nwe̠r ka̠ iguri d̠a̠ aka a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠koko awa.  
\v 31 Sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ awa i̠bi̠gh bho̠. Remua̠ bho̠ na̠ efugh a̠fugh, ogbo ya̠ na̠ eb̠ogina̠ bho̠ na̠ okoko od̠umeni, sa̠ a̠rukula̠ bho̠ na̠ erile, sa̠ a̠nwunom ikpom a̠rid̠ien bho̠ na̠ e̠bi̠gh esi. Sa̠ awa itutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Izre̠l. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠nigha̠ ma̠ D̠iobh O̠ni̠r (4,000) A̠nwunom Ed̠ia̠n 
\r (Amaki̠ 8:1-10) 
\p  
\v 32 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kokod̠i ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Igbirigbir o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ ed̠ighi ami̠. Ezin bho̠ onon oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ na̠ e̠ro̠ na̠ ami̠ sa̠ bebina̠ abar ola̠ ta̠ ed̠e bo̠. Ya̠a̠, ami̠ i̠bho̠ro̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ oruom awa ta̠ eyel o̠ko̠i̠, b̠o̠ka̠ awa i̠fu̠mu̠ d̠a̠ eten bho̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ a̠ken ikpokpogh abre̠di̠ ya̠ ta̠ elei onigha̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠nye̠n, d̠a̠ esi ola̠ od̠i kukunum o̠ko̠no̠n?” 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin unwuna̠ i̠ni̠ ikpokpogh abre̠di̠?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Od̠ua̠l ikpokpogh abre̠di̠, na̠ o̠nyi̠ki̠kara i̠gbara ikpo ina̠.” 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ awa e̠ro̠ ma̠a̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ a̠de.  
\v 36 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin od̠ua̠l ikpogh abre̠di̠ bho̠ na̠ ina̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ali̠se̠bh A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠pupugion a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ogir bho̠ ma̠ o̠ru̠gi̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠.  
\v 37 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa id̠e ilegha̠n, sa̠ ikpokpo ma̠ i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r ya̠ isughia̠n bho̠ i̠lo̠gi̠ imuzoghod̠i ma̠ od̠ua̠l a̠rukpuom.  
\v 38 Ogbo ya̠ id̠e ma̠ abre̠di̠ bho̠, bha̠ d̠iobh o̠ni̠r (4,000) ilobhiri. U̠wal ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ranwani̠ na̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny.  
\v 39 Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ oten oyeleghu, sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ oghugh agi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh Amagadan. 
\c 16  
\s1 Rafarisi na̠ Rasadusi Ipuru ma̠ Elegh d̠a̠ Agu̠o̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 8:11-13; A̠luk 12:54-56) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ Rasadusi bho̠ iru ra̠ o̠d̠a A̠zizo̠s okpon, sa̠ ipuru ma̠ i̠na a̠leriom awa ma̠ elegh d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny. 
\p  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Igiel o̠b̠u̠ghu̠bu̠gh bho̠ ab̠am agu̠o̠ ododo ma̠ a̠dule, sa̠ inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘E̠mu̠ a̠d̠io bho̠ ta̠ a̠bhon.’\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Ya̠a̠ ka̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ ab̠am agu̠o̠ ododo sa̠ ade̠bh ad̠i̠ro̠, sa̠ inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘E̠mu̠ a̠d̠io bho̠ ko obhon d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠didon.’ Inyin na̠ orue na̠ obhin o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ na̠ ologhom agu̠o̠ e̠mu̠ a̠d̠io bho̠ ta̠ aro̠, ya̠a̠ inyin urue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan elegh wa̠ robhel ekunuguma̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Amu̠m i̠basi̠ ola̠ oghila̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ a̠puru ma̠ oleriom o̠yo̠ ma̠ elegh, ya̠a̠ elegh ola̠ ta̠ oleriom bo̠, a̠ten elegh ta̠ A̠zona̠.”\wj* Sa̠ i̠na awe̠le̠ awa a̠ten ad̠u̠a. 
\s1 A̠yist ta̠ Rafarisi na̠ Rasadusi bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 8:14-21) 
\p  
\v 5 Igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ na̠ i̠b̠e̠i̠y d̠a̠ aku̠b̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ awa iloghoma̠n ma̠a̠ awa na̠ eweletia̠n o̠b̠ar na̠ abre̠di̠ obhin o̠gi̠. 
\p  
\v 6 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kikiom awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ilelegi, ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ a̠yist ta̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ Rasadusi bho̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ awa ibhin a̠kikiom bho̠ id̠ighom d̠a̠ i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an ma̠a̠, “Agu̠o̠ i̠yar obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ abre̠di̠ oru bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 8 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s amu̠gho̠nyan abar wa̠ awa na̠ e̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an bho̠, sa̠ agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ogbo ya̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠ghu̠a d̠o̠! Inyin udin ere na̠ o̠ku̠anan na̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ abre̠di̠ bho̠?\wj* 
\v 9 \wj I̠se̠n eka̠ bha̠ inyin ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠, bo̠d̠o̠ inyin urue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an, ma̠ o̠nu̠ o̠wal a̠rukpuom i̠pe̠re̠pe̠r abre̠di̠ ya̠ ipel d̠a̠ ogho ikpokpogh abre̠di̠ ya̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠r na̠ ogho e̠wala (5,000) a̠nwunom id̠e bho̠, ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Bo̠d̠o̠ o̠nu̠ o̠wal a̠rukpuom ya̠ u̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ od̠ua̠l ikpokpogh abre̠di̠ ya̠ d̠iobh o̠ni̠r (4,000) a̠nwunom id̠e sa̠ ipel bho̠ ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Eka̠ ma̠ ola̠ inyin o̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ ami̠ ifugh d̠o̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ abre̠di̠? Ya̠a̠ ikpona̠ ma̠ a̠yist Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ Rasadusi bho̠!”\wj* 
\v 12 I̠se̠ kisa̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠nyan ma̠a̠, i̠na na̠ ofugh d̠o̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠yist abre̠di̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ta̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ Rasadusi bho̠. 
\s1 A̠puta̠ Agba ma̠ A̠zizo̠s A̠mutiom 
\r (Amaki̠ 8:27-30; A̠luk 9:18-21) 
\p  
\v 13 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ d̠a̠ ebhugh A̠sizeria̠ d̠a̠ A̠filipai̠, sa̠ a̠pura̠n ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠nwunom na̠ e̠gba ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ka̠ a̠nyen?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Idi na̠ e̠gba ma̠ anwa Azo̠n Owurmamu̠m bho̠, ipa̠n sa̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ anwa I̠lai̠za, ipa̠n ogbo sa̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ anwa A̠zerimaya, bo̠d̠o̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ awa a̠riwil bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 15 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠ ami̠ ka̠ a̠nyen?” \wj* 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ Asai̠mo̠n A̠pita̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Anwa Akrai̠st, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “E̠b̠e̠l oyom Asai̠mo̠n, o̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zona̠. Ipulupul na̠ asi̠ i̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠wo̠gi̠na onon emutiom enigha̠ nyam, ya̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Sa̠ ami̠ na̠ ka̠ ab̠aram na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, anwa A̠pita̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠lo ma̠ aso̠si̠ d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ o̠gbe̠o̠ma onon, sa̠ ra̠limon a̠d̠ugh ko orue d̠o̠ e̠ne̠gi̠me̠ni̠ i̠na.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ami̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ri̠sabi̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny, sa̠ kere kere abar ola̠ anwa i̠bhad̠i̠ d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠ na̠ o̠bhad̠i̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny, sa̠ ola̠ anwa i̠ko̠gi̠o̠n d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠, na̠ o̠ko̠gi̠o̠n d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny.”\wj* 
\v 20 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠ sa̠ i̠na aghaghana ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ma̠ awa o̠gba d̠o̠ enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠na Akrai̠st bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ A̠gboloma̠ ma̠ Omugh D̠o̠yo̠  //  Na̠ Ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ Omugh D̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 8:31—9:1; A̠luk 9:22-27) 
\p  
\v 21 Ob̠eton d̠a̠ igiel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ake̠ ma̠ o̠gba o̠se̠ghe̠ni̠ inigha̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ akpe̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, ka̠ o̠bi̠gh a̠d̠izo ali̠gam a̠ruzu d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ ikei bho̠, na̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ ogbo-atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, sa̠ awa ta̠ egigh I̠na, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠.  
\v 22 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠bhin i̠na a̠ten d̠a̠ aka, sa̠ a̠bhin o̠gagaman okoroko a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, ko ofugh o̠ku̠a. A̠zib̠a̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ e̠tu̠tu̠! Abar ola̠ o̠ku̠a omutuma̠ d̠o̠ nyam!”  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na a̠tiba̠ra̠ awo̠ran A̠pita̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Eru, tene d̠a̠ aman d̠ami̠! Anwa na̠ ad̠agi̠an ka̠ ami̠, ezin bho̠ anwa na̠ obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ atu̠o̠m abar, ya̠a̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠.”\wj* 
\v 24 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ e̠ral o̠tu̠o̠no̠m ami̠, a̠ghel ozu d̠o̠yo̠, a̠rol e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren d̠o̠yo̠, atu̠o̠no̠m ami̠.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj O̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh otenemeni a̠ghud̠um e̠mara̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ta̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ atu̠n ami̠ a̠robh a̠ghud̠um e̠mara̠nwunom d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Ya̠a̠ a̠kere asu̠o̠, wa̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ ate̠i̠ ka̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, a̠dinom a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠? Bo̠d̠o̠, ka̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ere aru̠r a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠?\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Ezin bho̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ a̠ru na̠ isosorogia̠n ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠, seki̠na̠ itileduom d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ta̠ akpe̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ i̠se̠ ma̠ ya̠ ilegha̠n ya̠ i̠na a̠gir bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ akparame̠ni̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, idi inyin ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠, ka̠ omugh d̠o̠ tu̠tu̠n ta̠ e̠bi̠gh eruoma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ d̠a̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠.”\wj* 
\c 17  
\s1 Onwegina̠ Ozu ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 9:2-13; A̠luk 9:28-36) 
\p  
\v 1 Odin a̠d̠a̠ma̠ iten, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin A̠pita̠, na̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n umor d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ a̠bhin awa a̠bhun d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu esi ola̠ awa ku̠ku̠m i̠ro̠. 
\p  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na a̠nwegina̠ ma̠ ozu d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠awa, sa̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠ amu̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogogo bho̠, sa̠ ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠ i̠war agu̠o̠ e̠b̠alab̠al.  
\v 3 Sa̠ A̠mozizi na̠ I̠lai̠za imite d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠awa na̠ e̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an i̠na. 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, ya̠ a̠bhon agu̠o̠ i̠yar od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n bho̠! Ku̠gba ma̠ ta̠ a̠sora̠n bha̠, d̠ighi ami̠ igim i̠sar a̠rutu akpu̠ru̠ ma̠ esi onon: odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ oyom, ya̠a̠ odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ A̠mozizi, sa̠ odi ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ I̠lai̠za.” 
\p  
\v 5 I̠na od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ a̠fugh, sa̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ a̠kpegiom awa. Sa̠ okoroko ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠ a̠si a̠mite ma̠a̠, “Onon O̠nyi̠ etula̠n d̠ami̠, wa̠ na̠ a̠gir ya̠ na̠ ed̠igh ami̠ ma̠ ologi bho̠. I̠nagha i̠na!” 
\p  
\v 6 Sa̠ igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n okoroko bho̠, sa̠ ibom a̠rugugu isibh awa, sa̠ imel ib̠obhia̠n.  
\v 7 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ru ra̠ a̠kula̠n awa a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ib̠egina̠, o̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu.”\wj* 
\v 8 Sa̠ awa ib̠egion ra̠misigh d̠awa, ya̠a̠ i̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ a̠ten i̠na A̠zizo̠s ku̠ku̠m. 
\p  
\v 9 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ awa na̠ esor d̠a̠ igu bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s anyagh ra̠to d̠awa agba ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ ko o̠gba ma̠ aghi̠m bho̠ ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, tu̠tu̠n O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ i̠tu̠n ere na̠ e̠gba ma̠ I̠lai̠za ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ a̠ru?” 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠lai̠za ta̠ a̠ru ga̠i, sa̠ ta̠ atu̠ghu̠man eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ya̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠ I̠lai̠za na̠ a̠ru a̠ten, ya̠a̠ a̠nwunom ilelegi d̠o̠ i̠na, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, awa irughom i̠na ma̠ iya̠ awa i̠to̠ d̠a̠ rologi d̠awa. Obha̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n nyen O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ma̠ ogbika̠ d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa.”\wj* 
\v 13 I̠se̠ kisa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠nyan ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠na a̠fugh na̠ a̠gboloma̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ awa bho̠ ma̠ Azo̠n owurmamu̠m bho̠. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠koko ma̠ O̠nyi̠ Ola̠ O̠karabh E̠mu̠gh na̠ A̠nyegi 
\r (Amaki̠ 9:14-29; A̠luk 9:37-43) 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ awa iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠ru d̠o̠yo̠ ra̠ a̠kpuluma̠n a̠nigha̠ i̠na.  
\v 15 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, kpone ma̠ igbirigbir o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠, ezin bho̠ i̠na na̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ena̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠nyegi i̠na. A̠d̠izo robhel na̠ a̠robh i̠na na̠ alo̠gh d̠a̠ anya, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ amu̠m.  
\v 16 Sa̠ ami̠ ibhin i̠na iruom ogbo atu̠ghan d̠oyom, ya̠a̠ awa irue d̠o̠ ma̠ okoko o̠yo̠.” 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Sei, amu̠m ola̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ o̠to̠, ya̠ na̠ erugh ado̠l i̠te̠i̠! Ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ na̠ inyin a̠bia̠ eka̠? Ami̠ ta̠ a̠ne ma̠ ado̠l d̠inyin ka̠ ate̠i̠ eka̠? Ibhine ma̠ o̠nyi̠ bho̠ ma̠ eruom ami̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n.”\wj* 
\v 18 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s ab̠ab̠agi̠na ma̠ o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠, sa̠ a̠mite ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ozu o̠nyi̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠um epa̠ ma̠ onin obhel obha̠. 
\p  
\v 19 I̠se̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ iru ra̠ ipura̠n A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ a̠d̠ukun ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere ma̠ ola̠ i̠yar orue d̠o̠ ma̠ oze o̠karabh e̠mu̠gh bho̠ o̠si̠ghe̠?” 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ezin bho̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin ta̠ o̠ghu̠a d̠o̠. Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ akparame̠ni̠ na̠ agba ma̠a̠, ka̠ inyin u̠te̠i̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ola̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ ekpo oriren amu̠stad sa̠ inyin ufugh unigha̠ ma̠ igu onon ma̠a̠, ‘B̠etina̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ebha̠,’ sa̠ ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠. Abar ola̠ ta̠ akpar a̠pu inyin ogir ka̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠.”\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Ya̠a̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ a̠siseiny na̠ one o̠ko̠i̠ bo̠d̠o̠, ola̠ o̠ko̠no̠n ko orue d̠o̠ ad̠u̠a.\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠mula̠ A̠wa̠ A̠gboloma̠ ma̠ Omugh D̠o̠yo̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 9:30-32; A̠luk 9:43-45) 
\p  
\v 22 D̠a̠ igiel bho̠ awa inwe ikokod̠ia̠n d̠a̠ Agalili bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Na̠ a̠tua̠n igiel ta̠ owol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ob̠eton o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de a̠limon.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Sa̠ awa ta̠ egigh i̠na, sa̠ d̠a̠ a̠bin i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh.”\wj* Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ id̠igh ibom i̠ku̠nu̠. 
\s1 Otua̠ otua̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ awa id̠igh d̠a̠ Akapanu̠m bho̠, sa̠ igunmotua̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ A̠pita̠ ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠inyin na̠ a̠tua̠gha̠n otua̠ okpoki i̠wal e̠mu̠ a̠d̠uma̠ ogir \f + \fr 17:24 \ft Okpoki i̠wal-e̠mu̠ a̠d̠uma̠ ogir, bha̠ otua̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom Izire̠l ya̠ na̠ ed̠igh e̠mu̠ bho̠, na̠ etua̠ gha̠n. Na̠ ebhin ikpoki otua̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠man Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m. Ubhelegi ma̠ okpoki onon ma̠a̠, i̠wal-adrakma d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ A̠grik.\f*bho̠ ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 25 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Yii,” i̠na na̠ akpe̠, ya̠a̠ igiel i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ologi otu bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awalama a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Asai̠mo̠n, anwa i̠bi̠gh eka̠? Aru̠lala e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ esobh otua̠ na̠ enigha̠ ma̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠awa ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ na̠ egun d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ risoloma̠?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 26 Sa̠ A̠puta̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “D̠a̠ agu̠o̠ risoloma̠.” Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ku̠a sa̠ anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ id̠igh ani̠ d̠o̠.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Ya̠a̠, agu̠o̠ ola̠ ko o̠gamame̠ni̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ rologi d̠awa, bha̠ sore d̠a̠ o̠bhi̠i̠y ka̠ ato̠ri̠ ma̠ amu̠kpabh, sa̠ o̠pu̠r ena̠ wa̠ anwa ta̠ a̠kor bho̠, bha̠ b̠etone ma̠ akpato̠n o̠nu̠ bho̠, sa̠ anwa ta̠ abi̠gh okpoki. Bhine ma̠ ka̠ a̠tua̠ ma̠ a̠bin d̠ami̠ na̠ ita̠ oyom.”\wj* 
\c 18  
\s1 O̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ irileghom bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 9:33-37; A̠luk 9:46-48) 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ iru ra̠ ipura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “A̠nyen o̠ni̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhelegi ma̠ o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ ra̠ amarame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa.  
\v 3 Sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ka̠ rologi d̠inyin onwegia̠n d̠o̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ita̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny, inyin ko od̠igh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Ezin bho̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ aki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠gbara o̠nyi̠ onon, bha̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠d̠ighom o̠nyi̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a d̠a̠ ebula̠ a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠, bha̠ a̠d̠ighom ami̠.\wj* 
\s1 Ad̠agi̠an ya̠ ogir i̠karabh 
\r (Amaki̠ 9:42-48; A̠luk 17:1-2) 
\p  
\v 6 \wj “Ali̠gam ta̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠kpu̠o̠m o̠gbe̠o̠ma d̠a̠ orum bho̠ ud̠ineni d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io abadi̠, ta̠ a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ uta̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ odi okubh o̠nyi̠ d̠a̠ anwi̠i̠ny i̠nye̠n ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ami̠ bho̠ ma̠ omel od̠igh d̠a̠ i̠karabh.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Olo a̠leghe ma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom d̠a̠ ebula̠ rad̠agi̠an ya̠ na̠ ed̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom na̠ egir i̠karabh. Rad̠agi̠an ya̠ o̠ku̠a ko o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ omite, ya̠a̠ olo a̠leghe ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ ad̠agi̠an ta̠ e̠wo̠l d̠o̠yo̠ emite bho̠!\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ agu̠o̠ bo̠d̠o̠ a̠wel d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam ogir i̠karabh, sobhe ma̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠robh. Anwa ma̠ obhin ekud̠i agu̠o̠, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠ro̠ ukula̠ ka̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠oyom bo̠d̠o̠ a̠sike d̠oyom olegha̠n, sa̠ ta̠ orobh anwa o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ anya wa̠ ko od̠im d̠o̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ ekpo a̠d̠ien d̠oyom na̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam ogir i̠karabh, poko ma̠ asi̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠robh. Anwa ma̠ obhin onin ekpo a̠d̠ien od̠igh d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um a̠bhon a̠pu ma̠ anwa ma̠ onwuna̠ i̠wal ikpo a̠rid̠ien, sa̠ ta̠ orobh anwa o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ ogugua̠ anya.\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh O̠nana wa̠ a̠bhe bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 15:3-7) 
\p  
\v 10 \wj “I̠bi̠ghe̠, o̠ni̠ ko okpon bebina̠ onin d̠a̠ ikubh anwi̠i̠ny i̠nye̠n egurumeni. Ezin bho̠, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠awa na̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ obhel d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny.\wj* 
\v 11 \f + \fr 18:11 \ft O̠gbu̠r onon bo̠ d̠a̠ idi i̠pu̠r ibhurugho bho̠. A̠fugh onon agu̠b̠an wa̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠\xt A̠luk 19:10\ft .\f*\wj Ezin bho̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ a̠ru ra̠ otenemeni ogbo ya̠ na̠ ebhe bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 12 \wj “Inyin u̠bi̠gh eka̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100) ro̠nana, sa̠ odi d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠awa a̠bhe, i̠na ka̠ o̠we̠le̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ d̠iobh na̠ esugho (99) bho̠ d̠a̠ a̠rugugum bho̠, agi̠ ka̠ abho̠ro̠ghan wa̠ a̠bhe bho̠ ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠na abi̠gh, ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠bo a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ o̠nana wa̠ a̠bhe bho̠ a̠pu ma̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ d̠iobh na̠ esugho (99) ya̠ obhe d̠o̠ bho̠. \wj* 
\v 14 \wj Obha̠ agu̠o̠ od̠i, bo̠ d̠a̠ ologi O̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ ma̠ odi o̠nyi̠ d̠a̠ ikubh anwi̠i̠ny i̠nye̠n omugh. \wj* 
\s1 Umor wa̠ a̠gir i̠karabh bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 17:3) 
\p  
\v 15 \wj “Ku̠gba ma̠a̠, umor d̠oyom a̠d̠ighi nyam ma̠ i̠karabh, gi̠e̠ ka̠ agba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ esi ola̠ i̠wal inyin ku̠ku̠m od̠i. Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠na anagha nyam, bha̠ anwa na̠ a̠mula̠ ate̠i̠ umor d̠oyom.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠nagha d̠o̠ nyam, bha̠ barame̠ na̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ bo̠d̠o̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh ani̠. I̠wal bo̠d̠o̠ i̠sar ronyob̠a̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ onyob̠a̠ na̠ e̠kparame̠ni̠ ma̠ iku.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠nagha d̠o̠, bha̠ gba d̠a̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n bho̠. Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠kikiom a̠kokod̠ia̠n bho̠ nyen, bha̠ ibhine i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ obhebhia̠n bo̠d̠o̠ ogun ma̠ otua̠ ebhugh.\wj* 
\p  
\v 18 \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, kerekere abar ola̠ u̠gho̠ro̠gi̠ d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠, na̠ o̠gho̠ro̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny, sa̠ kerekere abar ola̠ u̠ko̠gi̠o̠n d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠, na̠ o̠ko̠gi̠o̠n d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny. \wj* 
\p  
\v 19 \wj “O̠lo̠gho̠m i̠se̠, ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠wal o̠ni̠ inyin enwuna̠ ma̠ onin ologi d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠ egboloma̠ kerekere abar, O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ ta̠ a̠muzughod̠iom a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ ya̠ ipuru bho̠.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ezin bho̠, esi ola̠ i̠wal bo̠d̠o̠ i̠sar o̠ni̠ ibhin a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ ikokod̠ia̠n, ami̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠awa.” \wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ o̠we̠le̠man d̠o̠  //  ma̠ i̠karabh opa̠n o̠ni̠ bho̠ 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠ni̠ igiel ya̠ ka̠ umor d̠ami̠ a̠d̠ighi ami̠ ma̠ i̠karabh sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ awe̠le̠man a̠nigha̠ bho̠? Agu̠o̠ od̠ua̠l igiel ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, od̠ua̠l (7) igiel d̠o̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, od̠ua̠l (7) igiel ta̠ e̠rabharabh na̠ d̠iobh (70).\wj* 
\p  
\v 23 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, irileghom ote̠nai̠ny agu̠b̠an o̠li̠le̠ma ola̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ okpon o̠wal ikpoki ogir ta̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Agu̠o̠ i̠na ake̠ na̠ a̠kpon bho̠, sa̠ ubhin o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠d̠igh i̠na ma̠ o̠mu̠gh a̠d̠usubh na̠ ogho o̠ni̠r (10,000) ami̠na.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj Ya̠a̠, agu̠o̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠kpe̠ bho̠ sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠ruom ma̠ owol i̠na, na̠ ani̠ bho̠, na̠ anwi̠i̠ny bho̠, na̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar d̠o̠yo̠ obhin o̠kpe̠. \wj* 
\p  
\v 26 \wj “Sa̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ a̠mel a̠de a̠kpud̠ia̠n i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Kpone ami̠ igbirigbir ma̠ a̠ne ma̠ ekud̠i obhel, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ akpe̠ nyam kerekere abar.’\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠kpon igbirigbir ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠, sa̠ awe̠le̠man i̠na a̠gbogion o̠mu̠gh bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu obha̠ ad̠u̠a sa̠ abi̠gh odi ob̠a̠ra̠motu ola̠ a̠d̠igh o̠mu̠gh i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠dusubh (100) a̠dinari̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠ghinigia̠n i̠na, adu̠ ma̠ e̠d̠o̠gh bho̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Kpe̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠mu̠gh ya̠ anwa na̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ bho̠!’\wj* 
\p  
\v 29 \wj “Sa̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ na̠ i̠na na̠ ogir bho̠, a̠mel d̠a̠ a̠de ale̠gh i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Kpone ami̠ igbirigbir ma̠ a̠ne ma̠ ekud̠i obhel, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ akpe̠ nyam kerekere abar.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 30 \wj “Ya̠a̠, i̠na na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, a̠b̠ol i̠na ka̠ alo̠gh d̠a̠ ikoli tu̠tu̠n akpe̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠mu̠gh bho̠.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Igiel bho̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu iyed̠i i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠kakanyi̠gha ma̠ ibom, sa̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠gba inigha̠ ma̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠awa ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 32 \wj “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠lebh i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa obom o̠karabh ob̠a̠ra̠motu. Ami̠ i̠tu̠n agu̠o̠ anwa i̠le̠gh ami̠ bho̠ awe̠le̠man eb̠la̠ i̠mu̠gh d̠oyom.\wj* 
\v 33 \wj Na̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ nyam nyen okpon igbirigbir ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ na̠ anwa na̠ ogir bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ami̠ ikpon anwa ma̠ igbirigbir bho̠ ke̠re̠?’\wj* 
\v 34 \wj Sa̠ ologi ta̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠o̠yo̠ agam sa̠ a̠bhin i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ egbikimeni ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠, tu̠tu̠n ta̠ akpe̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠mu̠gh bho̠ amado̠n.\wj* 
\p  
\v 35 \wj “Obha̠ agu̠o̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi nyen, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ inyin na̠ obhin d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ awe̠le̠man i̠karabh umor d̠o̠yo̠.”\wj* 
\c 19  
\s1 Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ogbogina̠ ilom 
\r (Amaki̠ 10:1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kunugiom atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ Agalili agi̠ d̠a̠ Azo̠dan agba ebhugh A̠zudia̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na, sa̠ i̠na a̠koko awa ma̠ i̠se̠. 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ idi Rafarisi iru d̠o̠yo̠ ra̠ i̠d̠a i̠na ikpon ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “Ezin ola̠ a̠sora̠n o̠ni̠ ma̠ odin oze ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ od̠i ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠a̠, uwa̠ ale̠m awa d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton bho̠, ale̠m awa ma̠ o̠ya na̠ olobhiri ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, o̠ni̠ ta̠ awe̠le̠ ma̠ o̠we̠de̠ na̠ oweni d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ akpabhan ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠wal awa ta̠ eten onin ozu ku̠ku̠m?’\wj*\f + \fr 19:5 \ft \xt Ob̠et 2:24\f* 
\v 6 \wj Sa̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ko onwuna̠ mu ma̠ ozu ola̠ o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ i̠wal awa, ya̠a̠ onin ozu ku̠ku̠m. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠di̠ar iya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ atu̠lo̠m a̠guri onin bho̠, o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ o̠bagi̠o̠n d̠o̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 7 Sa̠ awa ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ku̠a ka̠ A̠mozizi a̠din ere agba ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ire ogbogina̠ ilom a̠bhin a̠ze i̠na.”  
\v 8 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠mozizi a̠din rab̠agh e̠mu̠ d̠inyin a̠ma̠ra̠ inyin ozegi ranwani̠ d̠inyin. Ya̠a̠ na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton bho̠.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Ya̠a̠ ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠gbogina̠ ma̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠, a̠sigimeni d̠a̠ ebula̠ ari̠gi̠, sa̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠bhin opa̠n ani̠, bha̠ a̠sor oloko od̠e e̠ma.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ifugh inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ e̠do̠lo̠ghu̠ma ta̠ ani̠ na̠ owolom od̠i ma̠ o̠ko̠no̠n, sa̠ o̠we̠le̠man o̠walan ilom ta̠ a̠bhon a̠pu.” 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ko orue d̠o̠ ada ma̠ ikpo a̠fugh i̠nye̠n a̠bhin, ya̠a̠, ogbo ya̠ na̠ o̠to̠ onigha̠ bho̠ ku̠ku̠m.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ezin bho̠, ugiri ma̠ idi ka̠ d̠a̠ okurogh onweni ma̠ o̠ro̠ ibhogha̠n ilobhiri kisa̠ u̠maragi̠, ya̠a̠ idi sa̠ a̠nwunom ibhoghi itenemeni ma̠ ibhogha̠n ilobhiri, idi sa̠ awa na̠ agu̠o̠ isibhom ozu iten ibhogha̠n ilobhiri d̠a̠ ebula̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny. O̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠rue ada ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠nye̠n a̠bhin bho̠, bha̠ ada a̠bhin!”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠tutumeni ma̠ I̠gbara Anwi̠i̠ny 
\r (Amaki̠ 10:13-16; A̠luk 18:15-17) 
\p  
\v 13 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ a̠nwunom ibhin i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny iru d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠gbam agu̠o̠ otutumeni, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ikigima̠ awa.  
\v 14 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Ima̠ra̠ ma̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ eru d̠ami̠, o̠ni̠ ko okigima̠ awa, ezin bho̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny aro̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ awa.”\wj* 
\v 15 Igiel bho̠ i̠na na̠ agbam awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ awe̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh erile ad̠u̠a ma̠ i̠se̠. 
\s1 Okubh O̠li̠la bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 10:17-31; A̠luk 18:18-30) 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠-atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ami̠ ta̠ a̠gir a̠kere ob̠eb̠i abar ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠te̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um ya̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠?” 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa i̠tu̠n ere na̠ a̠pura̠n ami̠ ma̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ aro̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i? A̠zib̠a̠ ku̠ku̠m ob̠eb̠i. Ya̠a̠, agu̠o̠ anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan o̠te̠i̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠, bha̠ koko ma̠ roloko bho̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Iken?” Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “ Ko ogigh o̠ni̠, ko od̠e ma̠ e̠ma, ko ob̠igh a̠b̠igh, ko o̠gba ma̠ onyob̠a̠ igunugha̠,\wj* 
\v 19 \wj ‘zuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi a̠nigha̠ ma̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ d̠oyom,’ \wj*\f + \fr 19:19 \ft \xt E̠d̠u̠a 20:12-16\ft ; \xt Oloko 5:16-20\f*\wj ma̠ ‘a̠tula̠n o̠ni̠ wa̠ d̠a̠ aka d̠oyom ma̠ agu̠o̠ ozu d̠oyom.’\wj*\f + \fr 19:19 \ft \xt I̠to̠t 19:18\f*\wj ” \wj* 
\p  
\v 20 Sa̠ okubh o̠ni̠ bho̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ a̠koko ma̠ eb̠la̠ roloko i̠nye̠n. Abar wa̠ a̠sughonom ami̠ ma̠ ogir bho̠, ka̠ ere?” 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Agu̠o̠ anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan obhon olegha̠n bho̠, gi̠e̠ ka̠ a̠wol eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar d̠oyom ma̠ a̠bhin a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠, sa̠ anwa ta̠ ate̠i̠ e̠li̠la d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny, ma̠ a̠ru ra̠ atu̠o̠no̠m ami̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ okubh o̠ni̠ bho̠ amu̠gho̠n e̠kal onon bho̠, sa̠ i̠na aku̠ru̠ru̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a, ezin bho̠ i̠na obom o̠li̠la. 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠ akpar ibom ma̠ o̠li̠la ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom ote̠nai̠ny!\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Ami̠ na̠ abaram na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, e̠nam-a̠dol o̠wo̠l d̠a̠ oyol anu̠ga oten ta̠ a̠b̠ur a̠pu ma̠ o̠li̠la o̠ni̠ ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.”\wj*\fig E̠nam a̠dol|alt="Carmel" src="Horace Knowles" size="col" loc="Luke 18:25" copy="HK00038" ref="18:25" \fig* 
\p  
\v 25 Igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ ma̠ ibom ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ka̠ a̠nyen ta̠ a̠rue ate̠i̠ itenemeni?” 
\p  
\v 26 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kimeni a̠kpon awa agba ma̠a̠, \wj “D̠a̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠, bho̠ onon ka̠ orue d̠o̠ a̠mite, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠, bha̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar eb̠ur.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Bi̠ghe̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠we̠le̠man eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar d̠i̠yar na̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m anwa. Ere wa̠ i̠yar ta̠ o̠te̠i̠ bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 28 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ya̠ na̠ e̠tu̠o̠no̠m ami̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, d̠a̠ omom amu̠m bho̠, ma̠ igiel O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ i̠kasi̠ a̠dila̠de isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, inyin eka̠ ta̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal (12) ri̠kasi̠ erileghom d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal (12) roghol Izre̠l.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Sa̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ awe̠le̠man eghunotu, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠rumor, bo̠d̠o̠ aru̠marani̠, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠we̠de̠, bo̠d̠o̠ onweni, bo̠d̠o̠ anwi̠i̠ny, bo̠d̠o̠ ari̠si̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ ami̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ ate̠i̠ i̠wal e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh (100) o̠gbam, sa̠ ta̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Ya̠a̠, a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ya̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠pu̠r i̠se̠n bho̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ u̠man, sa̠ a̠d̠izo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ u̠man i̠se̠n bho̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠pu̠r.\wj* 
\c 20  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠rogh A̠sidogh Amu̠kpe̠ Ogbo Ogir A̠lei A̠grep 
\p  
\v 1 \wj “Ta̠ obhin irileghom ote̠nai̠ny o̠tu̠o̠m o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lei a̠grep, sa̠ a̠mite ma̠ ad̠i̠ro̠ ka̠ ako̠ ma̠ ogbo ogir agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ egir d̠a̠ a̠lei a̠grep d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj Sa̠ i̠na amu̠gho̠nyan na̠ ogbo ogir bho̠ ma̠ o̠kpe̠ o̠ni̠ i̠se̠ ma̠ onin a̠dinari̠ \wj*\f + \fr 20:2 \fq A̠dinari̠ \ft Ikpoki ogir e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠\f*\wj ma̠ e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠, sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠ e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ a̠lei d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 3 \wj “Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ esugho obhel ma̠ asi̠ro̠, sa̠ abi̠gh ipa̠n a̠nwunom ka̠ i̠mara d̠a̠ egbolom a̠b̠ua̠ ya̠a̠ abar ogir bo̠.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Sa̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, ‘Inyin eka̠ i̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ a̠lei bho̠ sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠kpon ya̠ i̠kpe̠ akpe̠ inyin.’\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ epa̠.\wj* 
\p \wj “Sa̠ a̠mula̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal obhel na̠ d̠a̠ i̠sar obhel d̠a̠ etita̠n a̠gir onin agu̠o̠.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Sa̠ a̠mula̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ ogho obhel d̠a̠ a̠dule ka̠ ami̠nana ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ e̠mara, sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, ‘Ezin ka̠ ere ma̠ ola̠ inyin na̠ o̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠n eb̠la̠ e̠mu̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, ugir d̠o̠ abar?’\wj* 
\p  
\v 7 \wj “Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhin i̠yar ogir bo̠.’ Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom awa ma̠a̠, ‘Inyin eka̠ i̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ a̠lei bho̠.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 8 \wj “Sa̠ agu̠o̠ a̠d̠io na̠ a̠gul bho̠, sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ a̠ruom we̠mu̠ ogir d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ ogbo od̠ighi bho̠ akpe̠gi̠ awa ma̠ ya̠ awa igir bho̠, sa̠ ake̠ d̠a̠ ya̠ o̠gu̠man bho̠ akpe̠ ka̠ a̠kunugiom d̠a̠ i̠pu̠r bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 \wj “Sa̠ i̠na akpe̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ iru d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ onin obhel bho̠, o̠ni̠ i̠se̠ onin a̠dinari̠.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ ib̠on iru bho̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠ i̠na ta̠ o̠kpe̠ a̠wa opeleni ma̠ o̠ku̠a, ya̠a̠ u̠kpe̠ awa nyen o̠ni̠ i̠se̠ onin a̠dinari̠.\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Awa i̠da ibhin, sa̠ i̠go̠ya inigha̠ ma̠ wa̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠,\wj* 
\v 12 \wj ma̠a̠, ‘I̠nye̠n ya̠ o̠gu̠man bho̠ igir onin awa-obhel ku̠ku̠m, sa̠ u̠kpe̠ awa na̠ i̠yar onin agu̠o̠, ogbo ya̠ ugir etita̠n a̠d̠io ub̠ogina̠ bho̠ sa̠ u̠nu̠nu̠an e̠si̠so̠ ogogo bho̠.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 13 \wj “Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran odi awa ma̠a̠, ‘A̠tologha̠n, o̠karabh ola̠ ami̠ d̠ighi nyam bo̠. U̠mu̠gho̠nyan d̠o̠ ma̠ akpe̠gi̠an onin a̠dinari̠ ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Bhine ma̠ otoyom ma̠ ad̠u̠a, ami̠ i̠kpe̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ onon wa̠ a̠ru ma̠ o̠gu̠man bho̠ ma̠ onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ nyen.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Bo̠d̠o̠, na̠ osora̠n d̠o̠ ami̠ ma̠ obhin ya̠ ologi d̠ami̠ ogir ogboloma̠ i̠di̠ar d̠ami̠ ke̠re̠? Bo̠d̠o̠, anwa na̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ obom ekpo a̠d̠ien na̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ya̠ ami̠ i̠ne̠ghe̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠?’\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 \wj “Obha̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ aro̠, iya̠ o̠gu̠man bho̠ ta̠ eten i̠pu̠r, sa̠ i̠pu̠r bho̠ ta̠ eten iya̠ o̠gu̠man.” \wj* 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠mula̠ a̠wa̠ A̠gboloma̠ ma̠ Omugh D̠o̠yo̠  //  Oleghemeni I̠sar Igiel 
\r (Amaki̠ 10:32-34; A̠luk 18:31-34) 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh erile ma̠ obhun o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, sa̠ a̠bhin d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ a̠ten d̠a̠ a̠d̠ukun, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠,  
\v 18 \wj “I̠bi̠ghe̠, i̠yar na̠ obhun o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, sa̠ ta̠ owol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ onigha̠ ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ sa̠ ta̠ esobh ase̠ omugh ebhumeni i̠na.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ta̠ ob̠eton i̠na o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ibhebhia̠n bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ e̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ e̠gu̠ro̠gh i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ e̠du̠ i̠na d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren egigh, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠!”\wj* 
\s1 Ipuru Onweni ta̠ A̠zemsi na̠ Azo̠n 
\r (Amaki̠ 10:35-45) 
\p  
\v 20 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ onweni anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ Aze̠bidi a̠ru na̠ i̠wal anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ ra̠ a̠kpud̠ia̠n i̠na ma̠ opuru abar. 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa iru ra̠ opuru ere?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ma̠ra̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠, d̠a̠ irileghom d̠oyom, i̠wal anwi̠i̠ny d̠ami̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de, odi d̠a̠ od̠iom, ya̠a̠ uwed̠i d̠a̠ ekiel d̠oyom.” 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ inyin na̠ a̠puru bho̠. Inyin ta̠ orue o̠d̠a ma̠ i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ okpa̠ko wa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ o̠d̠a bho̠ ke̠re̠?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “I̠yar ta̠ orue.” 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠ga̠i, inyin ta̠ o̠d̠a d̠a̠ okpa̠ko d̠ami̠, ya̠a̠ o̠ro̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom d̠ami̠ na̠ d̠a̠ ekiel d̠ami̠, bo̠ d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠ami̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ aro̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠guri a̠sisa̠n bho̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 Igiel bho̠ d̠iobh iyed̠i i̠mu̠gho̠n bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠gam inigha̠ ma̠ i̠wal a̠rumor bho̠.  
\v 25 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠kokod̠i awa agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ologhom ma̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ erileghom ibhebhia̠n bho̠ na̠ eponoma̠ awa, sa̠ ibom a̠nwunom bho̠, bha̠ ya̠ awa i̠to̠ ya̠ iten.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan o̠bu̠gh d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin bho̠, aro̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠inyin.\wj* 
\v 27 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ d̠inyin bho̠, aro̠ ma̠ e̠bana d̠inyin:  
\v 28 ma̠ agu̠o̠ bha̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ oru d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ ogir e̠bana onigha̠ i̠na bho̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na a̠ru ma̠ o̠ro̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu onigha̠ a̠nwunom na̠ onigha̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ obhin o̠ta a̠d̠izo ogbo.” 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠koko ma̠ I̠wal A̠nwunom Ikpom A̠rid̠ien 
\r (Amaki̠ 10:46-52; A̠luk 18:35-43) 
\p  
\v 29 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ Aze̠riko bho̠, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na.  
\v 30 I̠wal a̠nwunom ikpom a̠rid̠ien i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ aka eten bho̠. Igiel bho̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠ten bho̠, sa̠ awa ikele ifugh ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, kpone i̠yar igbirigbir!” 
\p  
\v 31 Ya̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠ghaghana awa, ma̠ awa e̠ro̠ b̠o̠b̠o̠m. Ya̠a̠, awa i̠lo̠gh kuma̠ e̠mi̠ emulughu ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi, kpone i̠yar igbirigbir!” 
\p  
\v 32 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s amara, sa̠ a̠bhelegi awa a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan ami̠ ma̠ ogir ere onigha̠ inyin?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, i̠yar na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan o̠bi̠gh abar\f + \fr 20:33 \ft O̠bi̠gh abar: O̠bi̠gh esi; a̠rid̠ien bho̠ ma̠ o̠kpakpagi̠na.\f*.” 
\p  
\v 34 Sa̠ igbirigbir awa id̠ighi ma̠ A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ i̠na a̠kula̠n a̠rid̠ien d̠awa, sa̠ d̠a̠ onin obhel obha̠, sa̠ awa inwe i̠bi̠gh abar, sa̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na. 
\c 21  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s A̠d̠igh d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m ma̠ Agu̠o̠ O̠li̠le̠ma 
\r (Amaki̠ 11:1-11; A̠luk 19:28-38; Azo̠n 12:12-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ awa na̠ etua̠n A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠, sa̠ i̠gbari̠ d̠a̠ igu Roliv d̠a̠ e̠ma Abe̠tfagi̠. Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom a̠duom i̠wal ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma wa̠ a̠sumogha̠n inyin bho̠, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh okubh ado̠ki̠ ola̠ u̠kpu̠o̠m na̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠. I̠ko̠gi̠o̠ne̠ awa ma̠ ebhin eruom ami̠.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠pura̠n inyin abar, i̠wo̠rane̠ ma̠a̠, Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan orughom, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 4 Eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n imite ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ omuzughod̠iom iwowa̠ ya̠ owil bho̠ a̠wa̠ bho̠, ma̠a̠: 
\q1  
\v 5 “I̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ O̠nyani̠ ta̠ Azayo̠n ma̠a̠, 
\q2 ‘Kpone, O̠li̠le̠ma d̠oyom na̠ a̠ru d̠oyom, 
\q1 ti̠to̠i̠ny d̠a̠ anyu̠ ado̠ki̠, 
\q2 olobhiri o̠nyi̠ ado̠ki̠, e̠nam a̠dol.’ ”\f + \fr 21:5 \ft \xt Azak 9:9\f* 
\p  
\v 6 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ igir agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom awa bho̠.  
\v 7 Sa̠ awa ibhin ado̠ki̠ bho̠ na̠ olobhiri o̠nyi̠ ado̠ki̠ bho̠ iru, sa̠ ibhin rakapa d̠awa i̠de̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ rado̠ki̠ bho̠, ma̠ A̠zizo̠s od̠igh orile.  
\v 8 Sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom i̠de̠de̠gi̠ ma̠ ibom rakapa d̠awa d̠a̠ eten bho̠, sa̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom isobhi ma̠ igologo a̠d̠e\f + \fr 21:8 \ft Iriren ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ esi bho̠ bha̠ ra̠d̠e. Igologo ra̠d̠e d̠awa bho̠ ekper epu ma̠ ita̠ i̠yar. \f* ibhin i̠de̠de̠gi̠ d̠a̠ eten bho̠.  
\v 9 Sa̠ ro̠lo̠gh ogele i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ na̠ d̠a̠ aman d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ imulughu ma̠a̠, 
\q1 “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̱ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi!” 
\q1 “E̠no̠gho̠man na̠ e̠te̠i̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠.” 
\q1 “Itutumeni \f + \fr 21:9 \ft Ekpo a̠fugh d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ Ibru ola̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, tenemeni. D̠iobh na̠ ogho o̠gu̠r (15)\f*e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny, wa̠ agi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ a̠pu bho̠!” 
\p  
\v 10 Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m, sa̠ eb̠la̠ e̠ma bho̠ na̠ a̠nye̠ge̠re̠, sa̠ na̠ epura̠n ma̠a̠, “Onon ka̠ a̠nyen?” 
\p  
\v 11 Sa̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Onon owil A̠zizo̠s, wa̠ Anazare̠t d̠a̠ Agalili bho̠.” 
\s1 O̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 11:15-19; A̠luk 19:45-48; Azo̠n 2:13-22) 
\p  
\v 12 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠zegi ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eb̠ua̠ ma̠ a̠b̠ua̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, sa̠ a̠kpululeni ma̠ rakpata ogbo ya̠ na̠ enwegi ma̠ ikpoki bho̠ na̠ i̠kasi̠ ta̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ewod̠i ma̠ ukpugh osege bho̠.  
\v 13 Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri ma̠a̠, ‘Otu d̠ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ otu a̠siseiny,’\wj*\f + \fr 21:13 \ft \xt Azaya 56:7\f*\wj ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ otenemeni ma̠ ‘E̠fe̠m aru̠gba.’\wj*\f + \fr 21:13 \ft \xt A̠zer 7:11\f*\wj ”\wj* 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ ikpom a̠rid̠ien na̠ a̠rukula̠ bho̠ iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠koko awa.  
\v 15 Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ roloko bho̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar ilologia̠n ya̠ na̠ emite bho̠, na̠ agu̠o̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny bho̠ na̠ emulughu d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠a̠, “Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̱ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi,” sa̠ rologi d̠awa igurom.  
\v 16 Sa̠ awa ifugh inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ amu̠gho̠n ya̠ i̠nye̠n na̠ efugh bho̠ ke̠re̠?” Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, 
\p \wj “Yii, inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠a̠,\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘D̠a̠ aru̠nu̠ i̠gbara anwi̠i̠ny ya̠ od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ e̠mam,\wj* 
\q2 \wj bha̠ esi itutumeni d̠oyom na̠ e̠d̠u̠a na̠ eru’\wj*\f + \fr 21:16 \ft \xt Raso̠r 8:2\ft  (Bi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ E̠rabharabh na̠ d̠iobh bho̠.)\f*\wj ?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 17 Sa̠ i̠na awe̠le̠ awa ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Abe̠tani̠ ka̠ a̠kod̠u ab̠al. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠rogi ma̠ oriren a̠fig ola̠ omum d̠o̠ ma̠ itu 
\r (Amaki̠ 11:12-14,20-24) 
\p  
\v 18 Ad̠i̠ro̠, sa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠mula̠ na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ na̠ o̠ko̠i̠.  
\v 19 Sa̠ i̠na abi̠gh oriren a̠fig ola̠ a̠tua̠n eten bho̠, sa̠ a̠rile ka̠ ate̠i̠ bha̠ na̠ o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ abar d̠a̠ eb̠o, a̠ten ra̠to ku̠ku̠m. Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Otu omite mu d̠oyom tu̠tu̠n ka̠ id̠ud̠ul!” Sa̠ oriren a̠fig bho̠ aghi̠ghi̠ra epa̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 20 Igiel bho̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠bi̠gh bho̠, sa̠ ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “Eka̠ ma̠ ola̠ oriren a̠fig bho̠ aghi̠ghi̠ra epa̠ ma̠ ogbo na̠ onin bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ka̠ inyin unwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ola̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ i̠wal, inyin ko ogir d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ ugir ugboloma̠ ma̠ a̠fig bho̠ ku̠ku̠m, ya̠a̠ ka̠ inyin ufugh unigha̠ ma̱ igu onon eka̠, ma̠a̠, ‘B̠etina̠ ka̠ a̠mel d̠a̠ abadi̠,’ sa̠ ta̠ a̠mite ma̠ o̠ku̠a.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Sa̠ kerekere abar ola̠ inyin ubhin d̠a̠ a̠siseiny upuru, sa̠ inyin uma̠ra̠, bha̠ inyin ta̠ o̠te̠i̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Ipura̠n ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠limon ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 11:27-33; A̠luk 20:1-8) 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ikei a̠nwunom bho̠ ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠kere a̠limon wa̠ anwa na̠ a̠bhin na̠ a̠gir i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ a̠nyen a̠nigha̠ nyam a̠limon onon bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 24 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ ta̠ opura̠n inyin ipura̠n nyen. Ku̠gba ma̠ inyin o̠wo̠ran ami̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ agba a̠nigha̠ inyin nyen a̠d̠ien a̠limon wa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠gir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj Owura̠ amu̠m ta̠ Azo̠n ka̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠ken a̠ru? D̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠?”\wj* Sa̠ awa ibhin id̠igh d̠a̠ i̠b̠e̠re̠gi̠an ifugh ma̠a̠, “Ku̠gba ma̠ i̠yar u̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘D̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny,’ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, ‘O̠ku̠a ka̠, ezin ka̠ ere wa̠ i̠yar oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ i̠na bho̠?’  
\v 26 Ya̠a̠ ka̠ i̠yar u̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘D̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠,’ ya̠a̠ i̠yar na̠ oghil a̠nwunom bho̠, ezin bho̠ awa ibhin ma̠ Azo̠n owil.” 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “I̠yar uloghom d̠o̠.” Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ ko o̠gba d̠o̠ nyen a̠nigha̠ inyin a̠d̠ien a̠limon wa̠ Ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠gir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh I̠wal A̠rumor bho̠ 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “Inyin u̠bi̠gh ani̠ eka̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ i̠wal anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ odi o̠ni̠. Odi o̠ni̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ i̠wal anwi̠i̠ny, sa̠ a̠ruom o̠pu̠r o̠nyi̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ a̠lei bho̠ ka̠ a̠gir a̠didon.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 29 \wj “Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ka̠ orue d̠o̠,’ ya̠a̠ a̠tepa̠, sa̠ a̠nwe ma̠ ologi agi̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 30 \wj “Sa̠ o̠we̠de̠ bho̠ ate̠i̠ uwed̠i agba ma̠ onin agu̠o̠. Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ a̠ma̠ra̠,’ ya̠a̠ na̠ o̠gi̠ d̠o̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 31 \wj “Oken d̠a̠ i̠wal awa a̠gir i̠to̠ ta̠ o̠we̠de̠ bho̠?”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠pu̠r bho̠.” 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, rogunma̠otua̠ bho̠ na̠ id̠eme̠ma bho̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ d̠inyin ka̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj Ezin bho̠ Azo̠n a̠ru ra̠ oleriom inyin agu̠o̠ orugh a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠, ya̠a̠ inyin uma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ i̠na. Ya̠a̠ rogunma̠otua̠ bho̠ na̠ id̠eme̠ma bho̠ ema̠ra̠ i̠na. Sa̠ eb̠la̠ agu̠o̠ bho̠ inyin u̠bi̠gh ya̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠ itiba̠ra̠ bho̠ eka̠, inyin uloghoma̠n d̠o̠ oma̠ra̠ i̠na otiba̠ra̠.\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh Ogbo ya̠ I̠ko̠ ma̠ A̠lei bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 12:1-12; A̠luk 20:9-19) 
\p  
\v 33 \wj “I̠nagha ma̠ opa̠n a̠sidogh: O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu aro̠, sa̠ a̠gbebhegh a̠grep d̠a̠ a̠lei bho̠, sa̠ a̠ko a̠kiton a̠lei bho̠. Sa̠ a̠gbo ma̠ esi ola̠ o̠fi̠d̠igi̠ itu bho̠, sa̠ a̠lo ma̠ otu ipoiny. Sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ esi bho̠ ma̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei ma̠ o̠ko̠ orughom, sa̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠.\wj* 
\v 34 \wj Ate̠i̠ obhel o̠ku̠ imuma̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ikponom ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ ka̠ obhin a̠bin imuma̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 35 \wj “Sa̠ ikponom ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ ikighom rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠mar id̠ul odi, sa̠ igigh opa̠n, sa̠ irobhod̠i ma̠ uwed̠i.\wj* 
\v 36 \wj Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ a̠ruom ipa̠n rob̠a̠ra̠motu ya̠ ib̠uiy ipu ma̠ i̠pu̠r bho̠. Sa̠ igir onin agu̠o̠ igboloma̠ awa.\wj* 
\v 37 \wj D̠a̠ okunugiom, sa̠ a̠ruom o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ awa. Sa̠ i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Ta̠ eghila̠n o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 38 \wj “Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ a̠gbo ya̠ i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ i̠bi̠gh i̠na bho̠, sa̠ imimia̠n ma̠a̠, ‘Onon uwa̠ ta̠ a̠d̠e ma̠ ad̠i̠a bho̠, id̠ighi ta̠ ogigh i̠na, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠d̠i̠ar do̠yo̠ eten iyiyar.’\wj* 
\v 39 \wj Sa̠ ikighom i̠na, inuoghom i̠na imutiom d̠a̠ a̠lei bho̠, sa̠ igigh i̠na.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 40 \wj “Igiel wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru, ta̠ a̠gir eka̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ikponom ma̠ a̠lei bho̠?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 41 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠na ta̠ amar a̠kunugi ma̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠lei bho̠ ma̠ ipa̠n i̠ko̠ ma̠ a̠lei ya̠ ta̠ enigha̠ gha̠n i̠na ma̠ a̠bin imuma̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ akpe̠ bho̠.” 
\s1 Ikputu wa̠ ughel bho̠ 
\p  
\v 42 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠a̠:\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘Ikputu wa̠ ilo ma̠ a̠rutu ighel bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj na̠ a̠ten e̠ko̠ otu bho̠, \wj* 
\q1 \wj Onon ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠mite,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠i̠yar, sa̠ a̠bhon o̠bi̠gh’\wj*\f + \fr 21:42 \ft \xt Raso̠r 118:22,23\f*\wj ? \wj* 
\p  
\v 43 \wj “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ta̠ o̠wo̠r inyin irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ obhin onigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ ta̠ emum ib̠eb̠i itu.\wj* 
\v 44 \wj Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠melema̠ ma̠ ikputu onon ta̠ a̠tutughud̠ia̠n, sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ i̠na a̠mel a̠bhum sa̠ i̠na ta̠ agbe̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠tutughud̠i.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 45 Igiel bho̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n a̠sidogh d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, sa̠ iloghoma̠n ma̠ a̠rogh a̠sidogh bho̠ a̠nigha̠ awa.  
\v 46 Sa̠ awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ob̠ol o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ ighil a̠nwunom bho̠, ezin bho̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ibhin ma̠ i̠na owil. 
\c 22  
\s1 A̠sidogh obom o̠d̠e̠ erogh bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 14:15-24) 
\p  
\v 1 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s alo̠gho̠m opa̠n a̠sidogh a̠rogh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠,  
\v 2 \wj “Irileghom ote̠nai̠ny agu̠b̠an o̠li̠le̠ma ola̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n o̠d̠e̠ erogh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Sa̠ i̠na a̠ruom rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ obhelegi eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ u̠tu̠n o̠d̠e̠ erogh ulebh bho̠, ya̠a̠ awa i̠bho̠ro̠ghan d̠o̠ ma̠ oru.\wj* 
\p  
\v 4 \wj “Sa̠ i̠na a̠puta̠ a̠ruom ipa̠n rob̠a̠ra̠motu, agba ma̠a̠, ‘I̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ulebh bho̠ ma̠a̠: I̠bi̠ghe̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n ed̠ia̠n bho̠ amado̠n. Na̠ ogigh rodughuna̠ na̠ rovi i̠nu̠m d̠ami̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠ na̠ elegha̠n. Itue d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ erogh bho̠.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 5 \wj “Ya̠a̠, awa ibhin d̠o̠ e̠tu̠o̠m abar, sa̠ iten i̠d̠u̠a; odi agi̠ d̠a̠ o̠si̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ uwed̠i agi̠ d̠a̠ esi a̠b̠ua̠ d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Sa̠ ipa̠n isibh rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠, irughom i̠te̠i̠ sa̠ i̠ze̠gi̠ awa.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Sa̠ ologi o̠li̠le̠ma bho̠ a̠gurom, sa̠ a̠ruom ogbo e̠gham d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ okunugi i̠ze̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠, na̠ o̠bhu̠gi̠ e̠ma d̠awa osoroni.\wj* 
\p  
\v 8 \wj “Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘O̠d̠e̠ erogh bho̠ na̠ a̠lei, ya̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ ulebh bho̠ i̠bi̠gh ma̠ i̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ awa ma̠ oru.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ reten bho̠, ma̠ elebh ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ inyin u̠manana ma̠ oru d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ erogh bho̠.’\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Sa̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ imite i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ reten bho̠ ka̠ ikokod̠i ma̠ ogbo ya̠ awa i̠manana bho̠, a̠d̠igh i̠karabh na̠ ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ imuzo d̠a̠ obom ogbo otu erogh bho̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ rakpata od̠e.\wj* 
\p  
\v 11 \wj “Sa̠ o̠li̠le̠ma bho̠ a̠d̠igh okpon ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ rakpata od̠e bho̠, sa̠ abi̠gh o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠lagha d̠o̠ ma̠ ibura̠ erogh e̠yal bho̠.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Sa̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘A̠tologha̠n, anwa id̠ighi eka̠ a̠d̠igh esi onon, ma̠ ola̠ anwa onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ibura̠ e̠yal erogh bho̠?’ Ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ owuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ o̠wo̠ran. \wj* 
\p  
\v 13 \wj “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ o̠li̠le̠ma bho̠ a̠ruom rob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘I̠bhad̠i̠ ma̠ a̠sike na̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ enuwoghom i̠na ka̠ ed̠ighom d̠a̠ obom azi̠m. I̠se̠ esi ed̠i na̠ o̠ghi̠r ib̠ub̠ura̠ od̠i.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 14 \wj “Ezin bho̠ ubhelegi ma̠ iya̠ ib̠uiy, ya̠a̠ ta̠ o̠so̠n o̠nyi̠ki̠kara a̠nwunom obhin.”\wj* 
\s1 Otua̠ otua̠ ebhugh onigha̠ A̠siza̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 12:13-17; A̠luk 20:20-26) 
\p  
\v 15 D̠a̠ igiel obha̠, sa̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠d̠u̠a ka̠ i̠mu̠gho̠nyan agu̠o̠ obhin d̠a̠ asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠ o̠kpati̠ ob̠ol o̠yo̠.  
\v 16 Sa̠ awa iruom ogbo atu̠ghan d̠awa na̠ ita̠ E̠ro̠d ma̠ o̠gi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ opura̠n ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, i̠yar ologhom ma̠ anwa na̠ amar a̠rugh d̠a̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i, sa̠ anwa na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ eten ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ga̠i, anwa na̠ okpon d̠o̠ bebina̠ o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh, sa̠ anwa obhin d̠o̠ ma̠ imitia̠n o̠ni̠ atu̠o̠m abar.  
\v 17 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar, anwa i̠bi̠gh eka̠? A̠sora̠n otua̠ otua̠-ebhugh onigha̠ A̠siza̠ ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ na̠ osora̠n d̠o̠?” 
\p  
\v 18 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s abi̠gho̠m ipesi d̠awa sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Sa̠ ibhelebhel, ere wa̠ inyin na̠ o̠d̠agi̠an ami̠ bho̠?\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ileriome ami̠ ma̠ okpoki otua̠ bho̠.”\wj* Sa̠ awa imutiom a̠dinari̠.  
\v 20 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Onon ka̠ a̠misigh ta̠ a̠nyen, sa̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ a̠nyen?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “A̠siza̠.” Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, inigha̠ ma̠ A̠siza̠ ma̠ ita̠ A̠siza̠, ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ ita̠ A̠zib̠a̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 Agu̠o̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n o̠ku̠a bho̠, sa̠ awa ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ i̠we̠le̠man i̠na iten i̠d̠u̠a. 
\s1 Ipura̠n ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh 
\r (Amaki̠ 12:18-27; A̠luk 20:27-40) 
\p  
\v 23 D̠a̠ onin a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠, sa̠ Rasadusi bho̠, ogbo ya̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh odi bho̠, i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na ipura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠,  
\v 24 “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, A̠mozizi agba ma̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠mugh ya̠ na̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠, umor bho̠ ta̠ a̠bhin ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ b̠o̠ka̠ amar o̠nyi̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na.  
\v 25 I̠se̠n bha̠ od̠ua̠l a̠rumor e̠ro̠ na̠ i̠yar, sa̠ o̠pu̠r bho̠ a̠bhin ani̠ ya̠a̠ na̠ o̠mar d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠, sa̠ a̠mugh awe̠le̠man ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ umor d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 26 Sa̠ a̠mutuma̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a ma̠ oleghemeni i̠wal bho̠ na̠ oleghemeni i̠sar bho̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ oleghemeni od̠ua̠l bho̠.  
\v 27 D̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠, sa̠ ani̠ bho̠ eka̠ a̠mugh.  
\v 28 O̠ku̠a ka̠, d̠a̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠ ka̠ i̠na ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ ani̠ ta̠ a̠nyen, ma̠ agu̠o̠ eb̠la̠ od̠ua̠l awa na̠ ebhin i̠na bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 29 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin na̠ o̠ru̠an o̠pi̠e̠, ezin bho̠ inyin u̠mo̠gho̠yan d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, a̠d̠igh a̠limon ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj D̠a̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh bho̠ o̠walan ilom bo̠, unigha̠nom d̠o̠ nyen anwi̠i̠nyan, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Ya̠a̠, ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh imumugh bho̠, inyin ta̠ osen d̠o̠ ma̠ iya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ agba a̠nigha̠ inyin bho̠ ma̠a̠,\wj* 
\v 32 \wj ‘Ami̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ Ebraham na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ Azi̠ki̠ na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ A̠zeko̠pu̠ ke̠re̠’\wj*\f + \fr 22:32 \ft \xt E̠d̠u̠a 3:6\f*\wj ? I̠na A̠zib̠a̠ imumugh d̠o̠, ya̠a̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 Igiel bho̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ ib̠a̠gha̠gha̠ ma̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠. 
\s1 Oloko wa̠ Abu̠gh a̠pu bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 12:28-34; A̠luk 10:25-28) 
\p  
\v 34 Igiel bha̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠mu̠gho̠n ma̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠kpegi ma̠ aru̠nu̠ Rasadusi bho̠, sa̠ awa ikokod̠ia̠n ani̠.  
\v 35 Sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, a̠pura̠n o̠d̠agi̠an o̠yo̠, ma̠a̠:  
\v 36 “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, oloko oken wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ oloko bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 37 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠: \wj “ ‘Tula̠ne ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠oyom na̠ eb̠la̠ ekpo ologi d̠oyom, na̠ eb̠la̠ eloghoma̠n ozu d̠oyom, na̠ ebla̠ ologi d̠oyom.’\wj*\f + \fr 22:37 \ft \xt Oloko 6:5\f* 
\v 38 \wj Onon o̠pu̠r oloko bho̠ sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu bho̠.\wj* 
\v 39 \wj Oleghemeni i̠wal bho̠ od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠pu̠r bho̠: ‘Tula̠ne ma̠ o̠ni̠etua̠n d̠oyom ma̠ agu̠o̠ ozu d̠oyom.’\wj*\f + \fr 22:39 \ft \xt I̠to̠t 19:18\f* 
\v 40 \wj Eb̠la̠ roloko bho̠ na̠ a̠riwil bho̠, u̠ke̠ri̠ d̠a̠ i̠wal roloko i̠nye̠n.”\wj* 
\s1 Ipura̠n ya̠ igboloma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ amar Akrai̠st bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 12:35-37; A̠luk 20:41-44) 
\p  
\v 41 Igiel bho̠ Rafarisi bho̠ ikokod̠ia̠n bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠:  
\v 42 \wj “Inyin na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an eka̠ na̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st? I̠na ka̠ o̠nyi̠ ta̠ a̠nyen?”\wj* Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠devidi.” 
\p  
\v 43 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠: \wj “O̠ku̠a ka̠ ere wa̠ igiel E̠mu̠gh bho̠ a̠d̠igh A̠devidi bho̠ sa̠ a̠bhelegi I̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠’? Sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠,\wj* 
\q1  
\v 44 \wj “ ‘Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠ami̠:\wj* 
\q2 \wj “Ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠\wj* 
\q1 \wj tu̠tu̠n ami̠ ta̠ a̠soroni ma̠ ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien d̠oyom a̠tenemeni ma̠ okpokpolom o̠gbam a̠sike d̠oyom.” ’\wj* \f + \fr 22:44 \ft \xt Raso̠r 110:1\f* 
\m  
\v 45 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠ A̠devidi a̠bhelegi i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠,’ ka̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠d̠ighi eka̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠?”\wj* 
\v 46 Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠rue ma̠ o̠wo̠ran o̠yo̠, bo̠d̠o̠ omula̠ opura̠n o̠yo̠ ma̠ abar na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, ob̠eton a̠d̠a̠ma̠ obha̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠. 
\c 23  
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠sugi ma̠ I̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ //  na̠ Rafarisi bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 12:38-40; A̠luk 11:37-52; 20:45-47) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ ogbo ogir d̠o̠yo̠,  
\v 2 ma̠a̠: \wj “I̠tu̠ghe̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠ na̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ i̠kasi̠ ta̠ A̠mozizi.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, kerekere abar ola̠ awa iruom inyin, igire. Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ko orugh agu̠o̠ awa, ezin bho̠, awa na̠ e̠gba ma̠ ipa̠n na̠ egir ipa̠n.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Awa na̠ e̠gho̠ro̠gi̠ ma̠ ra̠dol ya̠ i̠mu̠mo̠r ipu ma̠ a̠nwunom orol na̠ e̠gbam d̠a̠ ro̠kpalma a̠nwunom, ya̠a̠ awa ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠ bebina̠ ad̠u̠nu̠ agu̠o̠ d̠awa ma̠ od̠igh orol.\wj* 
\p  
\v 5 \wj “Eb̠la̠ ogir ya̠ awa na̠ egir bho̠, bha̠ na̠ egir agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ elelegi awa. Awa na̠ e̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ robhurugho o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ a̠siseiny d̠awa, sa̠ na̠ eweghemeni ma̠ i̠sabh akapa d̠awa.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Awa iba̠ra̠ ma̠ ri̠kasi̠ edim d̠a̠ rakpata o̠d̠e̠ na̠ ra̠dila̠de edim d̠a̠ a̠rutu u̠gala A̠zu,\wj* 
\v 7 \wj sa̠ iba̠ra̠ ma̠ ipeleguma̠ itum d̠a̠ a̠risisi a̠b̠ua̠, na̠ a̠nwunom obhelegi awa ma̠a̠, ‘O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.’ \wj* 
\p  
\v 8 \wj “Ya̠a̠, obhelegi d̠o̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ‘O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.’ Onin o̠ni̠ ku̠ku̠m O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠inyin, ya̠a̠ eb̠la̠ inyin a̠rumor.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Ko obhelegi ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, ‘O̠we̠de̠’ i̠se̠n a̠de onon. Ezin bho̠ inyin unwuna̠ ma̠ onin O̠we̠de̠ ku̠ku̠m, ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Obhelegi d̠o̠ inyin ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ezin bho̠ Akrai̠st ku̠ku̠m bha̠ O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠inyin.\wj* 
\v 11 \wj O̠ni̠ wa̠ abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin bho̠, aro̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠inyin.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ abu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ ta̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ aki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ ta̠ o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 13 \wj “Olo a̠leghe inyin i̠tu̠ghe̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠, Ribhelebhel! Ezi̠n bho̠, inyin na̠ ogugi ma̠ o̠nu̠ otu irileghom ote̠nai̠ny na̠ okigima̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ d̠inyin bho̠. Inyin ud̠igh d̠o̠ sa̠ inyin na̠ okigima̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ od̠i̠gh bho̠ ma̠ od̠igh.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Olo a̠leghe inyin i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ roloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠, Ribhelebhel! Inyin na̠ oponoma̠ ma̠ rekpukele anwani̠ na̠ o̠wo̠ro̠gh i̠di̠ar, sa̠ inyin na̠ osiseiny iwewegh a̠siseiny b̠o̠ka̠ olelegi inyin. Ta̠ o̠gu̠r inyin agu̠o̠ i̠zagba ola̠ abu̠gh ibom.”\wj*\f + \fr 23:14 \ft O̠gbu̠r onon bo̠ d̠a̠ idi i̠pu̠r obhurugho bho̠. A̠fugh onon agu̠b̠an ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ \xt Amak 12:40\ft  na̠ \xt A̠luk 20:47\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 15 \wj “Itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠. Ribhelebhel! Inyin na̠ o̠d̠u̠a ma̠ esi na̠ oten esi ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠te̠i̠ bebina̠ o̠ni̠, sa̠ ka̠ inyin na̠ o̠te̠i̠, sa̠ inyin na̠ omula̠ na̠ od̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠ten o̠nyi̠ e̠banya ola̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠pu inyin i̠wal igiel.\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 \wj “Itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin, ogbo ikpom a̠rid̠ien ya̠ na̠ erileghom ipa̠n ogbo! Inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aghad̠i̠an, bha̠ o̠kpe̠ bo̠. Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin a̠gol wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ aghad̠i̠an, bha̠ i̠na na̠ ako̠man.’\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Rema̠! Ogbo ikpom a̠rid̠ien! Oken abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ i̠wal a̠yi: a̠gol bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ a̠worogi ma̠ a̠gol bho̠?\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Inyin na̠ o̠gba nyen ma̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin enwen alu̠kpe̠ bho̠ aghad̠i̠an, ma̠ o̠kpe̠ bo̠. Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ a̠bhin e̠ne̠ghe̠ wa̠ u̠gbam d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠ aghad̠i̠an bha̠ na̠ ako̠man.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ogbo ikpom a̠rid̠ien, oken abu̠gh a̠pu d̠a̠ i̠wal a̠yi: enigha̠ bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ enwen bho̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠worogi ma̠ enigha̠ bho̠?\wj* 
\v 20 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠bhin enwen bho̠ aghad̠i̠an bho̠, ab̠aram na̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠gbam d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠ aghad̠i̠an.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Sa̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠bhin otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aghad̠i̠an bho̠, a̠bhin otu bho̠ na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠rugh d̠a̠ ologi bho̠ aghad̠i̠an.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Sa̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhin ote̠nai̠ny aghad̠i̠an, bha̠ a̠bhin a̠dila̠de irileghom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ i̠na wa̠ od̠i ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ i̠kasi̠ irileghom bho̠ aghad̠i̠an.\wj* 
\p  
\v 23 \wj “Itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠, Ribhelebhel! Ezin bho̠, inyin na̠ obhin aghan-od̠od̠ua̠ na̠ u̠ki̠a na̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere i̠gho̠gho̠ a̠mubobh, na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ a̠bin d̠a̠ a̠d̠iobh atu̠gi̠, ya̠a̠ inyin ubhin d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ilei abar ipu d̠a̠ oloko bho̠ o̠tu̠o̠m abar. A̠ma̠rugh igielake̠, na̠ okpon igbirigbir, na̠ onwuna̠ ologi ima̠ra̠. Akpe̠ inyin ogir i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n, ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ko o̠we̠le̠ ma̠ ogir i̠di̠ar iyed̠i nyen.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Ogbo ikpom a̠rid̠ien! Inyin na̠ omurugha̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠, sa̠ inyin na̠ o̠mi̠n e̠nam-a̠dol.\wj* 
\p  
\v 25 \wj “Itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠. Ribhelebhel! Ezin bho̠ inyin na̠ otitol aman okpa̠ko bho̠, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ ologi bho̠ bha̠ a̠ponoma̠, na̠ o̠ku̠ku̠, na̠ i̠karabh od̠ighi i̠di̠ar imuzo.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Rafarisi ikpom a̠rid̠ien! Id̠ia̠ ma̠ etitol eb̠la̠ ologi okpa̠ko bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ aman bho̠ eka̠ ta̠ ab̠ab̠ala.\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 \wj “Itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠. Ribhelebhel! Ezin bho̠ inyin u̠gu̠b̠an ranyu̠ od̠i ya̠ u̠mar u̠lo̠ sa̠ na̠ ekil d̠a̠ etire, sa̠ i̠gu̠b̠an ya̠ ibhon ibom d̠a̠ ologi. Ne̠ge̠ bha̠ i̠kpo̠kpo̠ imumugh a̠nwunom na̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere i̠gho̠ro̠gho̠r emuzo d̠a̠ ologi.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Obha̠ agu̠o̠ inyin eka̠ u̠gu̠b̠an ogbo ya̠ i̠b̠ab̠ala d̠a̠ anyu̠, sa̠ na̠ erugh a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠, ya̠a̠, ado̠l ibhelebhel na̠ a̠ma̠rugh i̠te̠i̠ imuzo d̠a̠ aghud̠um d̠inyin.\wj* 
\p  
\v 29 \wj “Itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ inyin i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠. Ribhelebhel! Ezin bho̠, inyin na̠ ob̠olob̠ol ranyu̠od̠i a̠riwil bho̠, sa̠ inyin na̠ oburi ma̠ ranyu̠od̠i ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom bho̠.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Sa̠ inyin na̠ o̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘I̠yar umite d̠a̠ amu̠m igba̠iny ro̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar nab̠o̠, i̠yar ka̠ ud̠igh ani̠ d̠o̠ o̠ze̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠riwil bho̠.’\wj* 
\v 31 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, inyin agu̠o̠ ud̠igh onyob̠a̠ ebhum ase̠ d̠inyin, ma̠a̠, inyin anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠ze̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠riwil bho̠.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj Inyin eka̠ i̠gi̠o̠me̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, ma̠ emuzoghod̠iom ogir ya̠ igba̠iny ro̠we̠de̠ d̠inyin i̠ke̠ bho̠!\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 \wj “I̠karabh i̠di̠ar! Anwi̠i̠ny i̠bho̠ru̠bho̠ru̠ i̠karabh i̠di̠ar! Inyin ta̠ od̠ighi eka̠ omiza̠n osobh ase̠ e̠ba anya bho̠?\wj* 
\v 34 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ami̠ na̠ a̠ruom a̠riwil, na̠ iloghom ma̠ i̠di̠ar, na̠ ogbo i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ na̠ a̠ruom inyin. Inyin ta̠ o̠ze̠gi̠ ma̠ idi awa, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠du̠gi̠ ma̠ idi o̠ze̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠gu̠ro̠gh idi d̠a̠ ru̠gala d̠inyin, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠d̠u̠a ma̠ e̠ma oten e̠ma ozegi awa.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj D̠a̠ ebul o̠ku̠a, eb̠la̠ asi̠ ta̠ ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom ya̠ uzu d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ d̠inyin, ob̠eton d̠a̠ asi̠ ta̠ ob̠eb̠i Ebe̠l ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ asi̠ ta̠ Azakaraya o̠nyi̠ ta̠ Abarakaya wa̠ igigh d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ enwen i̠ko̠l bho̠.\wj* 
\v 36 \wj Ya̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite d̠a̠ amu̠m onon.\wj* 
\p  
\v 37 \wj “A̠zeruse̠le̠m, A̠zeruse̠le̠m, anwa wa̠ na̠ aze̠ ma̠ a̠riwil bho̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠robhod̠i ma̠ ogbo ya̠ uruom oru d̠oyom bho̠. Ya̠a̠ i̠ni̠ igiel, ka̠ na̠ ebhir ami̠ ma̠ okokod̠i eb̠la̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠oyom oguri onin esi, ma̠ agu̠o̠ e̠nu̠r-e̠ma na̠ a̠bhin rapu̠ba d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠ghughuom anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ anwa na̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj Ya̠ga̠i, na̠ o̠we̠le̠ ma̠ otu d̠oyom oguri ma̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠.\wj* 
\v 39 \wj Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ob̠eton i̠se̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, inyin ko o̠bi̠gh mu̠ ami̠ tu̠tu̠n inyin ta̠ ofugh ma̠a̠, ‘Itutumeni e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ na̠ a̠ru bho̠.’\wj*\f + \fr 23:39 \ft \xt Raso̠r 118:26\f*\wj ” \wj* 
\c 24  
\s1 Ob̠ogion Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 13:1,2; A̠luk 21:5,6) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠mite na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ iru ra̠ i̠tu̠o̠gho̠m inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ eloma̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠.  
\v 2 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n? Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, ekpo ikputu ola̠ ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ ta̠ opa̠n ola̠ ko ob̠ogion d̠o̠ bo̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Elegh wa̠ ekunuguma̠ obhel bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 13:3-13; A̠luk 21:7-19) 
\p  
\v 3 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ igu Roliv bho̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ iru d̠o̠yo̠ ra̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, “Gba ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar, a̠kere obhel wa̠ i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite bho̠, na̠ ere wa̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ elegh eruoma̠ d̠oyom na̠ ekunuguma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 4 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠: \wj “I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpona̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ko ogelemeni d̠o̠ inyin.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj A̠d̠izo a̠nwunom ta̠ ebhin a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠ eru, sa̠ ta̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ Akrai̠st,’ sa̠ ta̠ egelemeni ma̠ a̠d̠izo ogbo.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Inyin ta̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n i̠mu̠mu̠gho̠n re̠gham, o̠ni̠ okpa̠ra̠numa̠ d̠o̠. I̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠ku̠a ta̠ emite, ya̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ obhel bho̠ ta̠ olei d̠o̠.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Ebhugh ta̠ ewia̠n ebhugh, sa̠ irileghom ta̠ ewia̠n irileghom. Ibom ro̠ko̠i̠ ta̠ esor, sa̠ ra̠de ta̠ enyegia̠n eb̠omia̠n ekurubh, d̠a̠ a̠d̠izo a̠risi.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ya̠a̠, eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n kisa̠ ob̠eton ali̠gam a̠ruzu bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 \wj “Igiel o̠ku̠a, ta̠ ob̠eton inyin onigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ta̠ e̠ni̠ni̠gi̠o̠m inyin, sa̠ ta̠ egigh inyin, sa̠ eb̠la̠ ibhebhia̠n bho̠ ta̠ e̠lo̠gh inyin a̠d̠ien d̠a̠ ebula̠ a̠d̠ien d̠ami̠.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Igiel o̠ku̠a, a̠d̠izo ogbo ta̠ emel e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠, sa̠ odi ta̠ a̠luom odi, sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠lo̠gi̠an a̠rid̠ien,\wj* 
\v 11 \wj sa̠ a̠d̠izo a̠riwil igunugha̠ ta̠ emite egelemeni ma̠ a̠d̠izo ogbo.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Sa̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ a̠ma̠rugh i̠te̠i̠ ta̠ a̠kpegiom a̠nwunom bho̠, etula̠n ta̠ aki̠r d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io a̠d̠izo ogbo.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ne ka̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠ten.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Sa̠ ta̠ o̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba irileghom bho̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ta̠ amu̠gho̠n, sa̠ ekunuguma̠ obhel bho̠ ta̠ a̠lei.\wj* 
\s1 Ibom Ali̠gam A̠ruzu bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 13:14-23; A̠luk 21:20-24) 
\p  
\v 15 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, igiel inyin u̠bi̠gh ka̠ abar ola̠ omitegha̠n d̠o̠ na̠ a̠mite amara d̠a̠ esi e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠d̠i̠ar na̠ e̠pi̠e̠gi̠an, ma̠ agu̠o̠ owil Adani̠e̠l a̠wa̠ bho̠ (o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠sen bho̠ amu̠gho̠nyan), \wj* 
\v 16 \wj bha̠, ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ A̠zudia̠, eghil ebhun d̠a̠ rebhugh ya̠ i̠gi̠ ma̠ anyu̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj O̠ni̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ anyu̠ otu bho̠ osor d̠o̠ ka̠ a̠bhin abar d̠a̠ otu d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Sa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ od̠ighi bho̠ omula̠ d̠o̠ ka̠ a̠bhin ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ya̠a̠ ekulom anwani̠ a̠rughun na̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ enigha̠ ma̠ amu̠mam bho̠, d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠ye̠, \wj* 
\v 20 \wj Isiseinye ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠inyin ko osora̠n d̠o̠ d̠a̠ obhel a̠d̠igho, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ Epobh bho̠.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Ezin bho̠, ka̠ a̠sora̠n d̠a̠ igiel ola̠ o̠ku̠a, ali̠gam a̠ruzu bho̠ ta̠ a̠peleni ka̠ ate̠i̠ esi ola̠, ta̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠ abar ola̠ oku̠a ta̠ od̠ia̠ d̠o̠ a̠mite ma̠ obhin d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ ra̠ o̠te̠i̠ i̠se̠n, ya̠ ko omite mu nyen.\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 \wj “Sa̠ ku̠gba ma̠a̠, ukperemeni d̠o̠ ma̠ obhel bho̠, bebina̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ a̠miza̠n a̠d̠um bo̠. Ya̠a̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ o̠so̠n bho̠, ta̠ okperemeni ma̠ obhel obha̠.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Igiel o̠ku̠a, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ agba a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ‘Bi̠ghe̠, Akrai̠st od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠n!’ Bo̠d̠o̠, ‘Od̠i ma̠ ebha̠!’ O̠ni̠ ko od̠umom.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Ra̠krai̠st igunugha̠ na̠ a̠riwil igunugha̠ ta̠ emite sa̠ ta̠ eleriom ibom relegh na̠ ogir ilologia̠n, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠b̠ur nab̠o̠, ka̠ igelemeni nyen ogbo ya̠ na̠ o̠so̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj I̠bi̠ghe̠! Ami̠ na̠ a̠d̠ia̠ agba a̠nigha̠ inyin.\wj* 
\p  
\v 26 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ni̠ agba a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ‘I̠bi̠ghe̠, od̠i d̠a̠ e̠ghana bho̠,’ ko o̠gi̠ ka̠ e̠bi̠ghan; bo̠d̠o̠, ‘I̠bi̠ghe̠, od̠i d̠a̠ e̠bhai̠, esi e̠wo̠gi̠na’ ko oma̠ra̠.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Ezin bho̠, agu̠o̠ i̠me̠me̠gi̠na agbararan, ka̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ opu omite ogogo bho̠, sa̠ na̠ awar na̠ a̠misi d̠a̠ osor ogogo bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ eruoma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ aro̠.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Kesikesi ola̠ e̠b̠u̠re̠ od̠i, obha̠ esi ro̠de̠le̠ bho̠ na̠ ekokod̠ia̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\s1 Eruoma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 13:24-27; A̠luk 21:25-28) 
\p  
\v 29 \wj “Ali̠gam a̠ruzu ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ i̠nye̠n ma̠ oten ku̠ku̠m bha̠,\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘Ogogo bho̠ o̠zu̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ uwetere bho̠ ko o̠mu̠ mu̠;\wj* 
\q1 \wj re̠ni̠nai̠ny bho̠ ta̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny emeleghu,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ ra̠limon ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ re̠nai̠ny bho̠ ta̠ enyegia̠n.’\wj*\f + \fr 24:29 \ft \xt Azaya 13:10; 34:4\f* 
\p  
\v 30 \wj “D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ elegh O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠mite d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny, sa̠ eb̠la̠ rebhugh e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ ta̠ ed̠igh i̠ku̠nu̠. Sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh ka̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ na̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠ugh ote̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠limon na̠ ibom isosorogia̠n.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Sa̠ ta̠ a̠ruom itileduom d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ opughe od̠od̠ue obom oghur, sa̠ ta̠ ekokod̠i ma̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠na na̠ aso̠n d̠a̠ inya̠ re̠ku̠l bho̠, obeton d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ odi agba a̠de na̠ e̠nai̠ny o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ esumogha̠n bho̠.\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh Oriren A̠fig bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 13:28-31; A̠luk 21:29-33) 
\p  
\v 32 \wj “I̠tu̠ghane̠ ma̠ a̠sidogh oriren a̠fig bho̠: Igiel bha̠ i̠gha na̠ edugh na̠ a̠nwegina̠ ma̠ a̠to, bha̠ inyin ologhom ma̠ a̠kozogh na̠ a̠tua̠n.\wj* 
\v 33 \wj Obha̠ agu̠o̠ od̠i nyen, igiel inyin u̠bi̠gh eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n, iloghome ma̠ obhel bho̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠a agu̠o̠, na̠ a̠misi d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ otu.\wj* 
\v 34 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, amu̠m onon ka̠ oten d̠o̠ a̠munia̠n kisa̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ta̠ emite.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj A̠de na̠ e̠nai̠ny ta̠ eten e̠d̠u̠a, ya̠a̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠ami̠ ko oten d̠o̠ e̠d̠u̠a.\wj* 
\s1 O̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom A̠d̠a̠ma̠ na̠ obhel bho̠ bo̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 13:32-37; A̠luk 17:26-30,34-36) 
\p  
\v 36 \wj “Ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ologhom a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠ na̠ obhel bho̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom bo̠, a̠d̠igh itileduom ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny bho̠, a̠d̠igh O̠nyi̠ bho̠. O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ ku̠ku̠m a̠loghom.\wj* 
\v 37 \wj Agu̠o̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ obhel ta̠ A̠nua̠ bho̠, obha̠ agu̠o̠ eruoma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ aro̠.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj Ezin bho̠ agu̠o̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ obhel bho̠, kisa̠ obom amu̠m a̠d̠igho bho̠ a̠ru bho̠, a̠nwunom na̠ ed̠e na̠ e̠d̠a, na̠ ebhinogh ranwani̠ na̠ enigha̠nom ra̠nwi̠i̠nyan, tu̠tu̠n d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ A̠nua̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ologi obom oghugh bho̠;\wj* 
\v 39 \wj sa̠ iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ ta̠ emite tu̠tu̠n obom amu̠m a̠d̠igho bho̠ a̠ru, sa̠ aze̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠. Obha̠ agu̠o̠ eruoma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ aro̠ nyen.\wj* 
\v 40 \wj D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, i̠wal o̠ni̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ o̠si̠, ta̠ obhin odi sa̠ ta̠ o̠we̠le̠ ma̠ uwed̠i.\wj* 
\v 41 \wj I̠wal anwani̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ esi o̠gbe̠ ed̠ia̠n na̠ e̠gbe̠ ma̠ ed̠ian, sa̠ ta̠ obhin odi o̠we̠le̠ ma̠ uwed̠i.\wj* 
\p  
\v 42 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, igone, ezin bho̠ inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠inyin ta̠ a̠ru bho̠.\wj* 
\v 43 \wj I̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠mu̠gho̠nyan abar onon. Ku̠gba ma̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ otu bho̠ a̠loghom obhel wa̠ o̠gba bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru bho̠ nab̠o̠, i̠na ka̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ omom a̠kigima̠ ma̠ o̠gba bho̠ ma̠ ob̠om otu bho̠ od̠igh.\wj* 
\v 44 \wj Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, inyin eka̠ ikokod̠ia̠ne, ezin bho̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠ru ma̠ obhel ola̠ inyin o̠ru̠ru̠an d̠o̠.\wj* 
\s1 A̠ga̠i Ob̠a̠ra̠motu na̠ O̠karabh Ob̠a̠ra̠motu 
\r (A̠luk 12:35-48) 
\p  
\v 45 \wj “I̠se̠, ka̠ a̠nyen a̠ga̠i ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ a̠loghom abar bho̠, ola̠ wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠sibh, ma̠ okponom rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠ onigha̠ awa ma̠ ed̠ia̠n d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ akpe̠ bho̠?\wj* 
\v 46 \wj E̠b̠e̠l ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ ka̠ wa̠nwuna̠ i̠na bho̠ a̠ru, sa̠ ta̠ abi̠gh ma̠ i̠na na̠ amar na̠ a̠gir bho̠.\wj* 
\v 47 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠b̠eton eb̠la̠ e̠li̠la d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ okponom.\wj* 
\v 48 \wj Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu obha̠ ma̠ o̠karabh o̠ni̠, sa̠ aru̠ru̠an d̠a̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠ami̠ ta̠ a̠bia̠ ma̠ oru,’\wj* 
\v 49 \wj sa̠ ake̠ ma̠ od̠ulogh rob̠a̠ra̠motu iyed̠i, sa̠ na̠ a̠d̠e na̠ ad̠a na̠ ro̠d̠amin.\wj* 
\v 50 \wj Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ ola̠ i̠na o̠ru̠ru̠an d̠o̠, na̠ obhel ola̠ i̠na ologhoma̠n d̠o̠.\wj* 
\v 51 \wj Sa̠ ta̠ agu̠r i̠na ma̠ obom agu̠o̠ i̠zagba, sa̠ ta̠ alo̠gh i̠na d̠a̠ agba ibhelebhel bho̠: i̠se̠ esi bho̠ ed̠i na̠ o̠ghi̠r ib̠ub̠ura̠ od̠i.\wj* 
\c 25  
\s1 A̠sidogh a̠d̠iobh Re̠kar Anwi̠i̠nyan bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 \wj “O̠ku̠a bha̠, ta̠ obhin irileghom ote̠nai̠ny o̠tu̠o̠m d̠iobh re̠kar anwi̠i̠nyan ya̠ ibhin rato̠di̠ d̠awa imite ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠bi̠ghan o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj Ogho d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠awa bha̠ rema̠, ya̠a̠ ogho bha̠ iloghodi̠ar.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Obhel bho̠ rema̠ bho̠ ibhin rato̠di̠ d̠awa bho̠, ibhin ani̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ amu̠nu̠ oliv e̠b̠aram.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Ya̠a̠, iloghodi̠ar bho̠ ibhin amu̠nu̠ oliv d̠a̠ rakana e̠b̠aram na̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ato̠di̠ d̠awa bho̠.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Sa̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ na̠ a̠bia̠ ma̠ oru bho̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa iduka̠ sa̠ adi̠la ibhinom awa.\wj* 
\p  
\v 6 \wj “I̠se̠, d̠a̠ egum a̠d̠io, sa̠ awa i̠mu̠gho̠n izul ma̠a̠: ‘O̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠misi! Imite ma̠ eru ra̠ e̠bi̠ghan i̠na!’\wj* 
\p  
\v 7 \wj “Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kar anwi̠i̠nyan bho̠ i̠su̠ma, sa̠ i̠pi̠ki̠ ma̠ rato̠di̠ d̠awa ibu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Sa̠ rema̠ bho̠ ifugh inigha̠ ma̠ iloghodi̠ar bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Inigha̠ i̠yar idi amu̠nu̠ oliv d̠inyin; ato̠di̠ d̠i̠yar na̠ ed̠im.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 \wj “Ya̠a̠, iloghodi̠ar bho̠ i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠ ‘E̠nyi̠, ita̠ i̠yar eka̠ ko olei d̠o̠ i̠yar. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, inyin na̠ agu̠o̠ i̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ewol bho̠ ka̠ egho ma̠ iya̠ inyin.’\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Sa̠ agu̠o̠ awa i̠d̠u̠a ka̠ ogho bho̠, sa̠ o̠ni̠ erogh bho̠ a̠ru. Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ ikokod̠ia̠n bho̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m i̠na id̠igh d̠a̠ o̠d̠e̠ erogh bho̠, sa̠ u̠du̠ ma̠ otu bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 11 \wj “A̠tepa̠, sa̠ re̠kar anwi̠i̠nyan iyed̠i iru nyen, sa̠ ifugh ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, Wa̠nwuna̠, gurone ma̠ a̠d̠ighom i̠yar!’\wj* 
\p  
\v 12 \wj “Ya̠a̠, i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, ‘Ya̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ inyin.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 13 \wj “O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, igone, ezin bho̠ inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ obhel bho̠.\wj* 
\s1 A̠sidogh i̠sar Rob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ 
\r (A̠luk 19:11-27) 
\p  
\v 14 \wj “Irileghom ote̠nai̠ny od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ ob̠etina̠ e̠gi̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠kokod̠i ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ aru̠gi̠ awa ma̠ i̠di̠ar d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ okponom.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi ogho e̠kpa ikpoki,\wj*\f + \fr 25:15 \ft e̠kpa ikpoki obhel obha̠\f*\wj sa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi i̠wal, sa̠ odi onin, o̠ni̠ i̠se̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ e̠mi̠ bho̠ a̠lei bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠etina̠ epa̠ ma̠ e̠gi̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj O̠ni̠ wa̠ ada ma̠ ogho e̠kpa ikpoki obhel obha̠, sa̠ a̠bhin a̠b̠ua̠ ma̠ a̠b̠ua̠, sa̠ ate̠i̠ asu̠o̠ ogho ab̠aram.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, wa̠ i̠wal bho̠ eka̠, ate̠i̠ asu̠o̠ i̠wal ab̠aram.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ya̠a̠, wa̠ unigha̠ ma̠ onin bho̠, agi̠ ka̠ a̠gbo d̠a̠ a̠de awo̠gi̠ ma̠ okpoki ta̠ wa̠nwuna̠ d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 19 \wj “Owewegh obhel a̠ten, sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ rob̠a̠ra̠motu bho̠ a̠ru ma̠ oselegi o̠wal ogir d̠awa.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Sa̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ unigha̠ ma̠ ogho e̠kpa ikpoki ab̠ar na̠ ipa̠n ogho e̠kpa a̠ru, sa̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, anwa inigha̠ ami̠ ogho e̠kpa ikpoki, bi̠ghe̠, ami̠ i̠te̠i̠ asu̠o̠ ipa̠n ogho e̠kpa.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 21 \wj “Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ do̠yo̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa a̠gir, anwa a̠ga̠i ob̠a̠ra̠motu! Anwa ibhin onyen ologi a̠gir d̠a̠ i̠ki̠kara i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ inigha̠ nyam bho̠, ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠se̠n ami̠ na̠ aso̠n anwa ma̠ orileghom i̠di̠ar ya̠ ib̠uiy ipu ma̠ i̠nye̠n. Ke̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠d̠e ma̠ e̠no̠gho̠man ta̠ wa̠nwuna̠ nyam.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 \wj “Sa̠ wa̠ unigha̠ i̠wal e̠kpa ikpoki eka̠ a̠ru ra̠ agba ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, anwa inigha̠ ami̠ i̠wal e̠kpa ikpoki, bi̠ghe̠, ami̠ i̠te̠i̠ asu̠o̠ ipa̠n i̠wal e̠kpa.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 23 \wj “Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ do̠yo̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa amar a̠gir, anwa a̠ga̠i ob̠a̠ra̠motu! Anwa ibhin onyen ologi a̠gir d̠a̠ i̠ki̠kara i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ inigha̠ nyam bho̠, ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, i̠se̠n ami̠ na̠ aso̠n anwa ma̠ orileghom i̠di̠ar ya̠ ib̠uiy ipu ma̠ i̠nye̠n. Ke̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠d̠e ma̠ e̠no̠gho̠man ta̠ wa̠nwuna̠ nyam.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 \wj “Sa̠ wa̠ unigha̠ ma̠ onin e̠kpa ikpoki bho̠ eka̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ amar a̠loghom anwa, anwa na̠ okpon d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ igbirigbir, anwa na̠ a̠b̠u ma̠ esi ola̠ anwa ogbebh d̠o̠, sa̠ anwa na̠ a̠kokod̠i ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ anwa okpo d̠o̠ asar.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ ami̠ ighil a̠rugugu, sa̠ ami̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠wo̠gi̠ ma̠ ikpoki d̠oyom d̠a̠ a̠de. Kpone, i̠do̠ ma̠ ikpoki d̠oyom.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 26 \wj “Sa̠ wa̠nwuna̠ do̠yo̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, ‘Anwa o̠gbo̠ro̠gbo̠r obhobho i̠kpo̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu. Anwa a̠loghom ma̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠b̠u ma̠ esi ola̠ ami̠ ogbebh d̠o̠, sa̠ ami̠ na̠ a̠kokod̠i ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ okpo d̠o̠ asar.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Ku̠gba ma̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ akpe̠ nyam o̠lo̠gh okpoki d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ otu-ikpoki bho̠, b̠o̠ka̠ igiel ami̠ iru, ami̠ ate̠i̠ ikpoki d̠ami̠ na̠ asu̠o̠ ya̠ ka̠ i̠mar bho̠.\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “ ‘Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ibhine ma̠ ikpoki bho̠ d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ enigha̠ i̠na wa̠ ate̠i̠ d̠iobh ami̠na bho̠.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Ezin bho̠, o̠ni̠ wa̠ ate̠i̠ ya̠ ib̠uiy bho̠, ta̠ onigha̠ ma̠ o̠gbam; ya̠a̠, i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ bho̠, bebina̠ o̠nyi̠ki̠kara ya̠ i̠na ate̠i̠ bho̠ eka̠, ta̠ o̠wo̠r obhin.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Sa̠ a̠ruom ma̠ oze ma̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu wa̠ omutiom d̠o̠ ma̠ asu̠o̠ bho̠, od̠ighom d̠a̠ obom azi̠m; i̠se̠ bha̠ esi ed̠i na̠ o̠ghi̠r ib̠ub̠ura̠ od̠i.’\wj* 
\s1 Osobh ase̠ Ra̠dede bho̠ 
\p  
\v 31 \wj “Sa̠ obhel bho̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠ru na̠ isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠, eb̠la̠ itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ta̠ ed̠igh na̠ i̠na eru, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ aro̠ d̠a̠ i̠kasi̠ a̠dila̠de irileghom isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj Sa̠ a̠nwunom eb̠la̠ ra̠dede bho̠ ta̠ ekokod̠ia̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ abagi̠o̠n awa ma̠ ebu ebu, agu̠o̠ okponom ro̠nana na̠ abagi̠o̠n ro̠nana bho̠ na̠ iwel bho̠.\wj* 
\v 33 \wj Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠bhin ro̠nana bho̠ amar a̠guri d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠, ya̠a̠ iwel bho̠ d̠a̠ ekiel.\wj* 
\p  
\v 34 \wj “D̠a̠ obhel obha̠ sa̠ O̠li̠le̠ma bho̠ ta̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ebu wa̠ d̠a̠ agba od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Itue ma̠ i̠se̠n, inyin ogbo ya̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ na̠ ane̠ghe̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ya̠ ukokod̠i uguri isisa̠n inyin ka̠ d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj Ezin bho̠, o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi ami̠ sa̠ inyin unigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, e̠d̠o̠gh amu̠m a̠d̠ighi ami̠, sa̠ inyin unigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ amu̠m o̠d̠a, ami̠ iru ma̠ isuloma̠ sa̠ inyin ud̠ighom ami̠,\wj* 
\v 36 \wj Ami̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ e̠dab̠a sa̠ inyin umuneni ami̠ ma̠ ukpe, ami̠ i̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r sa̠ inyin ukoko ami̠, u̠lo̠gh ami̠ ma̠ ikoli sa̠ inyin uru ra̠ ukpon ami̠.’\wj* 
\p  
\v 37 \wj “D̠a̠ obhel obha̠ sa̠ ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, a̠kere obhel wa̠ i̠yar u̠bi̠gh ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi nyam sa̠ i̠yar unigha̠ nyam ed̠ia̠n bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ e̠d̠o̠gh amu̠m a̠d̠ighi nyam sa̠ unigha̠ nyam amu̠m o̠d̠a bho̠?\wj* 
\v 38 \wj A̠kere obhel wa̠ i̠yar u̠bi̠gh anwa ma̠ isuloma̠ sa̠ ud̠ighom anwa bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ anwa i̠ro̠ ma̠ e̠dab̠a sa̠ umuneni nyam ukpe bho̠?\wj* 
\v 39 \wj A̠kere obhel wa̠ i̠yar u̠bi̠gh ka̠ anwa na̠ anwe̠r, bo̠d̠o̠ anwa i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ikoli sa̠ i̠yar u̠gi̠ ka̠ ukpon anwa bho̠?’\wj* 
\p  
\v 40 \wj “Sa̠ O̠li̠le̠ma bho̠ ta̠ awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, ‘Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, agu̠o̠ inyin ugir unigha̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠ami̠ wa̠ ikulom ipu bho̠, bha̠ inyin ugir unigha̠ ami̠.’ \wj* 
\p  
\v 41 \wj “D̠a̠ obhel obha̠ sa̠ i̠na ta̠ agba a̠nigha̠ nyen ogbo ya̠ d̠a̠ ekiel bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Itene ma̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠ami̠, inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ osugi ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ba anya wa̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ bho̠, wa̠ ugbonogi usisa̠n Eru Bho̠ na̠ itileduom d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 42 \wj Ezin bho̠ o̠ko̠i̠ a̠d̠ighi ami̠, ya̠ inyin unigha̠ d̠o̠ ami̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n, e̠d̠o̠gh amu̠m a̠d̠ighi ami̠ ya̠ inyin unigha̠ d̠o̠ ami̠ ma̠ amu̠m ya̠ o̠d̠a,\wj* 
\v 43 \wj Ami̠ iru ma̠ isuloma̠ ya̠ inyin ud̠ighom d̠o̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ otu, ami̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ e̠dab̠a ya̠ inyin umuneni d̠o̠ ami̠ ma̠ ukpe, ami̠ i̠nwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r aro̠ nyen d̠a̠ ikoli, ya̠a̠ inyin uru d̠o̠ ra̠ okpon ami̠.’ \wj* 
\p  
\v 44 \wj “O̠ku̠a sa̠ a̠wa ta̠ e̠wo̠ran nyen ma̠a̠, ‘Wa̠nwuna̠, a̠kere obhel wa̠ i̠yar u̠bi̠gh ka̠ anwa i̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠ko̠i̠, bo̠d̠o̠ e̠d̠o̠gh amu̠m a̠d̠ighi nyam, bo̠d̠o̠ anwa iru ma̠ isuloma̠, bo̠d̠o̠ anwa i̠ro̠ ma̠ e̠dab̠a, bo̠d̠o̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ asu̠nwe̠r, bo̠d̠o̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ikoli, sa̠ i̠yar u̠we̠le̠man oru ra̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ onigha̠ oyom?’\wj* 
\v 45 \wj Sa̠ i̠na ta̠ awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, ‘Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, agu̠o̠ inyin ogir d̠o̠ onigha̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ awa wa̠ ikulom ipu d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠ami̠ bho̠, bha̠ inyin ugir d̠o̠ onigha̠ ami̠ nyen.’\wj* 
\v 46 \wj Sa̠ i̠nye̠n ta̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ alu̠kpe̠ egbika̠ wa̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ bho̠, ya̠a̠ ib̠eb̠i a̠nwunom bho̠ ta̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ esi a̠ghud̠um ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠.”\wj* 
\c 26  
\s1 Imimia̠n Ogigh A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:1,2; A̠luk 22:1,2; Azo̠n 11:45-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Igiel bho̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ a̠munieni ma̠ ratu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠nye̠n bho̠, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠,  
\v 2 \wj “Inyin ologhom ma̠a̠, ka̠ i̠wal a̠d̠a̠ma̠ iten, bha̠ E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠ na̠ a̠lei; sa̠ ta̠ owol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ o̠du̠ ogigh.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 3 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ikei a̠nwunom bho̠ ikokod̠ia̠n d̠a̠ otu irileghom ta̠ we̠mu̠ okur bho̠ wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠keyafas bho̠,  
\v 4 sa̠ awa imimia̠n imutioghom re̠kal ya̠ obhin ikoiny ob̠ol A̠zizo̠s ogigh.  
\v 5 Ya̠a̠ imimia̠n ma̠a̠, “Ko o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ e̠yal bho̠ b̠o̠ka̠ elobhiri ogbo e̠ma na̠ osor.” 
\s1 Uzuom A̠zizo̠s amu̠nu̠ ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠ d̠a̠ Abe̠tani̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:3-9; Azo̠n 12:1-8) 
\p  
\v 6 I̠se̠n bha̠, A̠zizo̠s od̠i d̠a̠ Abe̠tani̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ Asai̠mo̠n wa̠ anwe̠r asu̠nwe̠r ekid̠igh bho̠.  
\v 7 Sa̠ odi ani̠ a̠bhin ololo amu̠nu̠ ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠ ola̠ ibom a̠b̠ua̠, a̠ru ra̠ a̠zuom d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na od̠i d̠a̠ akpata od̠e bho̠. 
\p  
\v 8 Ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ ogbo ogir bho̠ i̠bi̠gh bho̠, sa̠ iguromeni ma̠ rologi ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “A̠din ere na̠ a̠robh amu̠nu̠ ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠ i̠nye̠n o̠ku̠a?”  
\v 9 Nab̠o̠, amu̠nu̠ i̠nye̠n elei iya̠ ka̠ uwol ibom a̠b̠ua̠ obhin onigha̠ ma̠ ronyigoiny bho̠. 
\p  
\v 10 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s a̠loghom abar wa̠ awa na̠ e̠ru̠ru̠an bho̠, sa̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin udin ere na̠ o̠nyo̠gho̠ghan na̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i ya̠ ani̠ onon a̠gir a̠nigha̠ ami̠ bho̠?\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Ronyigoiny bho̠ sa̠ od̠i na̠ inyin eb̠la̠ obhel, ya̠a̠ Ami̠ ka̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ na̠ inyin eb̠la̠ obhel.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ezin bho̠, a̠zuom ami̠ ma̠ amu̠nu̠ ed̠u e̠nu̠nu̠ nyen, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man ozu d̠ami̠ ogboloma̠ a̠ma̠d̠i d̠ami̠.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, kesikesi ola̠ ta̠ o̠gba ma̠ ib̠eb̠i asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠, ta̠ o̠gba nyen abar onon wa̠ i̠na a̠gir bho̠ obhin o̠ru̠ru̠an i̠na.”\wj* 
\s1 A̠zuda̠s a̠wol A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:10,11; A̠luk 22:3-6) 
\p  
\v 14 Sa̠ odi d̠a̠ a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠, wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠zuda̠s Iskari̠o̠t bho̠, agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠,  
\v 15 ka̠ a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Inyin ta̠ onigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ ere ka̠ ami̠ ib̠eton i̠na inigha̠ inyin?” Sa̠ awa i̠wal a̠d̠usubh na̠ d̠iobh ikpoki a̠silva̠ inigha̠ i̠na.  
\v 16 Ob̠eton d̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zuda̠s ake̠ ma̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan e̠ti̠ti̠gha ola̠ ta̠ a̠sora̠n i̠na ma̠ owol A̠zizo̠s. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠e ma̠ E̠yal Opel Oten  //  Wa̠ Ekunuguma̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:12-21; A̠luk 22:7-13; Azo̠n 13:21-30) 
\p  
\v 17 D̠a̠ o̠pu̠r a̠d̠a̠ma̠ E̠yal Abe̠re̠di̠ wa̠ Owubh d̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan ta̠ A̠zizo̠s iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na ipura̠n ma̠a̠, “A̠kere esi wa̠ anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠ghan i̠yar o̠gi̠ ka̠ o̠tu̠ghu̠man osisa̠n oyom, ma̠ od̠e ed̠ia̠n E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠?” 
\p  
\v 18 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠gi̠e̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ ka̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ ma̠a̠, ‘O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ agba ma̠a̠: Obhel d̠ami̠ na̠ a̠tua̠n, ami̠ na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠ami̠ ta̠ od̠e ma̠ E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠ d̠a̠ otu d̠oyom.’ ”\wj* 
\v 19 Sa̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ igir agu̠o̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom awa bho̠, sa̠ awa ikokod̠ia̠n E̠yal Opel Oten bho̠. 
\p  
\v 20 Agu̠o̠ ate̠i̠ a̠dule bho̠, sa̠ i̠na na̠ a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠ i̠ro̠ d̠a̠ akpata od̠e,  
\v 21 na̠ ed̠e ma̠ ed̠ia̠n bho̠, sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin, odi o̠ni̠ inyin ta̠ a̠wol ami̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ awa ib̠ogina̠ ma̠ ibom, sa̠ o̠ni̠ o̠ni̠ i̠se̠ ake̠ ma̠ opura̠n o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠, “Wa̠nwuna̠, ami̠ ke̠re̠?” 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran awa ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ wa̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ na̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ onin e̠kpa ed̠ia̠n bho̠, bha̠ wa̠ ta̠ a̠wol ami̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ta̠ agi̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ u̠ge̠ ugboloma̠ I̠na bho̠, ya̠a̠ itogi e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ o̠wo̠l ob̠ol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ bho̠! O̠we̠le̠man o̠mar o̠yo̠ ka̠ ibhon a̠pu.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 25 Sa̠ A̠zuda̠s wa̠ ta̠ a̠wol i̠na bho̠ a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, anwa na̠ agba ma̠ ami̠, ka̠din?” 
\q1 \wj Sa̠ i̠na awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ agba.”\wj* 
\s1 Ed̠ia̠n ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:22-26; A̠luk 22:14-23; 1 Ako̠ri̠nt 11:23-25) 
\p  
\v 26 Obhel bho̠ awa na̠ ed̠e bho̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠bhin abe̠re̠di̠, sa̠ a̠tutumeni, sa̠ a̠puron a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Ibhine ma̠ ed̠e; onon ozu d̠ami̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin okpa̠ko bho̠, sa̠ ase̠bh A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ awa agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Eb̠la̠ inyin ibhine ma̠ e̠d̠a.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Ezin bho̠ i̠nye̠n asi̠ d̠ami̠, wa̠ aghu̠ame̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠zo̠ bho̠, asi̠ wa̠ uzu unigha̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ obhin o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, obhin i̠se̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, ami̠ ko o̠d̠a mu̠ ma̠ a̠min itu a̠grep tu̠tu̠n d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ inyin ad̠a ma̠ imom a̠min d̠a̠ irileghom ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ bho̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 30 Sa̠ awa i̠mo̠r aso̠r, sa̠ i̠d̠u̠a i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ igu Roliv. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s a̠wa̠ ma̠ A̠puta̠ ta̠ aku̠a I̠na 
\p  
\v 31 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Eb̠la̠ inyin ta̠ eghil e̠we̠le̠man ami̠ e̠d̠u̠a ma̠ a̠d̠ugula̠n onon ebula̠ ami̠, ezin bho̠ na̠ o̠ge̠ oguri d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ ma̠a̠:\wj* 
\q1 \wj “ ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠gigh okponom ro̠nana bho̠,\wj* 
\q2 \wj sa̠ o̠lo̠gh ro̠nana bho̠ ta̠ e̠sasaragi̠an.’\wj*\f + \fr 26:31 \ft \xt Azak 13:7\f* 
\m  
\v 32 \wj Ya̠a̠, igiel ami̠ na̠ a̠b̠etina̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ a̠b̠a̠ra̠ inyin d̠a̠ Agalili.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 33 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ighilighu i̠d̠u̠a eka̠, ami̠ ko oghil ani̠ d̠o̠ ad̠u̠a.” 
\p  
\v 34 Ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠, a̠d̠ugula̠n onon, kisa̠ olobhiri e̠nu̠r bho̠ ta̠ alal, anwa ta̠ aku̠a ma̠ i̠sar igiel ma̠a̠ anwa na̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ami̠.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 35 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh na̠ Anwa a̠mugh eka̠, ami̠ ka̠ o̠ku̠a d̠o̠ nyam.” Sa̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ifugh ani̠ ma̠ onin agu̠o̠. 
\s1 A̠siseiny wa̠ d̠a̠ Age̠tsemani bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:32-42; A̠luk 22:39-46) 
\p  
\v 36 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ ogbo atu̠ghan do̠yo̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ esi ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Age̠tsemani, sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠a̠, \wj “I̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n a̠dila̠de, ya̠ ami̠ ta̠ agi̠ ma̠ ebha̠ ka̠ a̠siseiny.”\wj* 
\v 37 Sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin A̠pita̠ na̠ i̠wal anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ Aze̠bidi ab̠aragi̠ma̠ i̠na, sa̠ i̠na asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an a̠d̠igh i̠ku̠nu̠.  
\v 38 Sa̠ i̠na agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Eloghoma̠n ozu d̠ami̠ na̠ aku̠nu̠ ma̠ ibom, aro̠ ka̠ omugh a̠sugho. I̠ro̠ omom na̠ ami̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 39 Sa̠ i̠na agi̠ ma̠ i̠ki̠kara d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ ka̠ a̠b̠obhia̠n a̠siseiny a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠, ku̠gba ma̠ ta̠ a̠b̠ur nab̠o̠, d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ okpa̠ko onon a̠ten ad̠u̠a d̠ami̠. D̠a̠ o̠ku̠a eka̠, o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ku̠ d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠ami̠, ya̠a̠ d̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠oyom.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 40 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agi̠ ka̠ ate̠i̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ sa̠ abi̠gh ma̠a̠ awa na̠ ekod̠u, sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n A̠pita̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin urue d̠o̠ ma̠ od̠igh na̠ ami̠ o̠ro̠ omom bebina̠ ekud̠i obhel ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 41 \wj I̠ro̠ ma̠ omom esiseiny b̠o̠ka̠ inyin umel d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ed̠igh d̠a̠ ad̠agi̠an. E̠mu̠gh bho̠ na̠ e̠ral ya̠a̠ ozu bho̠ na̠ a̠dugh.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 42 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ agi̠ ma̠ oleghemeni i̠wal igiel ka̠ a̠siseiny a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠, ku̠gba ma̠ okpa̠ko egbika̠ onon ka̠ orue d̠o̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a, a̠ten ka̠ Ami̠ i̠d̠a, bha̠ i̠to̠ d̠oyom emite.” \wj* 
\p  
\v 43 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ agi̠ ka̠ abi̠gh ma̠ awa na̠ ekod̠u, ezin bho̠ a̠rid̠ien d̠awa na̠ e̠mu̠mo̠r ibom.  
\v 44 Sa̠ i̠na awe̠le̠man awa a̠puta̠ agi̠ ka̠ a̠siseiny oleghemeni i̠sar igiel, a̠fugh onin abar bho̠. 
\p  
\v 45 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ i̠sar ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ ka̠ agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “Inyin od̠idia̠ na̠ ekod̠u na̠ esira̠ ma̠ epobh? Ikpone, iloghome ma̠ obhel wa̠ u̠to̠ ugiri bho̠ na̠ a̠lei, sa̠ ta̠ owol O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ idighi ma̠ i̠karabh.\wj* 
\v 46 \wj Ib̠egina̠! na̠ a̠lei o̠gi̠! Wa̠ a̠wol ami̠ bho̠ aro̠ ka̠ na̠ a̠misi ma̠ i̠se̠n!”\wj* 
\s1 Ub̠ol A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:43-50; A̠luk 22:47-53; Azo̠n 18:3-12) 
\p  
\v 47 I̠na od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ a̠fugh, sa̠ obom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom ya̠ isibhi ma̠ rab̠e̠ge̠re̠ na̠ re̠b̠am ya̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ re̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠m A̠zuda̠s, odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ awa a̠d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal bho̠, a̠ru.  
\v 48 I̠se̠n, wa̠ a̠wol i̠na bho̠ a̠tu̠o̠m elegh a̠leriom awa ma̠a̠: “O̠ni̠ wa̠ ami̠ ta̠ api̠pi̠o̠bh bho̠ bha̠ O̠ni̠ bho̠, ib̠ole i̠na.”  
\v 49 D̠a̠ onin obhel bho̠ sa̠ i̠na agi̠ epa̠ d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s ka̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “We̠mu̠ Atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠, ami̠ a̠bheleguma̠ nyam o!” Sa̠ api̠pi̠o̠bh i̠na. 
\p  
\v 50 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠tologha̠n, gire ma̠ abar wa̠ anwa idin iru bho̠.”\wj* 
\p Sa̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ iru ra̠ isibh A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ ib̠ol i̠na. 
\p  
\v 51 I̠se̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ aro̠ na̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mutiom ab̠e̠ge̠re̠ do̠yo̠ sa̠ a̠sobh a̠to ta̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ a̠b̠uton. 
\p  
\v 52 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s aghaghana i̠na a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Lo̠ghe̠ ma̠ ab̠e̠ge̠re̠ d̠oyom ma̠ esi wa̠ akpe̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ bho̠, ezin bho̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ esibh ab̠e̠ge̠re̠, na̠ emugh d̠a̠ ab̠e̠ge̠re̠.\wj* 
\v 53 \wj Bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ anwa na̠ aru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠, ami̠ ka̠ orue d̠o̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠ o̠fi̠ri̠ma ami̠ ma̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal ro̠lo̠gh\wj*\f + \fr 26:53 \ft Inya̠ e̠wala na̠ a̠d̠usubh o̠ni̠r (72000) ogbo e̠gham\f*\wj itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n i̠se̠n, ke̠re̠?\wj* 
\v 54 \wj O̠ku̠a ka̠ ta̠ od̠ighi eka̠ omuzoghod̠iom ya̠ u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, ya̠ i̠kpe̠ ma̠ omite bho̠?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 55 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ na̠ a̠wia̠n o̠go̠ ebhugh ke̠re̠, ma̠ ola̠ inyin ubhin rab̠e̠ge̠re̠ na̠ re̠b̠am na̠ oru ra̠ ob̠ol ami̠. Ami̠ i̠ro̠ghan a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠a̠ inyin ub̠ol d̠o̠ ami̠.\wj* 
\v 56 \wj Ya̠a̠, eb̠la̠ i̠nye̠n imite ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ omuzoghod̠iom i̠di̠ar ya̠ a̠riwil bho̠ i̠ge̠ iguri d̠a̠ a̠d̠ire e̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠.” \wj* Sa̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo atu̠ghan bho̠ i̠we̠le̠ i̠na i̠ghil i̠d̠u̠a. 
\s1 A̠zizo̠s d̠a̠ a̠misigh ogbo osobh ase̠ bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:53-65; A̠luk 22:54,55,63-71; Azo̠n 18:13,14,19-24) 
\p  
\v 57 Ogbo ya̠ ib̠ol A̠zizo̠s bho̠, ibhin i̠na e̠gi̠ d̠a̠ A̠keyafas, we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, esi wa̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠ na̠ ekokod̠ia̠n bho̠.  
\v 58 Ya̠a̠, A̠pita̠ aro̠ ma̠ egbeiny atu̠o̠no̠m i̠na ka̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ ogigo ta̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, sa̠ a̠d̠igh d̠a̠ ologi ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de na̠ rokponomotu bho̠, ma̠ o̠bi̠gh agu̠o̠ ta̠ a̠bhin a̠kunugiom. 
\p  
\v 59 Sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo osobh ase̠ bho̠ i̠bho̠ro̠ghan o̠ni̠ ola̠ ta̠ agba ma̠ onyob̠a̠ igunugha̠ a̠b̠ologiom A̠zizo̠s, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ ebhin esobh ase̠ bho̠ ebhumeni i̠na egigh.  
\v 60 A̠d̠izo ronyob̠a̠ igunugha̠ emite, ya̠a̠ abar ola̠ a̠sibh i̠na na̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠. 
\p D̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠wal ronyob̠a̠ imite,  
\v 61 i̠gba ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ onon agba ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ ta̠ a̠b̠ogion otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ sa̠ Ami̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠lo amado̠n d̠a̠ a̠bin i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠.’ ” 
\p  
\v 62 Sa̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ a̠b̠etina̠ amara a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa̠ ka̠ o̠wo̠ran d̠o̠ ke̠re̠? Onon ka̠ a̠kere a̠d̠ien abar ola̠ na̠ o̠gba na̠ ob̠ologiom anwa?”  
\v 63 Ya̠a̠, A̠zizo̠s aro̠ b̠u̠b̠o̠m. 
\p Sa̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ a̠bhin d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠, na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam ma̠a̠: Sibhigha̠ ku̠gba ma̠ anwa Akrai̠st O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.” 
\p  
\v 64 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran i̠na ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ agba a̠mutiom. O̠ku̠a eka̠, Ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, obhin i̠se̠n o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠, inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh O̠nyi̠ ta̠ O̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ a̠limon ka̠ na̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ o̠b̠u̠ghu̠b̠u̠gh bho̠.”\wj*\f + \fr 26:64 \ft Bi̠ghe̠ \xt Raso̠r 110:1\ft ; \xt Adan 7:13\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 65 Sa̠ we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ ago̠go̠i̠ny ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ a̠fugh a̠fugh i̠basi̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̱ A̠zib̠a̠! Ta̠ odin ere o̠bho̠ro̠ghan opa̠n onyob̠a̠? I̠bi̠ghe̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na na̠ a̠fugh a̠fugh i̠basi̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̱ A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 66 Inyin u̠bi̠gh eka̠?” 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “I̠na na̠ api̠o̠gho̠m, akpe̠ ma̠ omugh.” 
\pi1  
\v 67 Sa̠ awa i̠si̠ro̠gho̠m i̠na ma̠ i̠gho̠r d̠a̠ a̠misigh, sa̠ igorogh i̠na, sa̠ ipa̠n a̠nwunom i̠b̠abhagh i̠na,  
\v 68 ifugh ma̠a̠, “Akrai̠st! Wa̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠gor anwa bho̠.” 
\s1 A̠pita̠ aku̠a ma̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 14:66-72; A̠luk 22:56-62; Azo̠n 18:15-18,25-27) 
\p  
\v 69 I̠se̠n A̠pita̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ etire d̠a̠ ologi ogigo bho̠, sa̠ odi ob̠a̠ra̠motu o̠nyani̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠fugh a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa odi o̠ni̠ wa̠ i̠ro̠ ani̠ na̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ Agalili bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 70 Ya̠a̠, i̠na aku̠a d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ta̠ eb̠la̠ awa, sa̠ a̠fugh ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ anwa na̠ agba bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 71 Sa̠ i̠na ad̠u̠a agi̠ d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ogigo bho̠, sa̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ abi̠gh i̠na, sa̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Onon odi o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠rilogha̠n A̠zizo̠s wa̠ Anazare̠t bho̠.” 
\p  
\v 72 Sa̠ i̠na a̠puta̠ aku̠a, a̠sibhigha̠ ma̠a̠: “Ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠!” 
\p  
\v 73 O̠nyi̠ obhel a̠ten, sa̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠ iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ A̠pita̠, sa̠ i̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, anwa odi o̠ni̠ awa nyen, ezin bho̠ a̠nem d̠oyom na̠ agba nyam na̠ a̠mutiom.” 
\p  
\v 74 O̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠na ake̠ ma̠ ogurugia̠n, o̠ghad̠i̠an ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ iloghom d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠!” Ogbo na̠ onin sa̠ olobhiri e̠nu̠r alal.  
\v 75 Sa̠ A̠pita̠ aru̠ru̠an iwowa̠ ta̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ a̠wa̠ ma̠a̠, “Kisa̠ olobhiri e̠nu̠r ta̠ alal, anwa ta̠ aku̠a ami̠ i̠sar igiel, ma̠a̠ anwa na̠ a̠loghom d̠o̠ ami̠.” Sa̠ i̠na a̠rile a̠mite d̠a̠ ogigo bho̠ ka̠ a̠leghe agba ma̠ igbir. 
\c 27  
\s1 Ibhin A̠zizo̠s e̠gi̠o̠m Apai̠let 
\r (Amaki̠ 15:1; A̠luk 23:1,2; Azo̠n 18:28-32) 
\p  
\v 1 Ame̠ghe̠le̠, sa̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠, ikokod̠ia̠n imimia̠n iya̠ ogir ogboloma̠ A̠zizo̠s, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ta̠ osobh ase̠ obhumeni o̠yo̠ ogigh.  
\v 2 Sa̠ awa i̠bhad̠i̠ i̠na ibhin i̠gi̠o̠m Apai̠let we̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠. 
\s1 Osina̠ Omugh ta̠ A̠zuda̠s 
\r (Rogir 1:18,19) 
\p  
\v 3 Igiel bho̠ A̠zuda̠s wa̠ a̠wol i̠na bho̠ abi̠gh ma̠ na̠ osobh ase̠ obhumeni ma̠ A̠zizo̠s bho̠, sa̠ a̠loghoma̠n ma̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gir api̠e̠. Sa̠ a̠mulumeni ma̠ a̠d̠usubh na̠ d̠iobh ikpoki a̠silva̠ bho̠ agi̠o̠m we̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠,  
\v 4 agba ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ na̠ a̠gir i̠karabh, a̠wol o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠pi̠o̠gho̠m d̠o̠, a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ uzu ma̠ asi̠ d̠o̠yo̠.” Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Ere a̠gboloma̠ i̠yar? Anwa ku kpone ma̠ a̠d̠ighom.” 
\p  
\v 5 Sa̠ i̠na a̠zu ma̠ ikpoki bho̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ sa̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a ka̠ akpo̠ a̠sina̠ a̠mugh. 
\p  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ ikpokpo ma̠ ikpoki bho̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, “Na̠ osora̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ obhin ka̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ esi wa̠ na̠ okoko ma̠ ikpoki bho̠, agu̠o̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ ikpoki ogigha̠n o̠ni̠ bho̠.”  
\v 7 O̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠mu̠gho̠nyan obhin ikpoki bho̠ ka̠ ogho a̠de ta̠ ob̠olob̠ol ma̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ obhin otenemeni o̠karabh esi ola̠ od̠i risuloma̠.  
\v 8 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, obhin obhel obha̠ ra̠ o̠te̠i̠ a̠didon, na̠ obhelegi ma̠ a̠de obha̠, ma̠a̠, “A̠de Asi̠.”  
\v 9 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠ sa̠ umuzoghod̠iom iwowa̠ wa̠ owil A̠zerimaya a̠wa̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠: “Sa̠ awa ibhin a̠d̠usubh na̠ d̠iobh ikpoki a̠silva̠ bho̠, ikpoki e̠mu̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ anwi̠i̠ny Izre̠l ima̠ra̠ ma̠ awa ta̠ o̠kpe̠ bho̠.  
\v 10 Sa̠ awa ibhin ikpoki bho̠ igho ma̠ a̠de ta̠ ob̠olob̠ol ma̠ i̠di̠ar bho̠, agu̠o̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ a̠ruom ami̠ bho̠.”\f + \fr 27:10 \ft Bi̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ \xt Azak 11:12,13\ft ; \xt A̠zer 19:1-13; 32:6-9\ft .\f* 
\s1 Ipura̠n ta̠ Apai̠let 
\r (Amaki̠ 15:2-5; A̠luk 23:3-5; Azo̠n 18:33-38) 
\p  
\v 11 I̠se̠ sa̠ ibhin A̠zizo̠s ka̠ i̠marame̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ we̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n A̠zizo̠s ma̠a̠, “Anwa o̠li̠le̠ma ogbo A̠zu bho̠ ke̠re̠?” 
\p Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s awo̠ran ma̠a̠, \wj “Anwa na̠ agba aman.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 12 Sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠ ikpon abarabar ib̠ologiom i̠na, ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠wo̠ran d̠o̠ ma̠ abar.  
\v 13 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ Apai̠let a̠pura̠n i̠na ma̠a̠, “Anwa na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ ya̠ na̠ o̠gba na̠ ob̠ologiom anwa bho̠ ke̠re̠?”  
\v 14 Ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ o̠wo̠ran d̠o̠, bebina̠ abar, sa̠ a̠d̠igh ilologia̠n ibom ma̠ we̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠. 
\s1 Osobhma̠ ase̠ ogigh A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 15:6-15; A̠luk 23:13-26; Azo̠n 18:39—19:16) 
\p  
\v 15 I̠se̠n d̠a̠ e̠yal bho̠, bha̠ obhel wa̠ we̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠ na̠ a̠mutiomgha̠n o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ ikoli ola̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ipuru.  
\v 16 D̠a̠ obhel obha̠, bha̠ odi obom od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s\f + \fr 27:16 \ft A̠d̠ien onon bo̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠izo i̠pu̠r ra̠to a̠d̠ire ya̠ ubhin unwe ma̠ o̠nu̠ bho̠.\f* Abarabas aro̠ d̠a̠ ikoli.  
\v 17 D̠a̠ obhel bho̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ ekokod̠ia̠n bho̠, sa̠ Apai̠let a̠pura̠n ma̠a̠, “Inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠ghan ami̠ ma̠ imutiom oken d̠a̠ i̠wal awa onigha̠ inyin: A̠zizo̠s Abarabas, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠?”  
\v 18 Ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠loghom ma̠a̠ awa ibhin d̠a̠ egbugbo ologi eb̠eton A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st enigha̠ i̠na. 
\p  
\v 19 Agu̠o̠ i̠na aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ i̠kasi̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠, sa̠ ani̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠ruom a̠duom agi̠o̠m i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ko ogir abar a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ o̠pi̠o̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ abar bho̠. Ezin bho̠, ami̠ i̠bigh ibom ali̠gam a̠ruzu d̠a̠ amala ma̠ a̠didon d̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠yo̠.” 
\p  
\v 20 Ya̠a̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ ikei bho̠ itumugiom o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ epuru ku ma̠ Abarabas, ya̠a̠ ogigh A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st. 
\p  
\v 21 Sa̠ we̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠ a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “D̠a̠ i̠wal awa ka̠ ami̠ imutiom oken inigha̠ inyin?” 
\p Sa̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Abarabas.” 
\p  
\v 22 Sa̠ Apai̠let a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “O̠ku̠a ka̠ ogir ere ogboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zizo̠s wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠?” 
\p Sa̠ eb̠la̠ awa i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Du̠e̠ ma̠ a̠gigh!” 
\p  
\v 23 Sa̠ i̠na a̠pura̠n awa ma̠a̠, “Ezin ka̠ ere, a̠gir a̠kere a̠d̠ien i̠karabh?” 
\p Sa̠ imula̠ i̠lo̠gh e̠mi̠ imulughu ma̠a̠, “Du̠e̠ ma̠ a̠gigh!” 
\p  
\v 24 Ya̠ Apai̠let a̠loghoma̠n ma̠ abar ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue a̠gir alo̠gh bo̠ bho̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ na̠ e̠ko̠ro̠, sa̠ a̠bhin amu̠m a̠tita̠la̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ abhe̠bhi̠la d̠a̠ a̠misigh eb̠la̠ o̠lo̠gh a̠nwunom bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Ami̠ id̠igh ani̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ o̠kpe̠ ogigha̠n o̠ni̠ onon. Inyin na̠ agu̠o̠ ka̠ ekpon ed̠ighom!” 
\p  
\v 25 Sa̠ eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ i̠wo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Asi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ e̠mu̠ d̠i̠yar na̠ ranwi̠i̠ny d̠a̠ i̠yar!” 
\p  
\v 26 O̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠na a̠mutiom Abarabas a̠nigha̠ awa, ya̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ i̠na a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ o̠gu̠ro̠gh na̠ o̠du̠ o̠yo̠ ogigh. 
\s1 Ogbo E̠gham bho̠ iduom A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 15:16-21; Azo̠n 19:2,3) 
\p  
\v 27 Sa̠ ogbo e̠gham ta̠ we̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠ ibhin A̠zizo̠s i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ we̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠ sa̠ ikokod̠i ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo e̠gham bho̠.  
\v 28 Sa̠ i̠ko̠gi̠o̠n ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠ i̠lo̠gi̠ i̠na ma̠ obom akapa ododo,  
\v 29 sa̠ ilo ma̠ eghoi ib̠ub̠ulom izuom e̠mu̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠lo̠gh okpeti i̠ki̠ani̠ d̠a̠ od̠iom agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ ikpuluma̠n d̠a̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠ iduom i̠na ma̠a̠, “E O̠li̠le̠ma A̠zu, i̠yar na̠ okpud̠ia̠n o!”  
\v 30 Sa̠ i̠si̠ro̠gho̠m i̠na ma̠ i̠gho̠r, sa̠ ibhin okpeti i̠ki̠ani̠ bho̠ ib̠orogh e̠mu̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 31 Sa̠ igiel bho̠ awa na̠ eduom i̠na e̠we̠le̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠ko̠gi̠o̠n ibura̠ ododo ya̠ awa i̠lo̠gi̠ i̠na bho̠, sa̠ inwe i̠lo̠gi̠ i̠na ma̠ ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ibhin i̠na i̠d̠u̠a ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ka̠ o̠du̠ o̠yo̠ ogigh. 
\s1 O̠du̠ ogigh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 15:22-32; A̠luk 23:27-43; Azo̠n 19:17-27) 
\p  
\v 32 Agu̠o̠ awa na̠ emite bho̠, sa̠ awa i̠manana ma̠ o̠ni̠ A̠sirin ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ Asai̠mo̠n, sa̠ iponoma̠ i̠na ma̠ orol e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren ta̠ A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 33 Sa̠ i̠gi̠ ka̠ imisi ma̠ esi ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠a̠ Ago̠lgo̠ta, (a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, “Esi okpokpo e̠mu̠.”)  
\v 34 Sa̠ awa inigha̠ i̠na ma̠ a̠min ya̠ u̠gu̠a na̠ a̠non; ya̠a̠ igiel bho̠ i̠na ad̠e̠d̠i̠ma bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠gin o̠d̠a.  
\v 35 Sa̠ awa i̠du̠ i̠na, sa̠ irobh okob̠a̠ ibhin i̠ru̠gi̠an ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 36 Sa̠ awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de igon i̠na.  
\v 37 Sa̠ awa i̠ge̠ ma̠ iku wa̠ i̠gba igboloma̠ i̠na bho̠, i̠ke̠ri̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠: ONON A̠ZIZO̠S, O̠LI̠LE̠MA A̠ZU BHO̠.  
\v 38 Igiel bho̠ awa i̠du̠ i̠na bho̠, i̠du̠ na̠ i̠wal aru̠gba, odi d̠a̠ od̠iom agba d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠a̠ uwed̠i d̠a̠ okiel.  
\v 39 Sa̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eten bho̠ i̠ki̠ri̠ i̠na inyegi ma̠ aru̠mu̠ d̠awa  
\v 40 ifugh ma̠a̠, “Anwa wa̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠b̠ogion otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠lo amado̠n d̠a̠ a̠bin i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, tenemeni ma̠ ozu d̠oyom, agu̠o̠ anwa i̠ro̠ ma̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, bha̠ sore ma̠ a̠ru d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠!”  
\v 41 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠, na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠, na̠ ikei bho̠ iduom i̠na nyen efugh ma̠a̠,  
\v 42 “I̠na na̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo, ya̠a̠ na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ otenemeni ozu d̠o̠yo̠! O̠li̠le̠ma Izre̠l! I̠se̠n sore d̠a̠ e̠mi̠gi̠re̠ni̠an oriren bho̠ ma̠ a̠ru, sa̠ i̠yar ta̠ oma̠ra̠ nyam.  
\v 43 I̠na a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, na̠ a̠lei A̠zib̠a̠ a̠tenemeni i̠na ma̠ i̠se̠n, ku̠gba ma̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ma̠ra̠! Ezin bho̠ i̠na agba ma̠a̠, ‘Ami̠ O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.’ ”  
\v 44 Sa̠ aru̠gba ya̠ u̠du̠gi̠ d̠a̠ aka ta̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠ o̠ze̠gi̠ bho̠ eka̠ erogi i̠na. 
\s1 Omugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 15:33-41; A̠luk 23:44-49; Azo̠n 19:28-30) 
\p  
\v 45 Obeton d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ o̠wal ma̠ obhel bho̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal d̠a̠ e̠sala̠d̠io ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ i̠sar d̠a̠ etita̠n, sa̠ azi̠m a̠kpegiom eb̠la̠ e̠mara̠nwunom.  
\v 46 Sa̠ agu̠o̠ o̠wal ma̠ obhel bho̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ i̠sar d̠a̠ etita̠n, sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mulughu na̠ obom okoroko ma̠a̠, \wj “E̠lai̠, E̠lai̠,\wj*\f + \fr 27:46 \ft Idi i̠pu̠r robhurogho bho̠ u̠ge̠ ma̠a̠:\fqa Eloi, Eloi\f*\wj lama sabaktani̠?”\wj* (onon a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠, \wj “A̠zib̠a̠ d̠ami̠, A̠zib̠a̠ d̠ami̠, ere wa̠ Anwa na̠ awe̠le̠man ami̠ bho̠?”\wj*)\f + \fr 27:46 \ft \xt Raso̠r 22:1\f* 
\p  
\v 47 Sa̠ idi awa ya̠ i̠mara ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠, “Na̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠ I̠lai̠za.” 
\p  
\v 48 D̠a̠ ogbo na̠ onin, sa̠ odi awa a̠kpo ma̠ eghil ka̠ a̠bhin asapu̠ ato̠ri̠ d̠a̠ igheghed̠um a̠min, sa̠ akpu̠o̠m d̠a̠ okpeti a̠b̠eton a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠ o̠d̠a.  
\v 49 Ya̠a̠ ipa̠n ogbo ifugh ma̠a̠, “I̠we̠le̠, ta̠ o̠bi̠gh ka̠ I̠lai̠za ta̠ a̠ru ra̠ a̠tenemeni i̠na.” 
\p  
\v 50 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠nwe a̠mulughu na̠ obom okoroko, sa̠ ekpo epobh bho̠ a̠sobha̠n. 
\p  
\v 51 Sa̠ ukpe wa̠ ubhin usobhom a̠lukpesi e̠tu̠tu̠ d̠a̠ otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ a̠b̠eton d̠a̠ eb̠o bho̠ agu̠an a̠sor aru̠gi̠an i̠wal a̠bin, sa̠ a̠de bho̠ a̠nyegia̠n, sa̠ ra̠de o̠gbi̠o̠ma bho̠ ib̠ob̠omia̠n i̠saragi̠an.  
\v 52 Sa̠ ranyu̠ od̠i bho̠ ikpegina̠ sa̠ a̠d̠izo imumugh ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ib̠egina̠.  
\v 53 Sa̠ awa imiteghu d̠a̠ a̠rugugua̠ a̠ma̠d̠i bho̠, i̠gi̠ ka̠ imutuma̠ ma̠ a̠d̠izo a̠nwunom d̠a̠ E̠ma E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠. 
\p  
\v 54 Sa̠ igiel bho̠ we̠mu̠ ogbo e̠gham bho̠, na̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i na̠ i̠na na̠ egon A̠zizo̠s bho̠, i̠bi̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠de bho̠ a̠nyegia̠n a̠b̠obomia̠n a̠d̠igh bho̠, na̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠, sa̠ ibom a̠rugugu isibh awa, sa̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠, “Ya̠gia̠ga̠i, onon O̠nyi̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠!” 
\p  
\v 55 A̠d̠izo anwani̠ ya̠ i̠tu̠o̠no̠mghan A̠zizo̠s igir ogir inigha̠ i̠na bho̠, ob̠eton d̠a̠ Agalili, i̠ro̠ ani̠ ma̠ i̠se̠.  
\v 56 Idi awa bha̠, A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠, A̠meri oweni ta̠ A̠zemsi na̠ A̠zose̠fu̠, na̠ oweni anwi̠i̠ny ta̠ Aze̠bidi. 
\s1 A̠ma̠d̠i ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 15:42-47; A̠luk 23:50-56; Azo̠n 19:38-42) 
\p  
\v 57 Agu̠o̠ ate̠i̠ a̠dule bho̠, sa̠ o̠li̠la ola̠ Ari̠mati̠a ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠ A̠zose̠fu̠, ola̠ ra̠ a̠ten ani̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ atu̠ghan ta̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ru.  
\v 58 I̠na agi̠ d̠a̠ Apai̠let ka̠ a̠puru ma̠ ozu ta̠ A̠zizo̠s, sa̠ Apai̠let a̠ruom ma̠ enigha̠.  
\v 59 Sa̠ A̠zose̠fu̠ a̠bhin omom ukpe asi̠ni̠ni̠n ola̠ amar ab̠ab̠ala a̠bhurugi ma̠ egua̠de bho̠,  
\v 60 sa̠ a̠d̠i d̠a̠ omom od̠i ola̠ o̠yo̠, ola̠ i̠na a̠b̠u a̠mutiom d̠a̠ a̠de o̠gbi̠o̠ma ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ anyu̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠kiligi ma̠ obom o̠pad̠i̠ o̠gbi̠o̠ma a̠kpegiom o̠nu̠ od̠i bho̠ sa̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a.  
\v 61 Sa̠ A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠ na̠ A̠meri uwed̠i bho̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de isumogha̠n od̠i bho̠. 
\s1 Agu̠o̠ i̠mar ikponom od̠i bho̠ 
\p  
\v 62 I̠b̠ala bho̠, wa̠ aro̠ ma̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ Epobh bho̠, sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ na̠ Rafarisi bho̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ Apai̠let,  
\v 63 ka̠ i̠gba ma̠a̠, “We̠mu̠, ru̠ru̠ane̠ ma̠ abar wa̠ o̠ni̠ igelemeni bho̠ agba ma̠ igiel wa̠ i̠na od̠id̠ia̠ d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um bho̠ ma̠a̠, ‘Ka̠ i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ iten, ami̠ ta̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh.’  
\v 64 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, ruome ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ e̠mar ekponom od̠i bho̠ tu̠tu̠n d̠a̠ oleghemeni i̠sar a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ka̠ o̠gi̠ d̠o̠ ka̠ eb̠igh e̠si̠ghe̠, sa̠ ta̠ e̠gba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh, sa̠ igelemeni wa̠ o̠gu̠man bho̠ ta̠ a̠gurom a̠pu ma̠ o̠pu̠r bho̠.”  
\v 65 Sa̠ Apai̠let agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Ibhine ma̠ ogbo e̠gham ma̠ e̠gi̠ ka̠ ekponom, i̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ ekponom agu̠o̠ inyin uloghom obhin okponom bho̠.”  
\v 66 Sa̠ awa i̠gi̠ ka̠ i̠mar i̠lo̠ ma̠ od̠i bho̠ igir, sa̠ i̠lo̠gh elegh a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh, sa̠ iguri ma̠ ogbo e̠gham ma̠ o̠ro̠ okponom. 
\c 28  
\s1 Ob̠etina̠ d̠a̠ Omugh ta̠ A̠zizo̠s 
\r (Amaki̠ 16:1-8; A̠luk 24:1-12; Azo̠n 20:1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 A̠d̠a̠ma̠ Osira̠ Epobh bho̠ a̠ten, agu̠o̠ na̠ a̠nyiroghom o̠b̠al d̠a̠ o̠pu̠r a̠d̠a̠ma̠ esi a̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠, sa̠ A̠meri wa̠ Amagdala bho̠ na̠ A̠meri uwed̠i i̠gi̠ ka̠ okpon anyu̠ od̠i bho̠.  
\v 2 D̠a̠ awai̠, sa̠ a̠de bho̠ a̠nyegia̠n ibom, ezin bho̠ otileduom ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠sor a̠ru ra̠ a̠kiligi ma̠ o̠pad̠i̠ o̠gbe̠o̠ma bho̠ a̠guri d̠a̠ aka, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ anyu̠ bho̠.  
\v 3 I̠na a̠mite awar agu̠o̠ i̠me̠me̠gi̠na agbararan, sa̠ ibura̠ d̠o̠yo̠ ab̠al agu̠o̠ ab̠ala.  
\v 4 Ebula̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ekponom esi bho̠, ighil a̠rugugu ka̠ e̠te̠i̠ esi ola̠, awa ibhin igiri imugh onyinye. 
\p  
\v 5 Ya̠a̠, otileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ agba a̠nigha̠ ma̠ anwani̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu, ami̠ a̠loghom ma̠ inyin uru ra̠ okpon A̠zizo̠s wa̠ o̠du̠ ugigh bho̠.  
\v 6 I̠na bo̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n, i̠na na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ agba bho̠. Itue ra̠ e̠bi̠gh esi wa̠ uselegi i̠na bho̠,  
\v 7 ma̠ e̠nu̠r e̠gi̠ ka̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠a̠: ‘I̠na na̠ a̠b̠etina̠ d̠a̠ omugh, na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Agalili ka̠ ob̠a̠ra̠ inyin. Obha̠ esi wa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠bi̠gh i̠na bho̠.’ I̠nagha, ami̠ na̠ agba na̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin!” 
\p  
\v 8 Sa̠ awa inugia̠n i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ od̠i bho̠ na̠ a̠rugugu na̠ ibom a̠libhon ologi, sa̠ ikpo ma̠ eghil ka̠ o̠gba onigha̠ ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 9 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠mutuma̠ awa a̠fugh ma̠a̠, \wj “Ami̠ a̠bheleguma̠ o!”\wj* Sa̠ awa iru ra̠ i̠te̠i̠ i̠na ighinigia̠n a̠sike d̠o̠yo̠ ibuom i̠na.  
\v 10 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s agba a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, \wj “O̠ni̠ ko oghil a̠rugugu. I̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ e̠gba ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ a̠rumor d̠ami̠ ma̠a̠, ami̠ na̠ agi̠ d̠a̠ Agalili, awa ta̠ e̠bi̠gh ami̠ ma̠ ebha̠.”\wj* 
\s1 Asu̠gbagba Ogbo Ikponom bho̠ 
\p  
\v 11 Igiel bho̠ anwani̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a bho̠, sa̠ idi ogbo ikponom bho̠ id̠igh d̠a̠ e̠ma bho̠ ka̠ i̠gba ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ imite bho̠ inigha̠ ma̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠.  
\v 12 Sa̠ ogbo aru̠mu̠ rokur bho̠ imimia̠n na̠ ikei bho̠, sa̠ inigha̠ ma̠ ogbo e̠gham bho̠ ma̠ ikpoki ya̠ i̠mo̠mo̠nya,  
\v 13 sa̠ i̠gba inigha̠ awa ma̠a̠, “Inyin ta̠ ogba ma̠a̠, ‘Ogbo atu̠ghan d̠o̠yo̠ iru ma̠ a̠d̠ugula̠n ra̠ eb̠igh i̠na e̠si̠ghe̠, ma̠ obhel ola̠ i̠yar na̠ okod̠u.’  
\v 14 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠, asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n ed̠igh d̠a̠ a̠to ta̠ we̠mu̠ a̠dila̠de i̠to̠ ebhugh bho̠, i̠yar ta̠ ob̠okumeni ma̠ ologi d̠o̠yo̠ b̠o̠ka̠ inyin ud̠igh d̠a̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu.”  
\v 15 Sa̠ awa ibhin ikpoki bho̠ igir agu̠o̠ uruom awa bho̠. A̠nwunom A̠zu od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠ asu̠gbagba i̠nye̠n na̠ e̠sasaragi̠ tu̠tu̠n ka̠ a̠didon. 
\s1 Obom A̠duom bho̠ 
\r (Amaki̠ 16:14-18; A̠luk 24:36-49; Azo̠n 20:19-23; Rogir 1:6-8) 
\p  
\v 16 Sa̠ d̠iobh na̠ onin ogbo ogir bho̠ i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ igu d̠a̠ Agalili, d̠a̠ esi wa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠ruom awa ma̠ o̠gi̠ bho̠.  
\v 17 Igiel bho̠ awa i̠bi̠gh i̠na bho̠, sa̠ ibuom i̠na, ya̠a̠ idi awa ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠na A̠zizo̠s.  
\v 18 Sa̠ A̠zizo̠s a̠d̠ighoma̠ awa agba ma̠a̠, \wj “Na̠ onigha̠ ami̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠limon d̠a̠ a̠de na̠ iya̠ d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠gi̠e̠ ka̠ egir agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ eten ogbo atu̠ghan d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠dede, ma̠ ewur awa ma̠ amu̠m d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠, na̠ O̠nyi̠ bho̠, na̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj I̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ awa ma̠ osibh ogir eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ami̠ iruom inyin ogir bho̠. Iloghome ma̠a̠, ami̠ od̠i na̠ inyin kigiel kigiel tu̠tu̠n d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠.”\wj*